research/history/logs/agent_action_0113.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"64"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}。其中 shared 子库 B^sh 与 routed expert 子库 {B_e} 都是静态向量库，在线侧只做轻量 router 选择少量 routed experts，然后执行 shared 查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权求和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled 结构仍明确排除。当前实际历史已在 r107-r112 上形成 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的兼容低成本前沿，其中 r111 为 0.30x / FVU 0.1228，r112 为 0.28x / FVU 0.1282。唯一主假设：在 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, NUM_EXPERTS=64` 已稳定成立的前提下，继续把 deployment 预算从 `K=80` 压到 `K=64`，有机会把 total_cost 从约 0.28x 进一步左移到约 0.27x（selection≈0.20x, deployment≈0.06x），同时仍把 FVU 控制在约 0.13 左右，从而把 shared+routed 这条新结构段继续推进到更靠左的可部署 Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=64` 仍把 FVU 控制在约 0.135 或更低，则下一轮应继续以本轮为 reference，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 或 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 之一，定位这条 shared+routed 低成本线的下一处 knee，而不是回到旧 family。","如果 `K=64` 相比 r112 明显劣化并失去非支配性，则说明当前 shared+routed 线已接近 deployment knee；下一轮不应继续降 K，而应改做 matched `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1/3` 或切回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 做对照。","如果 `K=64` 结果与 r112 接近但只带来很小成本收益，则可判定 64-80 已是当前 target 的 lookup-budget 平坦区，后续应换轴而不是继续沿 K 线性外推。"],"notes_to_memory":["截至 round 112，当前工作区真实 frontier 已包含兼容的 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 段：r107 0.42x/0.1010，r108 0.38x/0.1072，r109 0.34x/0.1147，r110 0.32x/0.1191，r111 0.30x/0.1228，r112 0.28x/0.1282。","r111→r112 已证明在 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 下继续压 deployment 预算仍能形成新的更靠左非支配点，因此再做一档 `K=64` 有明确的信息增量。","本轮不需要代码修改；现有 `shared_routed_expert_topk`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 接线已在历史轮次中完成并稳定生效。"],"reference_round":112,"self_review":"相对 r112 只改一个 env 参数 `K`，满足单变量原则。继续沿 shared+routed 主线而不是回到提示里较旧的 `lowrank_expert_topk` 摘要，是因为当前工作区的 `frontier.json` 与 round summaries 已明确显示 r107-r112 形成了更新、更强的兼容低成本 Pareto 段；基于真实最新历史，`K=64` 是对 deployment knee 的最直接下一问。如果本轮不能形成新非支配点，下一轮就应换轴或换 family。","summary":"以 r112 为 reference，继续沿已验证的 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 低成本前沿做一次单变量 deployment-side left shift：只改 `K=64`，测试这条直接兼容的 shared+routed 结构能否把 Pareto 段从约 0.28x 再推进到约 0.27x，同时维持约 0.13 量级的 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:6:{"event_id": "evt_1774003026916276680", "ts": 1774003026, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 1, "session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "topk", "family_stage": "mainline", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "topk", "family_stage": "mainline", "change_type": "param_only", "expected_win": "explore_unknown", "hypothesis": "Because the frontier is empty, the next highest-value move is to establish a trustworthy K=128 quality anchor with the simplest mainline architecture before rewarding smaller K or drawing conclusions about new families. Run a proxy topk baseline at K=128 with the default expansion and optimizer explicitly pinned so later rounds can measure real FVU gains against a stable reference."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:25:{"event_id": "evt_1774003292104195472", "ts": 1774003292, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 2, "session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "mixture_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "mixture_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "change_type": "param_only", "expected_win": "lower_fvu", "hypothesis": "A soft mixture-of-experts encoder may beat the current K=128 topk anchor by giving the encoder more routing expressivity without the hard-capacity bottlenecks of grouped routing. Test the existing mixture_topk family at the same K=128 and expansion factor as a quality-first proxy comparison."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:36:{"event_id": "evt_1774003417642049301", "ts": 1774003417, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 3, "session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "residual_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "residual_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "change_type": "param_only", "expected_win": "lower_fvu", "hypothesis": "A residual two-branch encoder may reduce FVU at K=128 by letting the second encoder pass target what the first branch misses, which is directly aligned with the reconstruction objective. Test residual_topk at the same K=128 anchor point as a quality-first architecture probe."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:47:{"event_id": "evt_1774003556174788177", "ts": 1774003556, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 4, "session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "factorized_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "factorized_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "change_type": "param_only", "expected_win": "lower_fvu", "hypothesis": "A factorized nonlinear encoder may lower FVU at K=128 by adding a hidden mixing stage before latent scoring, giving the encoder more expressive feature composition while keeping the fixed-K decode path unchanged. Test factorized_topk at the same K=128 anchor point as the next quality-first family."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:58:{"event_id": "evt_1774003727964115369", "ts": 1774003727, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 5, "session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "factorized_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "factorized_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "change_type": "edit_architecture", "expected_win": "lower_fvu", "hypothesis": "factorized_topk likely failed because its hidden mixer is too narrow and lossy; widening that stage and adding a gate should preserve more information before latent selection and materially improve FVU. Re-test factorized_topk at K=128 after this single architectural stabilization edit."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:70:{"event_id": "evt_1774003975921242936", "ts": 1774003975, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 6, "session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "factorized_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "factorized_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "change_type": "edit_architecture", "expected_win": "explore_unknown", "hypothesis": "The stabilized factorized_topk crash was caused by an implementation bug in the widened hidden-path projection, not by the architecture itself. Fix the hidden-to-latent projection and rerun the same K=128 factorized_topk stabilization pass to recover a valid quality signal."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:83:{"event_id": "evt_1774004278483460776", "ts": 1774004278, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 7, "session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "hybrid_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "hybrid_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "change_type": "edit_architecture", "expected_win": "lower_fvu", "hypothesis": "A hybrid encoder that preserves the strong linear topk path and adds a gated nonlinear residual to latent logits can improve quality without discarding the baseline behavior that already works. Test a new hybrid_topk family at K=128 as a quality-first architecture probe."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:107:{"event_id": "evt_1774004828636920780", "ts": 1774004828, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 8, "session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "hybrid_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "hybrid_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "change_type": "param_only", "expected_win": "lower_fvu", "hypothesis": "hybrid_topk has now beaten the K=128 full baseline, so the next quality-first move is to stabilize the same family with an optimizer better suited to its smooth nonlinear residual branch. Test hybrid_topk at K=128 with Adam to see whether denser adaptive updates improve FVU beyond the current full frontier."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:129:{"event_id": "evt_1774005272724533136", "ts": 1774005272, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 9, "session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "hybrid_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "hybrid_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "change_type": "param_only", "expected_win": "lower_fvu", "hypothesis": "hybrid_topk with Adam is now the strongest K=128 configuration, so the next quality-first move is to increase representational capacity rather than shrink K or chase cost. Test hybrid_topk at K=128 with Adam and expansion_factor=16 to see whether extra latent capacity can materially reduce FVU again."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:155:{"event_id": "evt_1774005871798638237", "ts": 1774005871, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 10, "session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "hybrid_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "hybrid_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "change_type": "edit_architecture", "expected_win": "lower_fvu", "hypothesis": "hybrid_topk may now be limited by using the nonlinear branch only as an additive correction; letting it multiplicatively modulate the linear logits should improve support shaping while preserving the strong baseline path. Re-test hybrid_topk at the best-known K=128, expansion_factor=8, optimizer=adam setting after this targeted hybrid-family stabilization edit."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:168:{"event_id": "evt_1774006272353974795", "ts": 1774006272, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 11, "session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "jumprelu", "family_stage": "prototype", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "jumprelu", "family_stage": "prototype", "change_type": "param_only", "expected_win": "explore_unknown", "hypothesis": "A thresholded sparse activation family may beat the current hybrid mainline by learning which latent logits should be suppressed before top-k selection rather than only reshaping logits with extra branches. Test jumprelu at K=128 with Adam as a fresh quality-first family probe."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:179:{"event_id": "evt_1774006524611947227", "ts": 1774006524, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 12, "session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "jumprelu", "family_stage": "stabilize", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0ad1-3a24-7583-a982-5e5d5ddd449d", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "jumprelu", "family_stage": "stabilize", "change_type": "param_only", "expected_win": "lower_fvu", "hypothesis": "jumprelu looks promising enough to deserve a family-specific stabilization pass, and its current default threshold initialization is likely too weak to realize the benefit of learned gating. Test jumprelu at K=128 with Adam using a higher initial threshold and smoother STE bandwidth so the encoder starts from a more selective regime."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:195:{"event_id": "evt_1774007334931658897", "ts": 1774007334, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 13, "session_id": "019d0b11-31f4-7670-b039-f512e33764f2", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "gated", "family_stage": "prototype", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0b11-31f4-7670-b039-f512e33764f2", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "gated", "family_stage": "prototype", "change_type": "param_only", "expected_win": "explore_unknown", "hypothesis": "A gated SAE may materially lower proxy FVU at K=128 by decoupling support selection from coefficient magnitude, letting one branch learn which features should fire while another learns how strongly they should reconstruct. After two flat jumprelu stabilization rounds and stalled hybrid local search, this is the cleanest untried quality-first family already supported by the execution layer."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:206:{"event_id": "evt_1774007665871599257", "ts": 1774007665, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 14, "session_id": "019d0b11-31f4-7670-b039-f512e33764f2", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "adaptive_threshold_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0b11-31f4-7670-b039-f512e33764f2", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "adaptive_threshold_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "change_type": "edit_architecture", "expected_win": "lower_fvu", "hypothesis": "The current best family may need cleaner support suppression rather than another additive or multiplicative residual path. An adaptive-threshold TopK encoder that keeps the proven linear logits as the anchor but learns an input-dependent nonnegative per-latent suppression term could reduce false activations at K=128 and materially improve FVU without abandoning the strong baseline initialization."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:219:{"event_id": "evt_1774008175240313688", "ts": 1774008175, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 15, "session_id": "019d0b11-31f4-7670-b039-f512e33764f2", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "hybrid_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0b11-31f4-7670-b039-f512e33764f2", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "hybrid_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "change_type": "param_only", "expected_win": "lower_fvu", "hypothesis": "Recent new families have all clustered far above the current hybrid full frontier, so the most credible next move is a training-dynamics pass on the one family that has actually improved full FVU. Adding a modest orthogonality penalty to hybrid_topk may reduce decoder interference between active features, sharpen the effective support at K=128, and improve reconstruction quality without changing the proven architecture."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:231:{"event_id": "evt_1774008554904332251", "ts": 1774008554, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 16, "session_id": "019d0b11-31f4-7670-b039-f512e33764f2", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "union_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0b11-31f4-7670-b039-f512e33764f2", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "union_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "change_type": "edit_architecture", "expected_win": "lower_fvu", "hypothesis": "The recent hybrid and adaptive-threshold results suggest the main failure mode is not lack of an anchor but how nonlinear information is injected into support selection. A union_topk encoder that keeps the baseline linear top-k proposal intact while letting a nonlinear branch propose an alternate candidate set, with final support chosen from the union rather than from perturbed logits, could lower FVU by adding complementary features without destabilizing the proven linear path."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:253:{"event_id": "evt_1774009493267281583", "ts": 1774009493, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 17, "session_id": "019d0b33-55ef-79a1-9de3-1374e06fc246", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "union_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0b33-55ef-79a1-9de3-1374e06fc246", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "union_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "change_type": "edit_sae_code", "expected_win": "lower_fvu", "hypothesis": "The union_topk prototype likely failed because its nonlinear branch proposed candidates from the same centered input as the linear branch, so it mostly duplicated baseline support. Conditioning the nonlinear proposer on the linear branch residual, widening that branch, and letting it over-propose candidates before the final global top-k should increase support complementarity at K=128 and lower proxy FVU."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:266:{"event_id": "evt_1774010152433720863", "ts": 1774010152, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 18, "session_id": "019d0b33-55ef-79a1-9de3-1374e06fc246", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "refined_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0b33-55ef-79a1-9de3-1374e06fc246", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "refined_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "change_type": "edit_sae_code", "expected_win": "lower_fvu", "hypothesis": "Recent architecture edits have mostly tried to improve support selection, yet multiple distinct families have converged to the same proxy FVU plateau under normal runtime. A stronger next bet is that support is not the main bottleneck at K=128; instead, the selected coefficients are too crude. A refined_topk family that keeps the proven linear top-k support but recomputes the chosen coefficients with a small per-example ridge solve against the decoder atoms could materially lower FVU by directly reducing reconstruction error on the selected support."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:278:{"event_id": "evt_1774010757838450345", "ts": 1774010757, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 19, "session_id": "019d0b33-55ef-79a1-9de3-1374e06fc246", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "refined_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0b33-55ef-79a1-9de3-1374e06fc246", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "refined_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "change_type": "edit_sae_code", "expected_win": "lower_fvu", "hypothesis": "The round-18 refined_topk crash was caused by a mixed-precision implementation bug in the ridge solve, not by evidence against the architecture. Running the small support-wise solve in float32 and casting the refined coefficients back to the model dtype should make the family trainable under bf16 autocast, allowing a valid proxy read on whether coefficient refitting can lower FVU at K=128."}}
research/history_archive/07_20260321_004359/timeline.jsonl:296:{"event_id": "evt_1774024942714990732", "ts": 1774024942, "event": "agent_action_received", "round": 20, "session_id": "019d0c1f-e2b9-7fd2-a6b4-ad914bfbd977", "tier": "proxy", "run_name": null, "family_name": "hybrid_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "status": null, "decision": null, "payload": {"session_id": "019d0c1f-e2b9-7fd2-a6b4-ad914bfbd977", "tier": "proxy", "family_name": "hybrid_topk", "family_stage": "stabilize", "change_type": "param_only", "expected_win": "explore_unknown", "hypothesis": "Crash recovery and policy both point to a narrow param-only move: keep the current best working proxy configuration in hybrid_topk fixed and test whether it remains viable when K is reduced from 128 to 64. This is the required first step in K exploration, and it isolates the effect of sparsity level without confounding architecture or optimizer changes."}}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0077.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e(h(x))}(h(x))} α_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低维投影，e(h(x)) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{b_{e,i}} 是各 expert 的静态子库原子。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“共享投影 -> router 选单个静态 expert 子库 -> expert 内 local top-k -> 静态库查表加权求和”；静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `factorized_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`factorized_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。相对 r74 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变，直接回答当前高信息量结构问题：在 routed-only sparse-capacity 已连续给出正信号、而 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的容量扩展未继续改善后，把 shared low-rank basis 放进 expert 内部 head，而不是继续只堆 routed-only 容量，是否能在不拉长 active path 的前提下形成新的低到中成本 Pareto 段。若当前瓶颈已从总子库容量转向 scorer 质量与共享结构建模，则这次 matched architecture probe 应在约同一成本带内优于 r74。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 在近同成本下明显优于 r74，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只显式设置 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，确认 shared basis 宽度是否是该结构的主控制旋钮。","如果它接近但不明显优于 r74，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=128`，判断这条结构是否更适合更靠左的低成本段。","如果它明显弱于 r74，则归档当前 `factorized_expert_topk` 原型，后续把低成本结构预算转回 `expert_topk` 容量线或 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 trunk/stage 轴。"],"notes_to_memory":["`factorized_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和，兼容性为扩展兼容。","本轮是对 r74 的严格 matched architecture probe：保持 `K=160 / NUM_EXPERTS=128 / EF=1 / adam / 8e-4` 不变，只切换到 `factorized_expert_topk`，直接测试 expert-internal low-rank / shared-basis expert routing 是否比 routed-only 更值得继续。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 代码路径估算，`factorized_expert_topk K=160 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=128` 的总成本约在 0.49x 附近，仍处于当前要补的低到中成本带内，并显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","r71/r72 的负结果只覆盖较小容量 recipe，不能替代在当前 `NUM_EXPERTS=128` sparse-capacity recipe 下的 fresh matched validation。"],"reference_round":74,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r74 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这比继续在 `expert_topk` 上做第四次纯容量外推或回到旧 family 的 K/LR 邻域更符合当前阶段的结构扩展优先级，因为 routed-only 已给出连续容量正信号，而 r76 说明三段式 family 的低成本瓶颈不主要在继续加 expert 容量；现在更值得回答的是 shared-basis expert routing 是否能在相近成本下提供新的结构收益。主要风险是 `factorized_expert_topk` 的旧原型在较小容量下曾给出负信号，但那不足以否定当前更强 sparse-capacity recipe 下的 matched probe。","summary":"做一轮严格 matched 的 `factorized_expert_topk` 架构探针：以 r74 为参考，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，其余 `K=160, NUM_EXPERTS=128, EF=1, adam, lr=8e-4` 全部保持不变。目标不是继续细扫 routed-only 容量线，而是直接判定 `expert-internal low-rank / shared-basis expert routing` 在当前低到中成本带是否值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0099.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":98,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"112"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈S_2(r_1)} γ_j(x) c_j，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r 是共享 low-rank trunk，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，r_1 = x - t(x) - Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单个静态 expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 属于扩展兼容；`expert_topk` 属于直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 属于不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：r98 已经证明在 `K=96, TRUNK_RANK=40, NUM_EXPERTS=32` 的已压缩 recipe 上，residual cleanup 仍然非常有价值，FVU 从 matched `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 0.1305 明显压到 0.1030；因此当前最有信息量的问题不再是“要不要 residual”，而是该三段式结构在中等 deployment budget 下的最优 K 是否高于 96。相对 r98 仅将 `K: 96 -> 112`，如果这条 family 的主要收益不是偶然来自低 K 正则化，而是真的还受 lookup budget 限制，那么 FVU 应进一步低于 0.1030，并在约 total_cost=0.68x（selection≈0.53x，deployment≈0.15x）的可行带内形成更强的中低成本质量锚点。","summary":"r98 已经把 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 在压缩 recipe 上打成强正信号，因此本轮不再回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 做局部边界补点，也不切去别的 family。以 r98 为 reference，只改 `K=112`，直接回答 residual cleanup 这条三段式主线在当前 target 上是否还受 deployment budget 限制，以及 `K=96` 是否已经低于它的最佳工作点。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r98 只改 `K`。这不是 old-family 的盲目 K 轴微调，而是在刚得到强阳性结构证据后，对同一 family 做第一次 deploy-budget 扩展验证。选择 `112` 而不是直接跳到 `128`，是为了先用中间点判断质量增益斜率，避免过早把预算推到更高成本带。主要风险是 r98 的强结果已经接近这条 family 在当前压缩 recipe 下的饱和点，导致 `K=112` 只带来很小改进；但这同样有价值，因为它能告诉我们后续是否值得继续给 residual cleanup 增配 lookup 预算。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r98 (`lowrank_expert_residual K=96 TRUNK_RANK=40 NUM_EXPERTS=32`) 把 matched `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 0.1305 明显压到 0.1030，说明 residual cleanup 在当前 target 上不是边缘组件，而是强结构增益。","当前最值得回答的问题已经从“residual 是否必要”转为“这条三段式结构的最佳 deployment budget 在哪里”；因此下一步优先沿 `K` 做一次单变量扩展。","按当前 fresh cost 估算，`lowrank_expert_residual K=112 TRUNK_RANK=40 NUM_EXPERTS=32 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 的 total_cost 约 0.68x，仍处于允许的 0.3x-0.8x 结构对照带且远低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算。","当前不应把 `expert_topk ACTIVE_EXPERTS>1` 或 `factorized_expert_topk` 的负信号外推到 future shared+routed-expert 新 family；但在现有 family 仍有高信息量单变量问题时，也不应提前切去 code-edit。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=112` 明显优于 r98，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=128`，完成这条 `lowrank_expert_residual` deployment knee 的上沿定位。","如果 `K=112` 只小幅优于或基本持平于 r98，则可初步判定当前压缩 recipe 的最佳 K 已接近 96-112；下一轮应改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，区分收益更依赖 expert 段还是 residual cleanup 段。","如果 `K=112` 意外明显劣化，则说明 r98 的强点更可能来自更强的低-K 正则化而非 lookup 不足；下一轮应停止沿 K 上探，转向同 family 的预算重分配验证或准备 shared+routed-expert 新原型。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0003.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"继续使用直接兼容 family `topk`，最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i in S(x)} α_i(x) b_i`。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时，`{b_i}` 仍是单个静态向量库；在线仅做 top-k 选择、系数计算、查表 `W b_i`、加权求和，并可保持现有选择性补偿接口不变。本轮相对 r1 仅将 `K` 从 64 调到 48，回答当前主线在 `<0.5x` 低成本区间内，是否存在比 `K=32` 和 `K=64` 更优的中间 Pareto 点。","summary":"兼容性判断：`topk` 为直接兼容。当前 `<0.5x` 区域只有 `K=32` 与 `K=64` 两个点，且 `K=32` 明显牺牲 FVU、`K=64` 是当前质量最好点；在不改变 encoder 成本的前提下，测试中间 `K=48` 能最直接补足前沿曲率信息。按当前 proxy，selection 仍约 `0.25x`，deployment 约 `0.05x`，combined total_cost 约 `0.30x`，稳定落在低成本区且低于 `K=64` 的 `0.31x`。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"遵守单变量原则，基于 `reference_round=1` 仅修改 `K`。这轮的目标不是切换 family，而是在已建立的主线局部槽位里补一个中间 cost anchor，确认 low-cost frontier 的形状；如果 `K=48` 不能提供更优权衡，再更有根据地转向新 family 或高优先级未验证方向。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"48"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`topk` 当前 target 已形成两个低成本 anchor：`K=32` 与 `K=64`；需要中间点判断 frontier 曲率。","`K=48` 预估 total_cost 约 `0.30x`，仍在 `<0.5x` 低成本区，可直接检验 `topk` 在当前 hookpoint 的 K-FVU 平滑性。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=48` 接近 `K=64` 的 FVU，则可将其作为更优低成本主线点。","如果 `K=48` 仍明显接近 `K=32` 的退化，则说明当前 `topk` 在低 K 区间质量下降较陡，下一轮应优先切到其他兼容 family 做同成本对照。"],"reference_round":1}
