research/history/logs/agent_action_0024.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e*(x)}(x)} α_i(x) b_{e*(x),i}，其中 e*(x) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert 子库，S_{e*(x)}(x) 是该静态子库内的局部 top-k 支持集。在线导出时只需执行“router 选 1 个静态 expert 子库 + 在该子库内查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”，仍然是静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此兼容性判断为扩展兼容。主假设：在当前 target 上，已完成注册与 smoke 修复后的 `expert_topk` 原型，能在 K=64、EF=1 的超低成本区给出比现有 0.31x-0.33x frontier 更有信息量的首个 MoE-like 信号。","summary":"不再改实现，直接重跑已修复的 `expert_topk` prototype。相对 r10 的完整配置只改一个 env 参数：`ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk`，保持 `K=64`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变，先拿到这个新 family 在当前 target 的首个有效训练结果。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"当前最重要的是把刚修通注册链的 MoE-like family 真正跑出第一批信号，而不是继续对旧 family 做局部微调。风险是 prototype 虽然 parse/dispatch/forward/backward 已通过，但真实训练质量可能很弱；不过这正是当前阶段需要回答的结构问题。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"expert_topk"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：`expert_topk` 为扩展兼容；最终形式是单激活 expert 子库上的有限加权和，可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable。","reference_round 选 r10，是因为它提供了当前 target 上 `K=64, EF=1, adam, LR=8e-4` 的低成本锚点；本轮只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，满足 param_only 单变量规则。","`expert_topk` 的注册链与 smoke 已修复完成，本轮目标是获取首个真实训练结果，而不是继续修改实现。","按 prototype 的 smoke 成本估计，selection 和 deployment 都处于超低成本区，值得先确认其真实 FVU 是否有继续探索价值。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `expert_topk` 在超低成本区给出可接受的 FVU，下一轮再围绕同一 family 的 `K` 做单变量扩展，测其局部 Pareto 斜率。","如果结果明显差于已有低成本点，则说明当前固定 4-expert/1-active prototype 不足以成立，下一轮再决定是修结构还是转向其他兼容 family。"],"reference_round":10}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0095.json:22:    "expected_win": "lower_cost",
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0042.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"After multiple rounds dominated by gated-local tuning and unresolved crash recovery, the most informative next move is to advance an already-incubating alternate family rather than spend another round near the current gated anchor. A clean `topk` K=128 proxy run under the current strongest gated training regime tests whether simpler support selection benefits more from the improved optimizer and regularization settings than it did in earlier comparisons.","summary":"Run a fresh `topk` K=128 proxy mainline comparison using the current strongest signum gated regime to see whether the improved training setup materially closes the quality gap for the incubating top-k family.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline_comparison","self_review":"This is a better use of the round than another gated-adjacent parameter tweak because the search has gone too long without advancing a distinct family, and `topk` already has working runs that can cleanly absorb the stronger regime. The main risk is that top-k remains well behind gated on FVU, but that negative result is still useful because it would retire a lingering incumbent alternative and narrow future exploration toward more novel architectures.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.01"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["The search has now gone eight rounds without advancing a new family, so architecture exploration should take priority over more local gated tuning.","`topk` remains incubating with older K=128 proxy evidence taken under weaker regimes, so it deserves one clean comparison against the current strongest training setup before being retired or promoted.","This round keeps the regime fixed to the current gated anchor settings and changes only architecture, giving a direct read on whether simpler global top-k selection benefits from the newer training recipe."],"next_hypotheses":["If `topk` improves materially over its prior proxy results and is competitive with gated at K=128, promote it to full and begin family-specific stabilization from this stronger anchor.","If `topk` runs normally but remains clearly worse than gated, retire it from near-term focus and move to a more expressive new architecture family.","If `topk` is still worse on FVU but shows meaningfully better runtime or memory behavior, keep it alive as a cost-quality tradeoff family rather than a main quality contender."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0100.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":99,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈S_2(r_1)} γ_j(x) c_j，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r 是共享 low-rank trunk，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，r_1 = x - t(x) - Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单个静态 expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 属于扩展兼容；`expert_topk` 属于直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 属于不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：r98 在 `K=96`、r99 在 `K=112` 上连续给出清晰正斜率，说明当前压缩版三段式结构仍然受 deployment lookup budget 限制，而不是已经在 `K=96` 附近饱和。相对 r99 仅将 `K: 112 -> 128`，在保持 `TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变时，如果这条 family 的收益继续随 K 增长，那么 FVU 应进一步低于 r99 的 0.0973，并完成当前 `lowrank_expert_residual` deployment knee 的上沿定位。","summary":"r98 和 r99 已经把压缩版 `lowrank_expert_residual` 从 `K=96` 推到 `K=112` 且持续改善，因此本轮不切 family，也不回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 或 routed-only 方向。以 r99 为 reference，只改 `K=128`，直接回答这条三段式主线在当前 recipe 下的 deployment budget 是否仍有显著质量收益，并完成 `K=96-128` 的上沿定位。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r99 只改 `K`。这不是旧 family 的盲目 K 轴细扫，而是在连续两轮正信号后，对当前最有希望的中低成本三段式主线做一次必要的上沿确认。选择 `128` 而不是先改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，是因为当前最清楚的未决问题仍是 lookup budget 斜率是否继续存在；若 r99 已接近饱和，这轮会直接给出答案。主要风险是 FVU 改善很小而成本继续上升，但这同样有价值，因为它会告诉我们后续该把预算转向预算重分配或新 family，而不是继续堆 K。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r98 (`lowrank_expert_residual K=96 TRUNK_RANK=40 NUM_EXPERTS=32`) 到 r99 (`K=112`) 给出连续正斜率，说明当前压缩版三段式结构的收益不只来自 residual 是否存在，也仍受 deployment budget 影响。","当前最有信息量的问题是 `lowrank_expert_residual` 在这套压缩 recipe 下的 K-knee 上沿，而不是继续回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 做局部补点。","按当前 fresh cost 估算，`lowrank_expert_residual K=128 TRUNK_RANK=40 NUM_EXPERTS=32 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算，并处于允许的中低成本结构对照带。","当前不要把 `expert_topk ACTIVE_EXPERTS>1` 的负信号外推到 future shared+routed-expert family；但在现有 family 仍有清晰单变量正斜率时，也不应提前切去 code-edit。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=128` 继续明显优于 r99，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，测试在已确认更高 K 有效后，expert 段与 residual 段的最优预算分配。","如果 `K=128` 只带来极小改善，则说明这条 family 在当前压缩 recipe 下的 deployment knee 已接近 `K=112`；下一轮应停止继续堆 K，转而测试 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或准备 shared+routed-expert 新 family。","如果 `K=128` 意外退化，则说明 r98-r99 的收益更可能来自较低 K 正则化或训练噪声；下一轮应回到 `K=112`，并优先做同 family 的预算重分配验证而不是继续上探。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0114.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","reference_round":113,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"1"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}。其中 shared 子库 B^sh 与 routed expert 子库 {B_e} 都是静态向量库，在线侧只做轻量 router 选择少量 routed experts，然后执行 shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权求和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 继续明确排除。r107-r113 已经证明 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 在 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 下形成了真实低成本 Pareto 段，并在 r113 达到约 0.27x / FVU 0.1350。唯一主假设：在 `K=64, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64` 固定时，把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，会把 selection cost 从约 0.20x 降到约 0.14x、total_cost 从约 0.27x 左移到约 0.20x，同时若 FVU 仍明显优于当前直接兼容 cost anchor `expert_topk K=128` 的 0.3149，则可以回答“shared+routed 的低成本收益是否真的需要双 routed experts”，并在更低成本带建立新的结构性 anchor。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 在约 0.20x total_cost 下仍把 FVU 压到约 0.20 或更低，则下一轮应以本轮为 reference，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 或 `K`，继续细化这条更便宜的 shared+routed 子线。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 明显退化而劣于 r113 太多，则说明当前 shared+routed 前沿的质量确实依赖双 routed experts；下一轮不应继续压 active path，而应回到 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 主线换轴。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 与 r113 接近但成本显著更低，则可判定当前 target 上 shared+routed 的主要收益来自 shared+routed 分解本身，而不完全来自多 routed experts。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 selection cost 自检显示：`shared_routed_expert_topk K=64 NUM_EXPERTS=64 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 的 selection ratio 约 0.14x、deployment ratio 约 0.06x、combined ratio 约 0.20x；对应 r113 baseline (`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`) 为约 0.27x。","r107-r113 已经把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 的 shared+routed 低成本线推到 0.42x→0.27x；当前最有信息量的问题不再是继续线性降 K，而是这条线在更低 encoder 成本下是否仍成立。","本轮不需要代码修改；`ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 与 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 wiring 已在历史轮次中稳定生效。"],"self_review":"相对 r113 只改一个 env 参数 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`，满足单变量原则。之所以不继续沿 `K` 轴外推，是因为 r112→r113 已经连续两轮回答 deployment knee，并且都形成了新非支配点；当前更高信息量的是切换到 active-path 轴，直接比较当前 low-cost shared+routed 前沿对双 routed experts 的依赖程度。该点仍远低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","summary":"以 r113 为 reference，保持 `shared_routed_expert_topk`、`K=64`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 不变，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，测试 shared+routed 在约 0.20x total_cost 下是否仍能显著优于旧 `expert_topk` 低成本锚点，并回答当前低成本收益是否真的依赖双 routed experts。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0036.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":35,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"160"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，并只在该子库内做 local top-k 得到 α_{e,i}(x)。因此它可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。相对 r35 仅改 K: 128 -> 160，回答一个结构问题：在 lowrank+expert 这个新 family 中，适度增加 sparse residual 容量后，FVU 是否会比 plain expert_topk 的同成本邻域下降更快，从而证明 trunk+expert 组合值得继续推进。","summary":"继续验证新 family `lowrank_expert_topk`，不回到 old-family 微调。以 r35 为参考只提高 `K` 到 160，在仍低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x 总成本的前提下，检查 lowrank trunk + local expert residual 是否开始形成比 `expert_topk` 更有竞争力的中低成本 Pareto 斜率。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束；相对 r35 仅修改 `K`。这是对刚引入的新结构做最小必要的第二个锚点，而不是回到 plain selector 的局部扫点。按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 的 total_cost 约 0.69x，仍在预算内，且能直接回答该 family 是否具有继续扩展价值。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_topk K=160` 相对 r35 出现清晰 FVU 改善且斜率优于 `expert_topk`，下一轮仍保持 family 不变，只改 `K` 到 192，确认该 family 在 0.8x 附近是否继续沿 Pareto 前进。","如果 `K=160` 仍无明显收益，则应停止继续打磨该两段式原型，优先转向 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`，而不是退回 plain `topk/jumprelu/factorized_topk`。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","当前已完成新 family 首轮验证；Round 36 只补第二个 K 锚点，目标是判断 lowrank+expert 的 FVU-cost 斜率，而不是刷新全局最低 FVU。","成本估算：`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 约为 total 0.69x（selection 0.22x + deployment 0.47x），显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x。","若该点仍弱，应把后续结构预算转向三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`。"],"touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0056.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"The EF=32 `factorized_topk` variant improved with more capacity, but lowering LR regressed sharply, so the family now looks more sensitive to support-shaping regularization than to further optimizer slowdown. The cleanest remaining single-variable stabilization check is to raise `AUXK_ALPHA` on the best factorized recipe (EF=32, LR=1.6e-3) and test whether stronger dead-feature recovery improves utilization enough to recover proxy FVU.","summary":"Run a `factorized_topk` proxy stabilization pass at `EXPANSION_FACTOR=32`, `K=128`, `LR=1.6e-3`, and `AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125` to test whether stronger aux-k regularization improves the best current factorized setup.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This stays in exploitation mode on the only active incubating family, changes exactly one variable, and follows the remaining obvious stabilization axis after the LR regression. The main risk is that aux-k also fails to help, but that outcome would be useful evidence that the family is near exhaustion and ready to archive.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"32"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`factorized_topk` at EF=32 improved over EF=16, but reducing LR from 1.6e-3 to 8e-4 regressed from proxy FVU 0.3188326023519039 to 0.3457685150206089, so lower LR is not the right stabilization direction.","The best current factorized recipe remains EF=32, LR=1.6e-3, AUXK_ALPHA=0.01 at K=128.","This round tests the remaining obvious non-architectural stabilizer on that best recipe: stronger aux-k pressure for feature recovery and usage balance."],"next_hypotheses":["If higher AUXK improves `factorized_topk`, continue with one final nearby AUXK check or consider promotion pressure only if the gain is substantial.","If higher AUXK does not help, archive `factorized_topk` as exhausted under the current execution layer and return to a different search direction.","If AUXK improves quality but hurts runtime or stability, consider a small code/performance follow-up only if the quality gain is meaningful."],"primary_variable":"other_param"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0048.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","reference_round":42,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r。也就是先用静态 low-rank trunk 向量库 U={u_r} 重构平滑主干，再对残差用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 B_e={b_{e,i}} 并做局部 sparse 选择；因此它仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。Round 43 的 blocker 不是结构质量，而是运行时观测路径错误：`from sparsify import SparseCoder` 直接实例化时没有尊重 `cfg.architecture`，导致 policy behavioral-diff 实际在比较 topk vs topk，误把 `lowrank_expert_topk` 判成与 topk 完全相同。本轮只修复 `sparsify/` 内的构造分发，使直接构造 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 时也能按 `cfg.architecture` 返回正确 family，然后按 r43 的原设计重跑相对 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的低成本 probe，验证这条 `lowrank + expert` 结构在约 0.44x total_cost 下是否真能形成新的 Pareto 段。","summary":"当前优先级最高的不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 上做第四个低成本邻域点，而是先修掉 Round 43 暴露出的系统 blocker：`lowrank_expert_topk` 被 policy 的 behavioral diff 误拦。修复 `SparseCoder` 的直接构造分发后，按原计划重跑 r43 的 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 低成本验证，可以在不引入新 tunable 的前提下重新回答 `lowrank + expert` 这条高优先级结构线是否值得继续。","self_review":"满足当前阶段的运行时优先级：先修 blocker，再做结构比较。代码改动限制在 `sparsify/`，不碰 evaluation semantics，也不改 AutoResearch/launcher；真正实验配置相对 r42 仍只改一个 env 参数 `TRUNK_RANK=128`。这次 repair 的目标不是改训练语义，而是让公共构造入口与 `cfg.architecture` 一致，避免再次把 policy 误判当成结构结论。风险是修复后 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的真实低成本效果可能仍然一般；但那时才能把它当成结构证据，而不是观测链路伪影。","touched_files":["sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 43 的 `policy_reject` 根因是 exported `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 直接构造时未按 `cfg.architecture` 分发，behavioral diff 实际比较成了 topk vs topk。","`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容，不是动态字典。","按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=192 EF=1 TRUNK_RANK=128` 的 total_cost 约为 0.44x，修复 blocker 后应优先拿到这个点的真实 FVU，再决定该 family 是否继续。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果修复后 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的真实结果在约 0.44x 成本下明显优于当前 `<0.5x` anchor，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=64`，测试 lowrank+expert 是否还能继续向左延伸。","如果修复后该点仍明显弱于 `jumprelu`/`lowrank_expert_residual` 的低成本点，则应归档 `lowrank_expert_topk`，把预算转回其他高优先级结构方向。","如果修复后仍有新的 runtime/policy blocker，则下一轮继续只处理新 blocker，不把结果当成架构质量结论。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0086.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{e∈E(x-t(x))} Σ_{i∈S_e(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，|E(x-t(x))|=ACTIVE_EXPERTS。在线导出仍是“trunk 查表 + 少量静态 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。相对 r82 仅新增 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`、`K=128`、`TRUNK_RANK=64`、`NUM_EXPERTS=16`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 及其余训练配方不变时，先验证最近修复后的 multi-expert active path 是否能稳定进入真实训练链路，并在不超过当前预算的前提下给出比单 expert 路由更好的重构。按当前成本模型估算，该点约为 encoder 0.54x、deployment 0.19x、total 0.72x，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","summary":"Round 86 先做工程修复后的最小健康验证，不新开 family，也不改 recipe。以 r82 为 reference，只加 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`，直接确认最近修好的 `lowrank_expert_topk` 多 expert 路由在真实训练中不再 crash，且 `round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 都真实记录 `active_experts=2`。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r82 只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`。这轮的首要目标是排除最近两轮 crash 是否来自新实现写坏了，而不是追求 frontier 立刻改进；因此不切 family、不动 optimizer/LR/loss/preprocess。主要风险是 active path 从 1 个 expert 增到 2 个后 encoder 成本明显抬升，如果 FVU 改善不足，这条路线应尽快止损。另一个关键风险是参数虽被允许 override，但若未真实进入 round config 与 checkpoint config，这轮结果必须判无效。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"2"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是工程修复后的最小真实训练验证，不是新的结构结论轮；成功标准首先是训练链路恢复稳定并确认 `active_experts=2` 已真实持久化。","`lowrank_expert_topk` 在 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 下的 LUTurbo 形式仍是静态 trunk 库加少量静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","如果 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 或 checkpoint `config.json` 中缺少 `active_experts=2`，则本轮结果无效，不应拿 FVU 驱动后续决策。","按当前 1024x4096 成本 proxy，`lowrank_expert_topk K=128 TRUNK_RANK=64 NUM_EXPERTS=16 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 EF=1` 约 total 0.72x，属于允许的中成本结构性验证点。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果本轮稳定完成且 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 明确优于 r82，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=32`，测试“更大总容量 + 2 expert active path”是否形成新的 Pareto 段。","如果本轮稳定完成但改善很弱或退化，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改回 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 或提高到 `3`，明确当前 target 的最佳 active-expert 数，而不是继续混扫旧轴。","如果本轮再次 crash，则优先按 crash 栈定位实现问题；不要把结果解释成架构质量结论，也不要转去新 family。"],"reference_round":82}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0101.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_routed_expert_topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"HOOKPOINTS","value":"layers.[3].self_attn.q_proj"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"8e-4"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"1"},{"key":"NUM_EXPERTS","value":"32"},{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"1"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 B^sh 是始终激活的静态 shared 子库，E(x) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 routed experts，所有 b 都来自静态向量库，在线侧可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权和”流水线，因此兼容性判断为直接兼容。唯一主假设：相对已经给出负信号的 routed-only multi-expert active path，一个 always-on shared expert 能在保持 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1 短激活路径的同时补足通用容量，在约 total_cost=0.63x（selection≈0.51x, deployment≈0.12x）的中低成本带形成比 routed-only `expert_topk` 更强的新结构性 anchor。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该原型有效，下一步优先加 low-rank trunk，验证 `lowrank + shared+routed expert` 是否能把 total_cost 拉回 <0.5x。","如果该原型无明显收益，说明共享容量本身不足以替代 trunk/residual，后续应把 shared+routed 只作为 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的附加分支而不是独立主线。"],"notes_to_memory":["已在 `sparsify/` 新增最小异构 MoE family `shared_routed_expert_topk`：1 个 always-on shared expert + 少量 routed experts。","本地 smoke 已通过：`shared_routed_expert_topk`, d_in=1024, K=128, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=32；forward/backward 正常。","同一 smoke 配方下 fresh cost 估计为 selection 0.51x、deployment 0.12x、total 0.63x，满足 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":null,"self_review":"实现范围保持在 `sparsify/`，没有引入新 tunable 或执行层改动。当前原型把 shared expert 数固定为 1，先回答“shared+routed 是否值得继续”这个结构问题，而不是一次性扩大搜索维度。","summary":"补上了当前缺失的 shared+routed hetero-MoE 最小原型，并给出首轮全量训练配方用于验证它能否在 0.3x-0.8x total_cost 带形成新的兼容 Pareto anchor。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0040_repair_1.json:6:  "expected_win": "explore_unknown",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0068.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_e Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 e(x) 由轻量 router 选出单个 expert，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库。在线侧可直接导出为 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“router 选静态子库 + 子库内查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判断为直接兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r51 仅把 NUM_EXPERTS 从 16 提到 32，在保持 ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk、K=192、EF=1、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1 不变时，如果当前低成本带里纯 MoE-like routed sublibrary 仍有未吃满的静态容量收益，那么不带 trunk 的更大 expert 总容量应在仍可接受的 total_cost 下继续压低 FVU，并回答 routed-only 方向是否值得继续作为独立低成本前沿推进。","summary":"r67 已经对 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的继续扩容给出负信号，说明“更大 routed capacity + trunk”这条线当前不值得继续加码。本轮转向更干净的直接兼容 MoE-like 探针：相对 r51 只增大 `expert_topk` 的 `NUM_EXPERTS`，用不含 trunk 的 routed-only 结构回答容量收益是否仍成立。按当前代码路径成本估算，`expert_topk K=192 NUM_EXPERTS=32 EF=1` 约在 0.45x total_cost，仍落在本轮优先关注的低成本带。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r51 只改 `NUM_EXPERTS`。该 family 属于 LUTurbo 直接兼容 family，不触碰不兼容方向，也不需要新增 tunable 参数接线。选择这一步而不是继续细扫 `lowrank_expert_residual`，是因为当前阶段更需要回答纯 routed MoE-like 子库在低成本带是否还能形成独立 Pareto 段；主要风险是更大 expert 容量也可能带来与 r67 类似的吞吐回退，或说明容量并非当前瓶颈。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"NUM_EXPERTS","value":"32"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`expert_topk` 的最终形式仍是静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和，兼容性为直接兼容。","r67 对 `lowrank_expert_topk NUM_EXPERTS=64` 的负结果更像是在否定“trunk+更大 routed capacity”的继续扩容，而不是完全否定 routed-only MoE-like 方向。","本轮是对 `expert_topk` true sparse-capacity mode 的继续验证：保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 与 `K=192` 不变，只放大总静态 expert 容量。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=32` 明显优于 r51，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=160` 或 `128`，测试这条 routed-only 前沿能否进一步向左延伸。","如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=32` 改善很弱或再次出现明显吞吐回退，则可较清晰判定纯 routed sublibrary 扩容在当前 target 上已接近饱和，后续预算应更多回到 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或其他带 residual cleanup 的结构。","如果结果异常，先核对 round*.config.json 与 checkpoint config.json 中 `num_experts=32` 已真实生效，再决定是否把该轮当作结构证据。"],"reference_round":51}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0057.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Five rounds of factorized-topk stabilization failed to approach the gated frontier, so that direction is now effectively exhausted rather than merely under-tuned. The next mandatory informative move is a fundamentally different architecture family: a `residual_topk` SAE that spends the same total K budget across two sequential sparse stages, letting a second sparse pass model the first-pass residual instead of forcing one flat support set to capture everything at once.","summary":"Add a `residual_topk` prototype in `sparsify/` and run a K=128 proxy comparison under the current best signum regime to test whether two-stage sparse residual coding can beat flat top-k-style encoders.","change_type":"edit_sae_code","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"residual_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This satisfies the runtime mandate to stop minor parameter tweaks and switch to a genuinely different architecture approach after repeated stagnation. The main risk is implementation complexity or slow runtime, but a minimal two-stage prototype is still the cleanest next discriminator because it changes the coding mechanism itself rather than repeating another local sweep.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"residual_topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.01"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["`factorized_topk` now appears near-exhausted: EF=32 improved modestly over EF=16, but lower LR regressed and higher AUXK was effectively flat versus the best factorized result.","Severe stagnation rules out another minor parameter tweak; the next round must test a genuinely different sparse-coding mechanism.","`residual_topk` is intended as a two-stage sparse residual encoder that preserves comparable evaluation semantics while changing how the K budget is allocated internally."],"next_hypotheses":["If `residual_topk` runs and materially improves proxy FVU, keep the family alive and stabilize its internal K split next.","If it runs cleanly but is clearly worse than gated and not better than factorized-topk, archive it quickly and move to another architecture family.","If quality looks promising but runtime is poor, follow with a focused performance/code-fix round instead of discarding the family."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0046.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","reference_round":45,"env_overrides":[{"key":"STAGE1_RATIO","value":"0.25"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再路由到单个静态 expert 子库做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差做全局 sparse cleanup，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路。兼容性判定：`lowrank_expert_residual` 为扩展兼容。本轮相对 r45 仅改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`，主假设是在 `K=160, TRUNK_RANK=16` 的低成本配置下，默认 50/50 的两段 sparse 预算分配并不合适；由于 stage1 只覆盖单个 expert 子库，而 stage2 是全局 residual cleanup，把更多 K 留给 stage2 有机会在几乎相同 total_cost≈0.49x 下显著回收 r45 损失的质量。","summary":"r45 表明把 `lowrank_expert_residual` 直接压到 `K=160` 后，默认两段各分一半 sparse budget 会把 FVU 从 r44 的 0.13399 拉坏到 0.14361。下一步最有信息量的动作不是继续改 K 或回跳高成本，而是在同一低成本点上只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，测试低成本失真究竟来自总 sparse budget 不足，还是来自 expert 段与 global residual 段的预算分配失衡。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r45 只修改 `STAGE1_RATIO`。这轮保持 `K=160` 与 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 不变，因此 total_cost 基本不变，归因非常清晰；如果质量明显回升，就说明当前低成本失败主要是预算分配问题，而不是 `lowrank + expert + residual` 结构本身已经失效。风险是 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 属于较强干预，若 FVU 仍无改善，下一轮应再试更温和的配比，而不是立即否定该 family。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是 trunk 静态库 + expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。","在 `K=160, TRUNK_RANK=16` 下，调整 `STAGE1_RATIO` 不改变总 K，因此对 total_cost 基本无影响；它主要测试 expert 局部修正与全局 residual cleanup 的预算分配。","r44 到 r45 的退化提示：当前低成本点的主要问题可能不是总成本过低，而是默认 50/50 的 staged sparse allocation 不合适。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 能把 FVU 拉回到接近或优于 r44 的 0.13399，则下一轮继续同 family，只改 `K=168`，测试改良预算分配后是否能在约 0.50x 附近形成更稳的 Pareto 点。","如果 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 改善有限，则下一轮保持 r45 低成本配置，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.375`，测试是否存在更温和的折中点。","如果低成本区对 `STAGE1_RATIO` 也不敏感，则说明这条 family 在 `<0.5x` 带可能接近结构极限，之后应把更多预算转回其他高优先级结构方向。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0049.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","reference_round":42,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r。也就是先用静态 low-rank trunk 向量库 U={u_r} 重构平滑主干，再对残差用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 B_e={b_{e,i}} 并做局部 sparse 选择；因此它仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。r48 已明确表明当前 blocker 仍然是运行时构造路径：policy behavioral diff 通过 `from sparsify import SparseCoder` 直接实例化时，`cfg.architecture=lowrank_expert_topk` 仍未生效，导致比较结果依旧变成 topk vs topk。本轮主任务是继续修复 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` 中的直接构造分发，让 `SparseCoder(1024, SparseCoderConfig(architecture='lowrank_expert_topk', ...))` 真正返回对应 family，然后按 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的原计划重跑，拿到这条 `lowrank + expert` 结构在约 0.44x total_cost 下的首个有效点。","summary":"Round 48 证明 blocker 还没有消除：`lowrank_expert_topk` 再次在 behavioral diff 阶段被误拦，而且这次 round summary 显示并没有真正落地代码补丁。当前优先级最高的是继续做最小 repair，而不是回到 `lowrank_expert_residual` 再打磨一个低成本邻域点；先把 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 的分发修通，再重跑相对 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的低成本 probe，才能把 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的成败当成结构证据。","self_review":"满足当前阶段的运行时优先级：先消除重复 blocker，再做架构比较。代码改动范围仍只限 `sparsify/`，不改 evaluation semantics，也不改 AutoResearch/launcher；实验配置相对 r42 仍只改一个 env 参数 `TRUNK_RANK=128`。这次 repair 需要按架构集成 checklist 做完整验证：修复直接构造分发、用完全相同的 `architecture=lowrank_expert_topk, K=192, EF=1` 做 instantiate/forward/backward smoke，并确认 behavioral diff 不再把它判成 topk。风险是修复后该 family 的真实效果可能仍不强；但那时才是有效结构结论。","touched_files":["sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["r48 之后可以确认：当前 blocker 仍是 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 直接构造路径没有正确尊重 `cfg.architecture`，而不是 `lowrank_expert_topk` 本身的结构质量。","`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是静态 trunk 库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。","按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=192 EF=1 TRUNK_RANK=128` 的 total_cost 约为 0.44x；修复 blocker 后应优先获得这个点的真实 FVU。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 repair 后 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的真实结果在约 0.44x 成本下明显优于当前 `<0.5x` anchor，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=64`，测试 lowrank+expert 是否还能继续向左延伸。","如果 repair 后该点仍明显弱于 `jumprelu` 或 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的低成本点，则应归档 `lowrank_expert_topk`，把预算转回其他高优先级结构方向。","如果 repair 后出现新的失败模式，则下一轮继续只处理新的 blocker，不把结果误判为架构质量结论。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0073.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","reference_round":69,"env_overrides":[{"key":"NUM_EXPERTS","value":"64"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_e Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 e(x) 由轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“router 选单个静态子库 -> 子库内 local top-k -> 查表加权求和”，不依赖动态生成字典，因此 `expert_topk` 属于直接兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert`、`factorized_expert_topk` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能继续驱动 frontier。相对 r69 仅把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 32 提到 64，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk`、`K=160`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，直接回答当前低成本带最关键的 MoE-like 结构问题：如果 routed-only family 在 0.22x 左右的瓶颈仍有一部分来自总静态子库容量不足，而不是查表预算本身，那么把总容量继续做 true sparse-capacity 扩容、同时保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 的短激活路径，应能在几乎同一 total_cost 下继续压低 FVU，并形成新的低开销 Pareto 段。","summary":"Round 73 不回到旧 family 的 K/LR 邻域，而是沿当前最干净的 routed-only MoE-like 方向做一次单变量 sparse-capacity probe：以 r69 为参考，只把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 提到 64。这个动作正对当前“总容量与 active path 解耦”这一高优先级问题，而且成本预计仍停留在约 0.23x 附近，适合补当前明显欠覆盖的低成本前沿。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r69 只改 `NUM_EXPERTS`。这不是 plain selector 的重复扫点，也不是旧 family 的 K 轴微调，而是当前优先级最高的 true MoE-like 容量扩容验证。相比继续追 `factorized_expert_topk` 的局部宽度，先在已验证可运行、且直接兼容的 routed-only family 上回答“容量是否仍有收益”更符合 Round 73 的低开销探索目标。主要风险是 routed-only 方向在 `NUM_EXPERTS=32` 后已接近收益饱和；但无论正负，本轮都能清楚回答低成本带是否还值得继续向 true sparse-capacity MoE-like 扩容投入预算。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式保持为静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和，兼容性仍为直接兼容。","相对 r69 把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 32 提到 64 属于 true sparse-capacity 扩容：总静态容量增大，但每 token 的 active path 仍保持单 expert，不增加查表链路长度。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 粗估，`expert_topk K=160 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=64` 的 selection cost 只会较 r69 小幅上升，deployment 仍基本由 `K=160` 主导，因此 total_cost 预计仍在约 0.23x 附近，明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","`lowrank_expert_topk` 上的容量扩容负结果不能直接否定 routed-only `expert_topk`；两者瓶颈位置不同，本轮是对直接兼容 routed-only 前沿的独立验证。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=64` 在近同成本下显著优于 r69，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=128`，确认低成本带的 routed capacity 收益是否仍在继续。","如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=64` 改善很弱，则可较清晰判定 routed-only `expert_topk` 在当前 target 的低成本瓶颈已不主要在总子库容量，后续应把结构预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert` 这类带更强 residual cleanup 的兼容 family。","如果结果异常，先核对 `round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `num_experts=64` 已真实生效，再决定是否把该轮当作结构证据。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0050.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","reference_round":42,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r。也就是先用静态 low-rank trunk 向量库 U={u_r} 重构平滑主干，再对残差用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 B_e={b_{e,i}} 并做局部 sparse 选择；因此它仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。Round 48 和 Round 49 都表明 blocker 仍然是运行时构造路径，而不是结构质量：policy behavioral diff 通过 `from sparsify import SparseCoder` 直接实例化时，`cfg.architecture=lowrank_expert_topk` 仍未生效，比较结果依旧变成 topk vs topk。本轮主任务是继续修复 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` 中的直接构造分发，让 `SparseCoder(1024, SparseCoderConfig(architecture='lowrank_expert_topk', ...))` 真正返回对应 family，然后按 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的原计划重跑，拿到这条 `lowrank + expert` 结构在约 0.44x total_cost 下的首个有效点。","summary":"当前最高优先级仍是消除重复 blocker，而不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 上打磨低成本邻域点。r48、r49 连续两轮都显示 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在 behavioral diff 阶段被误拦，且 round summary 里 `touched_files=[]`、`patch_path=null`，说明修复并未真正落地；因此 Round 50 应继续做最小 repair，把 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 的分发修通，再重跑相对 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的低成本 probe。","self_review":"满足当前阶段的运行时优先级：先消除 blocker，再做结构比较。代码改动范围仍只限 `sparsify/`，不改 evaluation semantics，也不改 AutoResearch/launcher；实验配置相对 r42 仍只改一个 env 参数 `TRUNK_RANK=128`。这次 repair 需要给出可验证的完成标准：1. 直接构造 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 时按 `cfg.architecture` 分发；2. 用完全相同的 `architecture=lowrank_expert_topk, K=192, EF=1` 做 instantiate/forward/backward smoke；3. behavioral diff 不再把它判成 topk。风险是修复后该 family 的真实效果可能仍不强；但那时才是有效结构结论，而不是观测链路伪影。","touched_files":["sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["r48 和 r49 之后可以确认：当前 blocker 仍是 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 直接构造路径没有正确尊重 `cfg.architecture`，而不是 `lowrank_expert_topk` 本身的结构质量。","`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是静态 trunk 库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。","按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=192 EF=1 TRUNK_RANK=128` 的 total_cost 约为 0.44x；修复 blocker 后应优先获得这个点的真实 FVU。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 repair 后 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的真实结果在约 0.44x 成本下明显优于当前 `<0.5x` anchor，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=64`，测试 lowrank+expert 是否还能继续向左延伸。","如果 repair 后该点仍明显弱于 `jumprelu` 或 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的低成本点，则应归档 `lowrank_expert_topk`，把预算转回其他高优先级结构方向。","如果 repair 后出现新的失败模式，则下一轮继续只处理新的 blocker，不把结果误判为架构质量结论。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0020.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i。`factorized_topk` 只把在线选择链路改成 h(x)=ReLU(W1x), scores=W2h(x) 后再做 top-k，decoder 仍是单个静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理流水线，兼容性=直接兼容。r19 在 K=160, EF=1 下说明这个 family 有一定重构能力，但 auto scorer 过宽导致 selection 成本偏高；本轮主假设是把 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 压到 256 后，能把 total_cost 拉到约 0.28x，同时在该低成本带显著优于当前 topk 前沿。","summary":"相对 r19 的完整配置，本轮只改一个 env 参数：`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`。保持 `factorized_topk / K=160 / EF=1 / adam / LR=8e-4` 不变，专门验证低秩 scorer 缩窄后能否在 total_cost≈0.28x（selection≈0.12x + deployment≈0.16x）拿到优于当前 0.28x-0.31x topk 点的 FVU。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这是沿 r19 的单变量归因延续，避免再次混入 architecture 切换。风险是 hidden_dim=256 可能让 FVU 明显恶化，但即便如此，这轮也能直接回答 factorized scorer 是否真能把高 K 的部署优势转化成低成本 Pareto 改善；若仍无效，应降低该 family 优先级，把预算转向尚未充分验证的 routed/MoE-like 方向。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"256"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：`factorized_topk` 为直接兼容；最终导出形式不变，仍是单静态向量库上的有限加权和。","reference_round 选 r19，因为本轮要隔离 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 对同一 family 的影响；只改 1 个 env 参数，满足 param_only 单变量规则。","成本预估：在 K=160, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256 下，selection≈0.12x，deployment≈0.16x，total≈0.28x，正好落在当前急需补强的低成本区域。","若该点 FVU 仍明显差于同成本 topk，则说明当前 target 上 factorized scorer 的主要收益没有兑现，应减少继续打磨该 family 的预算。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果本轮在 0.28x 附近拿到正信号，下一轮继续以 r20 为 reference_round，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 到 384，测同 family 的质量/成本斜率。","如果本轮失败，则优先转向尚未在当前 recipe 下干净验证的其他低成本兼容 family，或开始实现真正轻量的 expert 子库 / MoE-like 路由原型。"],"reference_round":19}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0068.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`lowrank_residual` did not fail on quality grounds; it failed because the execution layer still rejects the architecture name before training starts. The smallest informative move is a narrow code-fix round inside `sparsify/` that registers and wires `lowrank_residual` into config validation and SAE class dispatch so the intended K=128 proxy prototype can finally produce a real signal.","summary":"Register and implement the `lowrank_residual` architecture in `sparsify/`, then rerun the same K=128 proxy prototype under the current signum baseline.","change_type":"edit_sae_code","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"lowrank_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This follows the blocker-first guidance by fixing the concrete architecture-selection failure instead of drawing conclusions from a non-run. The main risk is that additional compatibility issues appear after registration, but clearing the explicit selection gate is still the correct next step and keeps the architecture hypothesis intact.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 67 produced a concrete architecture-registration blocker for `lowrank_residual`: the runtime still rejects the architecture name in config validation before training begins.","This is stronger evidence of incomplete code integration than of a bad architecture, so `lowrank_residual` still has no usable quality signal.","The next round should keep the original `lowrank_residual` K=128 proxy target fixed and change only the code needed to make the family selectable and runnable by the existing launcher."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_residual` runs and shows competitive proxy FVU, keep the family alive and stabilize its trunk width next.","If it runs cleanly but is clearly worse than gated and not better than prior archived families, archive it quickly and move to another genuinely new family.","If it still fails after registration and dispatch are fixed, treat the remaining issue as a deeper implementation incompatibility and shift effort elsewhere."],"primary_variable":"code_fix"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0112.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}。其中 shared 子库 B^sh 与 routed expert 子库 {B_e} 都是静态向量库，在线侧只做轻量 router 选择少量 routed experts，然后执行 shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路；`shared_routed_expert_topk` 继续按直接兼容处理。明确排除不兼容 family：`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled 结构不能进入 frontier，也不能驱动本轮决策。r110→r111 已经完成 width knee 的连续左移，并在 `K=96, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 下得到新的非支配点 `0.30x / FVU 0.1228`，说明 shared+routed 低成本线仍成立；因此本轮应换到 deployment 轴，相对 r111 只把 `K` 从 96 降到 80，在保持 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 不变时，把 total_cost 进一步压到约 0.28x，同时不改变已验证的 shared+routed 结构假设。如果 FVU 只温和退化，则会新增一个更靠左的兼容 Pareto 点，并回答当前低成本线下一步更该压 lookup budget 还是已经触及部署侧 knee。","summary":"Round 112 以 r111 为 reference，保持 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的已验证结构不变，只改 `K=80`。width 轴已经连续给出新非支配点，本轮切到 deployment 轴，测当前 shared+routed 低成本前沿在 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 下还能否继续向左推进。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r111 只改 `K`。这不是回到旧 family 的局部扫点，而是在已经确认有效的 shared+routed 兼容主线上，从 encoder-width knee 切换到 deployment knee。选择 `K=80` 而不是继续压 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，是因为 r111 已经把 width 轴推进到 256 并形成新非支配点；继续连压宽度的边际信息已经下降，而 `K=80` 能更直接回答 lookup budget 的剩余空间。主要风险是 `K=96→80` 的退化幅度超过预期，但这同样是高价值结论，因为它会说明当前 shared+routed 线在约 0.30x 附近更受部署预算约束，不宜再继续向更低 K 推。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"80"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["本地兼容低成本 frontier 已形成 shared+routed 五段线，其中 r111 (`K=96, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`) 达到 total≈0.30x、FVU=0.1228，并继续优于旧 `expert_topk` anchors。","在 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 下，`K=80, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 的 selection 仍约 0.20x，deployment 约 0.08x，combined ratio 约 0.28x，显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算。","r110→r111 已经证明继续压每-expert width 仍能形成新非支配点；本轮因此切到 `K` 轴，补 deployment-side knee，而不是继续重复宽度压缩。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=80` 仍把 FVU 控制在约 0.13 左右或更低，则下一轮可继续保持 family 不变，只改 `K=64`，完成 shared+routed 在更低部署预算处的左边界定位。","如果 `K=80` 相比 r111 明显退化，则可初步判定当前 shared+routed 低成本线更接近 deployment knee，后续不应再继续降 K，而应回到 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 或切到 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 对照。","如果 `K=80` 与 r111 接近但未形成新非支配点，则下一轮必须换轴，不再连续压 `K`。"],"reference_round":111}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0005.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"切到直接兼容 family `jumprelu`，最终重构公式仍为 `x_hat = Σ_{i in S(x)} α_i(x) b_i`。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时，`{b_i}` 仍是单个静态向量库；在线链路仍是先形成支持集 `S(x)`、再计算系数、查表 `W b_i`、加权求和，阈值门控只改变支持形成方式，不改变静态库导出形式。本轮相对 r1 仅修改 `ARCHITECTURE`，在保持 `K=64, EXPANSION_FACTOR=1` 不变的同成本槽位下，测试 JumpReLU 的阈值化支持选择能否优于 plain top-k。","summary":"兼容性判断：`jumprelu` 为直接兼容。`factorized_topk` 在同成本带已经给出负结果，继续围绕它微调信息增量不高；下一步最干净的是换到另一个同成本、同部署开销、但支持形成机制不同的直接兼容 family。按当前本地成本估计，`jumprelu@K=64,EF=1` 的 total_cost 仍约 `0.31x`（selection `0.25x` + deployment `0.06x`），与当前最佳 `topk@K=64` 完全同槽位，适合做 matched architecture probe。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"遵守单变量原则，基于 `reference_round=1` 仅修改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮回答的问题很单一：在不改变 cost band、不引入额外部署复杂度的前提下，阈值化支持形成是否比 plain top-k 更适合当前 hookpoint。若仍无改进，说明当前 low-cost 区的直接兼容单库 family 已经出现连续负信号，后续应更积极转向其他结构槽位或高优先级未验证方向。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"jumprelu"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`jumprelu` 直接兼容 LUTurbo：最终形式仍是单静态向量库上的有限加权和 `Σ α_i b_i`，阈值只影响支持形成。","本地成本估计显示 `jumprelu@K=64,EF=1` 与 `topk@K=64,EF=1` 同为约 `0.31x` total_cost，适合做 matched probe。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `jumprelu@64` 优于 `topk@64`，下一轮可在该 family 内做 `K` 邻域或带宽相关探索。","如果 `jumprelu@64` 仍不优于 `topk@64`，下一轮应优先切到新的结构槽位，例如 `whitened_topk` 的更高但仍 `<0.5x` 成本带，或开始准备轻量 expert 子库方向的最小实现。"],"reference_round":1}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0115.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","reference_round":113,"env_overrides":[{"key":"LATENTS_PER_EXPERT","value":"224"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}。其中 shared 子库 B^sh 与 routed expert 子库 {B_e} 都是静态向量库，在线侧只做轻量 router 选择少量 routed experts，然后执行 shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权求和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 继续明确排除。r113 已在 `K=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64` 下形成约 0.27x / FVU 0.1350 的低成本前沿点，而 r114 证明把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 降到 1 会明显伤害质量，说明当前 shared+routed 的收益确实依赖双 routed experts。唯一主假设：在保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 与 `K=64` 不变的前提下，把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 256 缩到 224，可以把 selection cost 从约 0.20x 压到约 0.18x、total_cost 从约 0.27x 左移到约 0.24x，同时仍显著优于旧低成本 anchor `expert_topk K=128` 的 FVU 0.3149，从而回答当前低成本前沿的下一步更该压每-expert 宽度，而不是继续压 active experts。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224` 仍把 FVU 控制在约 0.16 或更低，则下一轮可继续以本轮为 reference，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`，完成 `K=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 这条 shared+routed 子线的 width knee 定位。","如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224` 相比 r113 只温和退化但成本明显更低，则 shared+routed 低成本前沿仍可继续沿 width 轴左移，后续不必回到 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`。","如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224` 明显劣化接近 r114，则说明当前 `K=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 已接近 width floor；下一轮应换轴或切回 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 对照，而不是继续压 width。"],"notes_to_memory":["r114 已明确给出负信号：`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 在约 0.20x total_cost 下退化到 FVU 0.2038，说明当前 shared+routed 前沿的质量确实依赖双 routed experts。","本地 cost 自检显示：`shared_routed_expert_topk K=64 NUM_EXPERTS=64 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224` 的 selection ratio 约 0.18x、deployment ratio 约 0.06x、combined ratio 约 0.24x；相对 r113 的约 0.27x 有明确左移空间。","本轮不需要代码修改；`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 与 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 wiring 已在历史轮次中稳定生效。"],"self_review":"相对 r113 只改一个 env 参数 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，满足单变量原则。之所以不以 r114 为 reference 去改回 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`，是因为那会把本轮语义变成‘撤销上轮失败’，信息量较低；更合理的是把 r114 作为证据，确认 active-path 不该再压，然后回到 r113 这个有效前沿点上沿 width 轴继续探索。该点仍远低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","summary":"以 r113 为 reference，保持 `shared_routed_expert_topk`、`K=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 不变，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`，测试在已知双 routed experts 必要的前提下，shared+routed 低成本前沿是否还能通过缩窄每-expert 宽度继续左移到约 0.24x。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0050.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Crash recovery mode requires returning to the best known working gated path with only a minor parameter adjustment. The safest informative move is to reuse the strongest stable recipe and probe the adjacent lower-K point `K=64`, which is already a validated Pareto setting and avoids the blocked architecture-code path entirely.","summary":"Run a gated proxy stabilization pass on the current best EF=16 signum configuration with `K=64`, keeping LR=1.6e-3 and AUXK_ALPHA=0.01 fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This follows crash-recovery constraints exactly by avoiding code edits and using the strongest validated family with one small parameter change. The main risk is limited novelty because K=64 is already known, but this is the least risky way to recover a clean signal after consecutive architecture-path crashes.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.01"},{"key":"K","value":"64"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Crash recovery mode requires a param-only round on the current best working configuration, so this round returns to the stable gated recipe.","The `factorized_topk` path has now crashed repeatedly for implementation-layer reasons, so it should not be touched again until session stability is re-established.","Using gated K=64 preserves the strongest known architecture and training regime while testing a previously healthy lower-cost Pareto point."],"next_hypotheses":["If the K=64 proxy run is healthy and matches its prior behavior, keep using the gated family for recovery until crashes stop.","If K=64 regresses unexpectedly under the same stable regime, return to the exact K=128 anchor on the next round to separate runtime noise from configuration effects.","If stability is restored after this round, resume broader exploration only with a clear implementation plan that avoids the recent factorized-topk registration failure mode."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0033.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i。对 `jumprelu` 而言，JumpReLU 门控只改变支持集 S(x) 的形成方式，decoder 仍是同一个静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的查表 + 加权求和链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。r32 已把 `jumprelu` 推到当前最佳 <0.5x 点，说明该 family 在当前 target 的低成本区确有信号；下一步最有信息量的动作是只增大 K、保持门控参数不变，测试它能否在仍低于 0.5x 的成本带继续沿 Pareto 前沿改进，而不是重新换 family 打散归因。","summary":"基于 r32 的 jumprelu 配方做一次低成本边界扩展：仅把 K 从 224 提到 240，保持 ARCHITECTURE=jumprelu、EF=1、JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD=0.05、JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH=0.05、adam、8e-4 不变，验证该 family 能否在约 0.48x total_cost 下继续刷新 <0.5x 区域前沿。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"主要风险是 K=240 只带来边际 FVU 改善，不足以抵消部署成本上升，形成一个被 r32 近似支配的弱点；但在 jumprelu 已经拿到当前最佳 <0.5x 点的前提下，这一步能直接判断该 family 的低成本优势是否具备可扩展性。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"240"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["jumprelu 当前是本 target 上已验证的最佳 <0.5x family，且门控参数已固定到一个可复现的低成本工作点。","在当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，jumprelu K=240 EF=1 的预估成本约为 encoder 0.25x + deploy 0.23x = total 0.48x，仍属于本阶段重点的 <0.5x 区域。","本轮只改 K，不改 architecture 或 JumpReLU 动态参数，用于判断 r32 的改善是否能沿同一 family 的低成本 Pareto 继续延伸。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 jumprelu K=240 继续明显优于 r32，则下一轮可考虑把该 family 视为当前低成本主线候选，并在 <0.5x 区域内补一个相邻 K 点确认曲线形状。","如果 K=240 仅边际改善或退化，则停止继续上推 jumprelu 的 K，转去新的兼容 family 或新的结构槽位。"],"reference_round":32}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0071.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":69,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e(h(x))}(h(x))} α_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低维投影，e(h(x)) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{b_{e,i}} 是各 expert 的静态子库原子。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的链路是：先做共享低维投影 h(x)，再做 router 选单个静态 expert 子库，再由该 expert 的小型 head 在低维空间上打分并做 local top-k，最后把 (e,i) 扁平化为静态库查表上的有限加权和；静态库本身不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容。兼容性先验在本轮保持清晰：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert` 与本轮新增的 `factorized_expert_topk` 都属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，只能留作历史参考，不能继续驱动 frontier。相对 r69 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`EF=1` 与训练 recipe 不变，直接回答当前高优先级问题：把 shared low-rank basis 放进 expert 内部 head，而不是放在 expert 外部做全局 trunk，是否能在不拉长 active path 的前提下形成新的低成本 Pareto 段。按当前 proxy 粗估，shared basis + active expert head 的 encoder 成本应仍落在约 0.3x 量级，配合 `K=160` 的部署成本后总成本预计仍在约 0.45x-0.5x 带，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","summary":"Round 70 已经说明现有 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 EF=1 外置 trunk 原型不足以继续支撑低成本前沿。本轮不再补旧 family 的局部点，而是新增一个更贴近当前高信息量假设的最小原型 `factorized_expert_topk`，并以 r69 为 matched reference 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，验证“shared low-rank basis + routed expert head”是否优于纯 routed-only `expert_topk`。","self_review":"这满足单轮单变量约束：训练配置相对 r69 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。代码侧只在 `sparsify/` 内完成最小 family 接线，不新增 tunable，因此不需要改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。选择开新 family 而不是继续扫 `expert_topk` 的 K 或 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的局部旋钮，是因为当前提示已明确指出更高信息量方向在 expert-internal low-rank；继续围绕 EF=1 旧原型做小修小补的信息增量已经不足。主要风险是 auto `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 可能偏大或偏小，导致首轮结果更多反映默认宽度而非结构上限；但这正符合新 family 第一轮先看结构是否值得继续、而不是先调宽度的要求。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 71 优先新增 `factorized_expert_topk`，覆盖当前未实现但高优先级的 `shared low-rank basis + expert-specific head` 结构槽位。","首轮原型不新增 tunable，复用现有 `NUM_EXPERTS` 与 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 语义；训练配置相对 r69 仅切换 `ARCHITECTURE`，归因最干净。","必须按 sae-architecture-integration checklist 完成 whitelist、dispatch、class、exact-string instantiate/forward/backward smoke，然后再把真实训练结果当作结构证据。","不兼容 family 继续排除在 active frontier 外；本轮比较对象只限兼容 family。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 在与 r69 相近总成本下明显优于 routed-only `expert_topk`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只显式设置 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，测试共享 basis 宽度是否是该新结构的主控制旋钮。","如果它只小幅改善但仍明显弱于 `<0.5x` 最佳锚点，则下一轮可做 matched `K=128` 左移测试，判断这条新结构更适合低成本还是中成本带。","如果它没有改善或训练异常，则应快速归档该 family 的当前原型，并把结构预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或其他兼容的新 MoE-like 方向，而不是继续在旧 EF=1 原型上做邻域微调。"]}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0049.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`factorized_topk` has now failed for a concrete architecture-registration reason rather than an ambiguous quality or runtime signal: the execution layer rejects the architecture name in `SparseCoderConfig` before training begins. The next coherent move is a narrow code-fix round that wires `factorized_topk` into the existing config/class registry and forward path so the prototype can finally receive one real K=128 proxy measurement under the strongest current regime.","summary":"Register and enable the `factorized_topk` architecture in `sparsify/`, then rerun the same K=128 proxy prototype under the current signum baseline.","change_type":"edit_perf_code","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This is the smallest defensible next step because the latest failure is an explicit compatibility bug, not a quality result, and continuing to retry without fixing registration would waste rounds. The main risk is that the family still underperforms once it runs, but one valid proxy result is required before deciding whether to stabilize or retire it.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.01"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 48 produced a concrete execution-layer error for `factorized_topk`: the architecture name is not registered in `SparseCoderConfig`, so the family still has no usable quality signal.","This is stronger evidence of a missing code integration step than of a bad architecture, so the family should not be retired on quality grounds yet.","This round keeps the original `factorized_topk` K=128 proxy target fixed and changes only the code needed to make the architecture selectable and runnable by the existing launcher."],"next_hypotheses":["If the registered `factorized_topk` run completes and beats plain `topk`, keep the family alive and begin stabilizing its internal factorization design.","If the run completes normally but remains far behind gated, retire shallow factorization and move to a different encoder-expressivity direction.","If `factorized_topk` still fails after registration is fixed, treat the remaining issue as a deeper implementation incompatibility and shift effort elsewhere."],"primary_variable":"code_fix"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0062.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判断为扩展兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r61 仅把 STAGE1_RATIO 从 0.25 降到 0.125，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`、`TRUNK_RANK=64`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`K=128`、`EF=1` 不变时，把固定 K 预算更多分给全局 residual cleanup；如果 r61 的剩余误差主要来自 routed expert 之后仍未覆盖的全局残差结构，而不是 expert stage 容量不足，则 FVU 应在几乎相同 total_cost 下继续下降。","summary":"r61 已证明三段式 `lowrank_expert_residual` 在当前更强的 trunk+expert 配方上优于纯 `lowrank_expert_topk`。Round 62 不再加成本，而是做同成本预算重分配：只降 `STAGE1_RATIO`，直接回答当前收益更依赖 expert 段还是 residual cleanup 段。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r61 只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`。该 family 属于 LUTurbo 扩展兼容 family，不触碰不兼容方向，也不需要新增 tunable 参数接线。选择这个动作而不是继续扫 `K` 或 `TRUNK_RANK`，是因为 r61 已经给出新的中成本结构锚点，当前最有信息量的问题是固定总预算下 expert/residual 两段的最优分配。主要风险是 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.125` 可能让 expert 段过窄，导致质量回退；但无论正负，结构归因都很清晰。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"STAGE1_RATIO","value":"0.125"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 当前已在 `TRUNK_RANK=64, NUM_EXPERTS=32, K=128` 下形成新的中成本质量锚点；下一步重点应转向固定总预算下的段间分配，而不是继续无差别增容量。","Round 62 是对 r61 的纯预算分配 probe：只把更多 K 留给 global residual cleanup，看剩余误差是否主要在 residual 段。","该轮 total_cost 预计与 r61 基本同一量级，因为只改变 stage1/stage2 的 K 切分，不改变总 K、trunk 或 expert 容量。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.125` 继续改善，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只回测更温和的 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.1875` 或提高 `K`，寻找这条三段式结构在 0.5x-0.6x 带的更优 Pareto 落点。","如果它明显变差，则说明当前更强 trunk+expert 配方下，expert 段仍不能再缩，后续应优先考虑压 `K` 或回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的更低成本延展，而不是继续给 residual 段加预算。","如果结果异常，先核对 round config 与 checkpoint config 中 `stage1_ratio=0.125` 是否真实生效，再决定是否把该轮当作结构证据。"],"reference_round":61}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0064.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(r_1)}(r_1)} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 r_1 = x - Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i，B={b_i} 是静态 coarse library，C_e={c_{e,j}} 是静态 expert residual 子库，e(r_1) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert；在线可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“coarse 查表 + expert residual 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判断为扩展兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r61 仅把 ARCHITECTURE 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=128`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EF=1` 和训练 recipe 不变，直接回答当前中成本带的主要收益究竟来自 low-rank trunk，还是来自“coarse global library + routed expert residual”这条 trunk-free staged 结构；如果后者已经足够，则该 family 应在接近当前中成本带的位置给出接近 r61 的 FVU，并形成新的结构性 Pareto 段。","summary":"连续两轮对 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的局部预算微调没有带来改进，本轮不再继续在同一 family 上细扫，而是切到高优先级但欠验证的 `two_stage_residual_expert`。相对 r61 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，做一次高信息量的 matched 结构对照，判断 low-rank trunk 是否真的是当前 target 的必要组成。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r61 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。该 family 属于 LUTurbo 扩展兼容 family，不触碰不兼容方向，也不需要新增 tunable 参数接线。当前 `lowrank_expert_residual` 已经拿到有效中成本锚点，但最近两轮继续调 `STAGE1_RATIO` 与 `K` 都未改善；继续在同一 family 局部打磨的信息增量已经下降，因此应把预算切到仍然高优先级、但当前 target 上尚未用 `NUM_EXPERTS=32 / K=128` 重新验证的 `two_stage_residual_expert`。主要风险是参考配置里遗留的 `TRUNK_RANK=64` 对该 family 实际上不生效，因此这是“训练 recipe matched、结构语义不含 trunk”的对照，而不是严格共享所有有效结构参数的配方。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_stage_residual_expert"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`two_stage_residual_expert` 的 LUTurbo 形式是静态 coarse library 加静态 expert residual 子库上的有限加权和，兼容性为扩展兼容。","Round 64 是对 r61 的结构对照：在相同 `K=128 / NUM_EXPERTS=32 / STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 训练配方下，只看去掉 low-rank trunk、改为 coarse sparse stage 后是否仍能保住质量。","如果该对照明显落后于 r61，则当前 target 上 low-rank trunk 的价值可视为已被重新验证，后续不应再把 `two_stage_residual_expert` 当成同优先级主线。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `two_stage_residual_expert` 接近或优于 r61，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO`，把这条 staged sparse 结构压向更低成本带。","如果它明显弱于 r61，则可较清晰判定当前 target 上 low-rank trunk 是必要组成；后续应把预算回投到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_residual`，而不是继续展开 trunk-free staged family。","如果结果异常，先核对 round config 与 checkpoint config 中 `architecture=two_stage_residual_expert` 是否真实生效，再决定是否把该轮当作结构证据。"],"reference_round":61}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0037.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":27,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个 expert 子库 e(x) 并在其内做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差再做一次小预算 sparse 补偿。因此它仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：在与 r27 相同的 EF=1、K=192 recipe 下，把 `expert_topk` 升级为 `lowrank + expert + residual` 三段式结构，能回答‘仅有 lowrank+expert 仍不足时，加入第二段 residual 修正是否会形成新的结构性 Pareto 段’这个当前更关键的问题。","summary":"不继续在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上做第三个邻域扫点，而是进入下一结构槽位：实现最小可运行的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 原型。以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，先验证三段式结构本身是否值得继续。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：运行配置相对 r27 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮优先解决结构未知量，而不是继续在已显示弱势的 recipe 上局部打磨。选择 r27 而不是 r34/r18，是因为它提供了与 expert 路由最接近的 matched baseline，同时避免把结论混入 jumprelu 或大 K 主线。风险是该三段式原型在 K=192 处总成本大概率落在中成本带而非极低成本带，但这仍符合当前阶段允许用少量中成本质量锚点回答结构问题的策略。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_residual` 首轮能稳定训练且 FVU 明显优于 `expert_topk K=192`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，验证 expert 段与 residual 段的预算分配是否是主要控制旋钮。","如果该 family 训练稳定但收益有限，下一轮优先只改 `TRUNK_RANK`，验证 trunk 是否过重并侵蚀了低成本收益。","如果三段式 family 连 matched baseline 都无法明显改善，应停止继续围绕该原型打磨，转向 `two-stage residual expert` 方向，而不是回到 plain selector 家族。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 的导出形式是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","本轮要回答的是三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 是否值得继续，而不是再问一次 `expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 K 轴斜率。","建议实现时复用现有 lowrank trunk、expert local top-k、以及 residual second-pass 模块，避免新增 tunable 名称；优先复用现有 `TRUNK_RANK` 与 `STAGE1_RATIO` 语义。","若新增 family 需要后续调 `TRUNK_RANK`/`STAGE1_RATIO`，应同时补齐该 architecture 在 override registry 中的允许键，避免后续 param_only 回合静默拒绝 override。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0044.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","reference_round":37,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"16"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库并做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差做 sparse cleanup，因此仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。本轮相对 r37 只改 `TRUNK_RANK=16`，主假设是该 family 的质量主要由 expert+residual 两段支撑，trunk 可以被压到近乎最小而仍维持对当前 <0.5x anchor 有竞争力的 FVU，从而把这条已验证结构线推进到约 0.52x total_cost 的近低成本带。","summary":"Round 43 的 `lowrank_expert_topk` 被 policy 的 behavioral-diff blocker 拦截，这一轮先不把预算继续投到被运行时策略卡住的 family，而是沿当前最强且已验证兼容的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 继续向低成本带延伸。以 r37 为参考仅下调 `TRUNK_RANK` 到 16，预计把总成本从约 1.06x 压到约 0.52x，直接回答这条三段式结构在接近 0.5x 区域是否还能保持明显优于现有低成本 anchor 的质量。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r37 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。这不是旧 family 的局部 K 轴打磨，而是在当前主线结构上做一次高信息量的成本压缩试验；相比继续追 `lowrank_expert_topk`，它避免再次撞上已知 policy blocker。风险是 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 比 r38 的 128 更激进，FVU 可能明显恶化；但这正是本轮要回答的核心问题，即 lowrank+expert+residual 在接近 0.5x 带时是否仍然成立。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是 trunk 静态库 + expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。","按当前实现的成本估算，`lowrank_expert_residual K=192 EF=1 TRUNK_RANK=16` 的 encoder≈0.32x、deployment≈0.20x、total≈0.52x，仍在 1.5×h×n 硬约束内。","Round 43 的阻塞来自 policy 侧 behavioral diff 对 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的拦截，不应把那次 `policy_reject` 误判为结构质量结论。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 仍把 FVU 压到当前 `jumprelu K=248` 的 0.1342 以下，则下一轮继续同 family，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=8`，测试这条结构前沿能否真正贴近 0.5x。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 的 FVU 退化过大，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=32`，寻找这条主线在 0.5x-0.6x 带的折中点。","如果这轮显示 trunk 几乎压空后质量仍稳，则后续再考虑 `STAGE1_RATIO`，细化 expert 段与 residual 段的预算分配。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0034.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i。对 `jumprelu` 而言，JumpReLU 门控只改变支持集 S(x) 的形成方式，decoder 仍是同一个静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的查表 + 加权求和链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。r33 已把 `jumprelu` 推到当前最佳 <0.5x 点，因此下一步最有信息量的动作是在不改 family 与门控参数的前提下，只把 K 推到仍低于 0.5x 的边界附近，测试该 family 的低成本前沿是否还能继续改善。","summary":"基于 r33 的 jumprelu 配方做一次低成本边界细化：仅把 K 从 240 提到 248，保持 ARCHITECTURE=jumprelu、EF=1、JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD=0.05、JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH=0.05、adam、8e-4 不变，验证该 family 能否在约 0.49x total_cost 下继续刷新 <0.5x 区域前沿。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"主要风险是 K=248 的收益已经进入递减区，只会带来很小的 FVU 改善，不足以形成新的高质量 Pareto 点；但在 jumprelu 已成为当前最佳 <0.5x family 的前提下，这一步能直接判断它在低成本边界附近是否仍有可扩展性。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"248"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["jumprelu 当前是本 target 上已验证的最佳 <0.5x family，且门控参数已固定到一个稳定工作点。","在当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，jumprelu K=248 EF=1 的预估成本约为 encoder 0.25x + deploy 0.24x = total 0.49x，仍属于本阶段重点的 <0.5x 区域。","本轮只改 K，用于细化 jumprelu 在低成本边界附近的 Pareto 形状，而不把收益与门控参数变化混在一起。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 jumprelu K=248 继续明显优于 r33，则下一轮可考虑测试 0.5x 边界附近的 K=256，确认跨过边界是否仍值得。","如果 K=248 仅边际改善或退化，则停止继续上推 jumprelu 的 K，转去新的兼容 family 或新的结构槽位。"],"reference_round":33}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0022.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i。`factorized_topk` 只改变在线选择链路为 h(x)=ReLU(W1x), scores=W2h(x) 后再做 top-k，decoder 仍是单个静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理流水线，兼容性=直接兼容。r20-r21 说明在极低成本区它能提供更低 selection cost，但质量仍落后于 topk；本轮主假设是仅把 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 从 256 提到 384，在保持 K=192 不变时可显著提升打分质量，并在 total_cost 约 0.38x 的 matched-cost 区间内逼近或改写当前低成本前沿。","summary":"相对 r21 的完整配置，本轮只改一个 env 参数：`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=384`。保持 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_topk`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`K=192`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变，专门测试 factorized scorer 宽度是否是当前 family 的主要瓶颈。预计 total_cost 约从 0.31x 升到 0.38x（selection 约 0.19x，deployment 约 0.19x）。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"这是比继续加 K 更干净的单变量测试，因为 r20->r21 的 K 增益较弱，而 r19 对比 r21/r20 表明 scorer 宽度更可能主导质量。风险是即使 widened scorer 也仍显著落后于同成本 topk；若如此，应停止继续打磨这个 family，把下一轮预算转向其他兼容 family 或真正轻量的 MoE-like 新方向。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"384"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：`factorized_topk` 为直接兼容；最终导出形式始终是单静态向量库上的有限加权和。","reference_round 选 r21，因为本轮只想隔离 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 对同一 family、同一 K 的影响；满足 param_only 单变量规则。","成本预估：K=192, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=384 时，selection 约 0.19x，deployment 约 0.19x，total 约 0.38x，正好对应当前 frontier 中 topk K=128 的 matched-cost 槽位。","如果该点仍明显差于 topk 0.38x 区域的 FVU，说明 factorized scorer 在当前 target 上的主要价值更偏向超低成本 anchor，而非中低成本主线。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果本轮在约 0.38x 处取得明显 FVU 改善，下一轮继续以该 family 当前最好点为 reference_round，只改 `K` 到 224 或 256，测其沿部署成本方向的 Pareto 斜率。","如果本轮收益不足，则降低 `factorized_topk` 的后续优先级，转去验证其他尚未充分覆盖的低成本兼容 family，或启动真正轻量 expert 子库 / MoE-like 路由原型。"],"reference_round":21}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0106.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":105,"family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"2"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 B^sh 是始终激活的静态 shared 子库，E(x) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 routed experts，所有原子都来自静态向量库，因此在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。明确排除不兼容 family：`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled 结构不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r105 已经完成 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=512` 的真实训练生效验证，并在更低 active-path 宽度下得到 val_fvu=0.1364；下一步最有信息量的问题不再是参数是否接通，而是“更窄 expert + 更多 active routed experts”是否优于当前单路 routed 方案。相对 r105 仅把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从默认 1 提到 2，在保持 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=512`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`K=128`、`EF=1` 与其余训练配方不变时，active path 从 `shared + 1 routed` 变为 `shared + 2 routed`，预计总成本约从 0.39x 升到 0.52x，仍远低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束；如果 shared+routed 的收益主要来自更细粒度的局部组合而不是单 expert 宽度本身，则这一步应能显著压低 FVU，并回答这条 MoE-like 方向是否值得继续进入 matched-cost 带。","summary":"Round 106 不回到旧 family 的 K 轴，也不再重复 `NUM_EXPERTS` 容量外推。以 r105 为 reference，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`，直接回答 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 在已验证生效的窄 expert 宽度下，增加少量 routed experts 是否能形成更有价值的低到中成本结构段。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r105 只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`。`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 的 allowlist、runner、脚本透传、runtime config 与 checkpoint config 已在 r105 被真实验证，因此本轮不再需要 edit_sae_code。选择继续沿 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 而不是回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 `TRUNK_RANK/K` 微调，是因为当前阶段更需要回答高优先级未充分验证的 shared+routed MoE-like 结构是否成立；而 r105 已经把“更窄 per-expert width”这个前提铺好。主要风险是 total_cost 会从约 0.39x 抬到约 0.52x，若 FVU 改善不足，这条路线就不应继续占用低开销预算。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r105 已经给出真实参数生效证据：`shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 runtime_config_json 与 checkpoint config 中都包含 `latents_per_expert=512`，并完成了有效训练，val_fvu=0.13637857139110565。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，`shared_routed_expert_topk K=128 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=64 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=512 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 的 selection≈0.39x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.52x，仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算。","本轮是 shared+routed 方向的首个真实 multi-routed probe：不再回答参数是否接通，而是回答更细粒度 routed composition 是否比单路 routed 更值得继续。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 在约 0.52x 下把 FVU 明显压到接近或优于 r104 的 0.1107，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=384` 或 `768`，细化这条 shared+routed 线的 matched-cost 宽度 knee。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 只带来很小改善或变差，则可初步判断当前 shared+routed 收益更依赖单 expert 宽度而非多 routed experts，后续应收缩这条 family，把低成本预算转回 `lowrank_expert_topk` 或 matched `lowrank_expert_residual`。","如果结果异常，先核对 round106 的 runtime_config_json 与 checkpoint config 中同时出现 `active_experts=2` 和 `latents_per_expert=512`，再决定是否把该轮当作结构证据。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0027.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_perf_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式取 x_hat = Σ_e Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}；在当前实现里 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1，因此在线侧先用轻量 router 选一个静态 expert 子库，再在该子库内做 local top-k，最后把 (e,i) 扁平化为全局索引进入 LUTurbo 的查表 + 加权求和流水线。相对 r21 仅切到 expert_topk，可把选择成本压到约 0.06x、总成本压到约 0.25x；若 FVU 明显优于当前低成本区的 factorized_topk K=192 / topk K=80-128 点，就能补出新的 <0.5x Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果 expert_topk 在约 0.25x 总成本下把 FVU 压到 0.20 左右或更低，下一轮优先在同 family 内扫 K=160/224，刻画低成本 Pareto 形状。","如果 expert_topk FVU 明显差于 factorized_topk K=192，则不要在它上面做 recipe 微调，转去其他兼容的低成本新 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["expert_topk 现已注册为 direct_compatible；其导出形式为 router 选静态子库后在子库内做有限加权和。","在当前 target (1024x4096 proxy) 下，expert_topk K=192 EF=1 的预估成本为 sel=266240 (0.06x), deploy=786432 (0.19x), total=1052672 (0.25x)。","使用 _get_sae_class('expert_topk') 的 instantiate/forward/backward smoke 已通过。"],"reference_round":21,"self_review":"主要风险是单 expert 路由过硬导致容量利用不足，K=192 已接近每个 expert 的 256 上限，可能出现 router 失衡或局部字典饱和；但这轮的价值在于用一次结构上更贴近 LUTurbo 子库部署的 probe，判断 MoE-like 方向在当前 target 的低成本区是否值得继续。","summary":"修复 AutoResearch 对 expert_topk 的兼容性注册后，基于 r21 做一次低开销 MoE-like probe：仅把 ARCHITECTURE 改为 expert_topk，保留 K=192、EF=1、adam、8e-4，验证轻量 router + 单 expert 子库是否能在 0.25x 总成本附近提供比现有低成本点更好的 FVU。","touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0098.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":96,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_residual"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈S_2(r_1)} γ_j(x) c_j，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r 是共享 low-rank trunk，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，r_1 = x - t(x) - Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库。在线侧可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单个静态 expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 属于扩展兼容；`expert_topk` 属于直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 属于不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：r95-r97 已基本完成当前 `lowrank_expert_topk` 主线的 `TRUNK_RANK=40-48` 与 `K=96-128` knee 定位，因此下一个高信息量问题不再是继续细扫该 family，而是 residual cleanup 在已压缩 recipe 上是否仍值得其额外成本。相对 r96 仅将 `ARCHITECTURE: lowrank_expert_topk -> lowrank_expert_residual`，保持 `K=96`、`TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EF=1`、`adam`、`8e-4` 不变；如果 residual 分支在当前 target 上仍有真实结构价值，则 FVU 应显著低于 r96 的 0.1305，并有机会把这条 mid-cost 线压回接近 0.11 左右，同时总成本约为 selection≈0.53x、deployment≈0.13x、total≈0.66x，仍处于允许的 0.3x-0.8x 结构对照带且远低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算。","summary":"当前不再继续细扫 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 `K` 或 `TRUNK_RANK`，因为 `K=96-128` 与 `TRUNK_RANK=40-48` 的边界已经基本补齐。以 r96 为 matched reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`，直接回答 residual cleanup 在当前最强低成本 `lowrank + expert` recipe 上是否值得其额外成本，这是 operator guide 明确要求在 knee 定位完成后优先回答的结构问题。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r96 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这不是回到旧 family 的局部 K 轴，也不是继续重复 routed-only 或 `factorized_expert_topk` 的已否定方向，而是对当前已完成 knee 定位的有效主线做一次高信息量 matched 结构切换。主要风险是参考配置中的 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 下原本不生效、在新 family 下会开始生效，因此这是“recipe matched、但并非所有旋钮都语义共享”的 architecture swap；不过这正是当前需要的真实部署可行结构对照。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 当前主线的 `TRUNK_RANK=40-48` 与 `K=96-128` 边界已基本补齐：r95、r96、r97 已经给出足够清晰的 deployment/trunk knee 信息。","按照当前 operator guide，knee 定位完成后，下一个高优先级问题应是 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 对照，而不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上细扫。","`lowrank_expert_residual K=96 TRUNK_RANK=40 NUM_EXPERTS=32 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 的 fresh cost 约为 selection 0.53x、deployment 0.13x、total 0.66x，适合作为 0.3x-0.8x 带内的结构价值验证点。","`factorized_expert_topk` 与 routed-only `ACTIVE_EXPERTS>1` 方向仍维持负信号，本轮继续避开这些已低优先级路线。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 在约 0.66x 成本下把 FVU 明显压到接近 0.11 或更低，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=112` 或 `K=128`，细化 residual cleanup 在这一 recipe 上的最优 deployment 预算。","如果 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 只带来很弱改善，说明当前 target 上 residual cleanup 对已压缩的 `lowrank + expert` recipe 边际价值有限；下一轮应停止让三段式结构主导预算，并考虑回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 主线或转向 `two_stage_residual_expert`。","如果结果异常偏弱或训练行为反常，应先把它归因为 architecture swap 中 `STAGE1_RATIO` 从 inert 变为 active 的语义差异，再决定是否需要一轮同 family 的 budget 重分配验证。"]}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0048.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`factorized_topk` still lacks a usable proxy quality signal, and the most recent failure evidence points to the sanity invocation itself rather than a meaningful architecture outcome. The least-bad next move is to rerun the same `factorized_topk` K=128 proxy comparison without further code churn so the family can receive one clean measurement under the current strongest regime.","summary":"Retry the `factorized_topk` K=128 proxy prototype under the current signum baseline, keeping the same regime and avoiding additional code changes so the family can get its first real quality read.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This is narrower and better justified than another code-edit round because the latest recorded failure mode does not provide evidence that the architecture implementation itself is wrong. The main risk is another blocked run, but a clean retry is necessary before either stabilizing or retiring the family.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.01"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`factorized_topk` still has no valid proxy quality measurement despite multiple attempts, so the family remains unresolved rather than negatively established.","The latest recorded sanity failure shows a syntax error in the generated check command, which is stronger evidence of a runtime invocation problem than of an architecture-quality issue.","This round keeps the exact `factorized_topk` prototype target fixed and changes nothing except giving the family another clean chance to produce a real proxy result."],"next_hypotheses":["If the retry completes and materially beats plain `topk`, keep `factorized_topk` alive and begin family-specific stabilization on its internal factorization design.","If the retry completes normally but remains far behind gated, retire shallow factorization and move to a different encoder-expressivity direction.","If the retry still fails before producing usable metrics, treat the blockage as an execution-layer issue around this prototype path and shift effort elsewhere."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0016.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"320"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式固定为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i。`topk` 的在线侧只输出稀疏支持集 S(x) 与对应系数 α_i(x)，离线侧字典库 B={b_i} 保持静态且不随样本动态生成，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态向量查表加权和推理链路，兼容性判定为直接兼容。本轮相对 r15 仅改 `K: 256 -> 320`，回答一个问题：当 deployment 预算从约 0.25x 推进到约 0.31x、总成本从约 0.50x 提到约 0.56x 后，`topk, EF=1` 的 deployment-side frontier 是否仍有显著 Pareto 改善，且训练曲线后段是否继续稳定下行而不是开始明显饱和。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=320` 仍带来清晰改善，则说明当前 `topk, EF=1` 在 0.5x 以上成本带仍未走平，后续可考虑继续做一次更高 K 探针，或在相近总成本下引入其他兼容 family 做横向对比。","如果 `K=320` 收益已明显减弱或曲线后段变平，则说明 deployment 增益开始递减，后续应停止继续抬 `K`，优先转向其他兼容 family 或高优先级未充分验证的轻量 expert 子库 / MoE-like 方向。"],"notes_to_memory":["`topk` 为直接兼容 family；导出形式保持为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i`，满足 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态库有限加权和约束。","Round 16 继续只改 `K`，避免引入 optimizer/LR/family 混杂；当前目标是确认 deployment 轴在越过 0.5x 总成本后是否开始明显变平。","按当前 proxy 线性近似，`K=320` 的 deployment 成本约 0.31x，总成本约 0.56x（0.25x + 0.31x），显著低于 1.5x 硬约束。"],"reference_round":15,"self_review":"满足单轮单参数变更约束；相对 r15 只修改了 `K`。选择 `K=320` 而不是切换 family，是因为 r11-r15 沿 deployment 轴持续给出可解释改善，当前最有信息量的问题是越过 0.5x 成本后斜率是否开始显著变平。","summary":"继续主线 `topk`。其最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i`，可直接导出为 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态字典查表加权和，因此属于直接兼容。Round 16 以 r15 为参考，只把 `K` 从 256 提到 320，在不改变 encoder 成本的前提下测试 0.5x 以上总成本带的 deployment 边际收益，并重点观察训练曲线是否开始明显饱和。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0085.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"2"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{e∈E(x-t(x))} Σ_{i∈S_e(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，|E(x-t(x))|=ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2。在线导出仍是“trunk 查表 + 2 个静态 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此兼容性判断为扩展兼容。相对 r60 仅新增 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2，在保持 ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk、K=128、TRUNK_RANK=64、NUM_EXPERTS=32、EXPANSION_FACTOR=1、OPTIMIZER=adam、LR=8e-4 不变时，验证 shared trunk + routed experts 是否能通过更短于全容量扩张的 active path 提供新的 0.3x-0.8x total_cost Pareto 段。按当前成本模型估算，该点约为 encoder 0.54x、deployment 0.19x、total 0.73x，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 在约 0.73x total_cost 下显著优于 r60，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 NUM_EXPERTS=64，验证“更大总容量 + 短 active path”是否继续成立。","如果 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 改善很弱或退化，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3 或回到 1，明确当前 target 的最优 active-expert 数，而不是继续混扫旧轴。","如果 lowrank_expert_topk 的多 expert active path 仍不给正信号，则后续把已接通的 ACTIVE_EXPERTS 转去 lowrank_expert_residual，测试 residual cleanup 是否比纯 routed topk 更需要多 expert。"],"notes_to_memory":["ACTIVE_EXPERTS 已完成最小必要接线：sparsify 配置/前向消费、override_registry、config_resolution、runner/runtime 持久化、audit/rebuild、scripts/autoresearch_test.sh 透传均已补齐。","expert_topk、factorized_expert_topk、lowrank_expert_topk、lowrank_expert_residual、two_stage_residual_expert 已本地 smoke 通过 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 的 forward/backward。","参数生效已验证：本地 validation run 的 checkpoint config.json 与 layer cfg.json 中都出现 active_experts=2；模拟的 round config 也解析出 active_experts=2。","当前 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 的 lowrank_expert_topk 成本估算约 total 0.73x，属于允许的中低成本结构性 anchor，而不是超预算点。"],"reference_round":60,"self_review":"这轮先修复了 r84 的真实 blocker，而不是把 override 拒绝误判成结构结论。相对 r60 的实际实验语义仍只新增一个 env 参数 ACTIVE_EXPERTS，因此归因保持单变量；代码改动也限制在允许范围内的 sparsify/、research/AutoResearch/、scripts/autoresearch_test.sh。主要风险是 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 会把 active expert scorer 成本从单 expert 提高到双 expert，total_cost 从约 0.48x 抬到约 0.73x；如果 FVU 改善不足，这条 MoE-like active-path 扩展线就应尽快收缩。","summary":"已修复 ACTIVE_EXPERTS 的端到端接线并完成本地验证，现在可以重跑原本被 r84 阻塞的最小 MoE-like probe。建议本轮以 r60 为 reference，只加 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2，直接回答 lowrank_expert_topk 的 multi-expert active path 是否值得继续。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/__main__.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/config_resolution.py","research/AutoResearch/runner.py","research/AutoResearch/rebuild_runtime_state.py","research/AutoResearch/controller.py","research/AutoResearch/policy.py","research/AutoResearch/prompt.py","research/AutoResearch/audit_history_execution.py","scripts/autoresearch_test.sh"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0108.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":107,"family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","expected_win":"lower_cost","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"LATENTS_PER_EXPERT","value":"320"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 B^sh 是始终激活的静态 shared 子库，E(x) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 routed experts，所有原子都来自静态向量库，因此在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。明确排除不兼容 family：`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled 结构不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r107 已证明 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 在 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=384, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 下形成新的低成本非支配点，约 0.42x total_cost 对应 FVU=0.1010，明显优于当前 `<0.5x` 主线 `lowrank_expert_topk K=96` 的 0.1305。下一步最有信息量的问题是这条 shared+routed 前沿还能否继续向左推进，而不是立刻回到旧 family 的 K/TRUNK_RANK 邻域。相对 r107 仅把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 384 降到 320，在保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`K=128`、`EF=1` 与其余训练配方不变时，按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，总成本将约从 0.42x 进一步降到 0.38x，仍远低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束；如果 FVU 仍显著优于当前 `<0.5x` anchor，则 shared+routed 将把新的结构性 Pareto 段继续向更低成本带延展。","summary":"Round 108 继续沿已形成新前沿的 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做单变量 left-shift。以 r107 为 reference，只把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 384 压到 320，直接测试这条 shared+routed 线能否从约 0.42x 进一步左移到约 0.38x，同时保持对当前 `<0.5x` 主线的明显质量优势。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r107 只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`。这不是重复无信息的同轴扫点，因为 r105 回答的是窄 expert 是否可行，r106 回答的是多 routed experts 是否有价值，r107 回答的是 shared+routed 能否在约 0.42x 形成新非支配点；本轮则是对这条已成立新结构段做第一次明确的 low-cost knee 定位。`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 已在 r105-r107 的 runtime config 与 checkpoint config 中真实生效，不需要 edit_sae_code。主要风险是 320 过窄导致 FVU 回退过多，但这同样是高价值结论，因为它会清楚界定 shared+routed 线在 `<0.5x` 区域的容量下限。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r107 已形成新的兼容前沿点：`shared_routed_expert_topk K=128 NUM_EXPERTS=64 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=384` 在约 0.42x total_cost 下达到 val_fvu=0.10104858130216599。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，`shared_routed_expert_topk K=128 NUM_EXPERTS=64 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 的 selection≈0.25x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.38x，明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算。","当前 `<0.5x` 最优质量已从 `lowrank_expert_topk` 转移到 shared+routed 线；本轮应优先界定这条新结构段的 left-shift 边界，而不是立即回到旧 family 的邻域微调。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 在约 0.38x 下仍把 FVU 控制在 0.11 左右或更低，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256` 或 `K=96`，继续细化 shared+routed 的低成本前沿。","如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 明显退化但仍优于 `lowrank_expert_topk`，则可回到 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=352` 或 `384`，把这条新前沿在 0.38x-0.42x 带内做更细的 knee 定位。","如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 退化到接近或差于当前旧主线，则可判定 shared+routed 在当前 target 的有效容量下限接近 384，后续应减少这条 family 的 left-shift，转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 做 matched 对照。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0045.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","reference_round":44,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"160"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再路由到单个静态 expert 子库做局部 sparse 选择，最后做全局 residual sparse 补偿，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路。兼容性判定：`lowrank_expert_residual` 为扩展兼容。本轮相对 r44 只改 `K: 192 -> 160`，主假设是 r44 在 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 下已经把质量压到 FVU≈0.13399，说明三段式结构在近低成本带仍有信号；若只小幅下调 sparse budget，就有机会把 total_cost 从约 0.52x 压到约 0.49x，同时把 FVU 保持在当前 <0.5x anchor 附近甚至更优，从而真正把这条结构线推进到低成本 frontier 内。","summary":"r44 已经证明 `lowrank_expert_residual` 在 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 时能以约 0.52x 成本达到 FVU≈0.13399，几乎贴住当前低成本最佳点。下一步最高信息量动作不是继续压 trunk，而是基于 r44 只下调 `K` 到 160，用最小部署压缩把该点直接推入 `<0.5x` 带，验证这条 `lowrank + expert + residual` 结构能否形成真正的低成本 Pareto 段。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r44 只修改 `K`。这不是在 old-family 上做无意义的 K 轴细扫，而是在当前最强结构线上做一次门槛穿越测试，因为 `TRUNK_RANK` 继续降低已几乎不再降总成本，而 `K` 是把 0.52x 压进 0.49x 的直接旋钮。风险是 r44 的 FVU 只比 `jumprelu K=248` 好约 0.00017，`K=160` 可能让质量回退；但这正是当前阶段最需要确认的 frontier 形状。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual K=192 TRUNK_RANK=16` 在 r44 取得 val_FVU≈0.133988，已非常接近当前低成本最佳 anchor。","按当前实现的成本估算，`lowrank_expert_residual K=160 EF=1 TRUNK_RANK=16` 的 selection≈0.32x、deployment≈0.17x、total≈0.49x，可进入当前重点关注的 `<0.5x` 区域。","在该 family 上继续降低 `TRUNK_RANK` 的边际成本收益已很小；若目标是跨入 `<0.5x` 带，`K` 比 `TRUNK_RANK` 更直接。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=160` 仍保持 FVU 不高于当前 `<0.5x` 最佳点 0.1342，则下一轮继续同 family，只改 `K=144`，测试这条结构前沿能否进一步向左延伸。","如果 `K=160` 的 FVU 明显恶化，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改回 `K=176`，寻找跨过 0.5x 阈值前的折中点。","如果 `K=160` 依然有竞争力，则后续再考虑只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，判断 expert 段与 residual 段的预算分配是否还能带来额外质量。"]}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0036.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"The stabilized gated regime has now improved both K=128 and K=64, so the next clean Pareto probe is to test whether that same family extends to K=32 and can displace the older JumpReLU low-K point. A gated K=32 proxy run under the same validated settings will show whether the current best family can dominate more of the frontier rather than remaining a high-K-only solution.","summary":"Run the stabilized gated configuration in proxy at K=32 with AUXK_ALPHA=0.01 to test whether the improved gated family can replace the current JumpReLU K=32 Pareto point.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"pareto","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This keeps the search on the strongest validated family and changes only K, which gives a clean low-K comparison against the existing frontier. The main risk is that gated may degrade too sharply at K=32, but that outcome is still useful for defining the family’s viable sparsity range.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.01"},{"key":"K","value":"32"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["The gated family now holds the best full results at both K=128 and K=64 under the stabilized AUXK_ALPHA=0.01 regime.","This round tests whether the same gated regime can also improve the K=32 Pareto point, potentially unifying the frontier under one family.","Using the same architecture, optimizer, learning rate, and expansion factor isolates K as the only changed variable for a direct comparison with the existing JumpReLU K=32 result."],"next_hypotheses":["If gated K=32 proxy is clearly better than the current JumpReLU K=32 point, promote it to full and treat gated as the new mainline family across the tested K range.","If gated K=32 is close but not clearly better, test whether reducing expansion factor improves the low-K tradeoff within the gated family.","If gated K=32 is substantially worse, keep gated focused on K>=64 and resume architecture exploration specifically for the ultra-low-K regime."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0087.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e(z)}(z)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 z = Bx 是共享低维投影，e(z) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{B_e} 对应若干静态 expert 子库，最终重构仍是静态向量库上的有限加权和。在线导出链路可写成“shared low-rank projection -> router 选静态 expert 子库 -> expert 内 low-rank head 做 local scoring/top-k -> 查表加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `factorized_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r74 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，在保持 `K=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，shared-basis expert routing 能在仍处于低到中成本带的前提下，比 routed-only `expert_topk` 更有效地利用子库容量，从而把当前低开销 Pareto 前沿向下推进。按当前成本模型粗估，selection 约 0.33x、deployment 约 0.16x、total 约 0.49x，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","summary":"Round 87 不回到旧 family 的 K 轴微调，而是用一个高信息量、已实现但当前 target 尚未充分验证的结构方向补低成本前沿：以 r74 为 matched reference，只切换到 `factorized_expert_topk`。这直接回答提示里优先级很高的“expert 内 low-rank / shared-basis routing”是否比 routed-only MoE-like 更值得继续。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r74 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这不是 plain selector 的重复扫点，也不是当前主线 family 的 K 邻域打磨，而是对高优先级未充分验证结构 `shared low-rank basis + expert-specific head` 的 matched probe。主要风险是 auto `factorized_hidden_dim` 可能让 selection cost 接近 0.5x 带上沿，且该 family 若训练不稳定，首次结果可能更多体现优化难度而非结构上限；因此保留 sanity 更稳妥。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`factorized_expert_topk` 的最终导出形式仍是静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和；共享低秩投影与 expert head 只改变在线打分链路，不引入动态字典。","这轮是对提示里高优先级方向“expert 内 low-rank / shared-basis expert routing”的直接 matched 验证，比继续细扫 `expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的旧轴信息增量更高。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 粗估，`factorized_expert_topk K=160 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=128` 的 total_cost 约 0.49x，正好落在当前最需要补强的低成本带。","如果 sanity 或训练异常，先把问题归因为该 family 的实现/稳定性，而不是把单次失败上升成对 shared-basis expert routing 方向的结构性否定。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 在近同成本下明显优于 r74，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=128`，测试这条 shared-basis routed 前沿能否继续向左延伸。","如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 优于 r74 但仍明显落后于 <0.5x 最优点，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS` 或 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，区分瓶颈是在总静态容量还是 shared basis 宽度。","如果结果不如 r74，则说明当前 target 上 shared-basis scorer 还不足以单独形成新前沿，后续更应把预算转向 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert` 这类带 residual cleanup 的结构。"],"reference_round":74}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0110.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":109,"family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","expected_win":"lower_cost","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"LATENTS_PER_EXPERT","value":"288"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 B^sh 是始终激活的静态 shared 子库，E(x) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 routed experts，所有原子都来自静态向量库，因此在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。明确排除不兼容 family：`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled 结构不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r107→r109 已经把 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的低成本前沿从约 0.42x 左移到约 0.34x，并表明 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 的 shared+routed 组合值得继续；但 r108→r109 的退化说明继续单纯压部署侧 `K` 可能已经开始伤害局部 lookup budget。相对 r109 仅把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 320 降到 288，在保持 `K=96`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`EF=1` 与其余训练配方不变时，按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，总成本将约从 0.34x 进一步降到 0.32x，而不再额外压缩 sparse lookup 预算；如果 FVU 明显优于当前 0.19x 的 `expert_topk K=128` 和现有 0.34x shared+routed 点，则说明 shared+routed 低成本线下一步更该从 encoder 宽度压缩而不是继续降 K。","summary":"Round 110 不再继续沿 `K` 轴直线左移，而是对当前最强的 shared+routed 低成本点做一次 encoder-side matched-cost probe。以 r109 为 reference，只把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 320 压到 288，直接回答这条新结构线在 `K=96, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 下更该压每-expert 宽度还是压查表预算。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r109 只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`。这不是重复 r107→r109 的同一假设：r108→r109 已经回答了继续降 `K` 的影响，而本轮专门把变量切回 encoder 宽度，目的是分离“lookup budget 不足”与“expert 宽度仍可压缩”这两个解释。`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 已在 r105-r109 的 runtime config 与 checkpoint config 中真实生效，不需要 edit_sae_code。主要风险是 288 过窄导致 FVU 明显劣于 r109；但这同样是高价值结论，因为它会直接表明当前 shared+routed 线在低成本带的下一步不应再压 expert 宽度，而应回到 `K` 或切到其他 family。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["本地兼容 frontier 已形成 shared+routed 的三段低成本线：r107 (`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=384, K=128`) FVU=0.1010、r108 (`320,128`) FVU=0.1072、r109 (`320,96`) FVU=0.1147。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，`shared_routed_expert_topk K=96 NUM_EXPERTS=64 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=288` 的 selection≈0.23x、deployment≈0.09x、total≈0.32x，明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算。","r108→r109 已显示继续降 `K` 会明显伤质量；本轮因此改做 encoder-side left-shift，判断 shared+routed 低成本线下一步更该压宽度还是压 lookup budget。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=288` 在约 0.32x 下仍把 FVU 控制在 0.12 左右或更低，则下一轮可保持 family 不变，只改 `K=80`，继续把 shared+routed 前沿向更低部署预算推进。","如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=288` 明显退化但仍优于 `expert_topk`，则可回到 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 并只改 `K=112`，确认 shared+routed 线的更优 knee 是否在 0.34x-0.36x 带。","如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=288` 劣于 r109 明显，则可初步判定当前 shared+routed 低成本线更缺 encoder 宽度而不是 lookup budget，后续不应继续压每-expert width，而应转向 `K`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 或 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 对照。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0030.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i。对 `jumprelu` 而言，JumpReLU 只改变支持集 S(x) 的形成方式，decoder 仍是同一个静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的查表 + 加权求和链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。r29 在与 topk K=192 相同的约 0.44x total_cost 上已经打到几乎持平的 FVU，因此下一步不该换 family，而应只改一个 JumpReLU 动态参数，让门限从默认 0 抬起，测试更强的支持整形能否把 0.44x 区域的 FVU 稳定压到明显低于 topk K=192。","summary":"基于 r29 的 jumprelu 配方做一次单变量动态参数 probe：仅设置 JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD=0.05，保持 ARCHITECTURE=jumprelu、K=192、EF=1、adam、8e-4 不变，验证轻度正门限是否能把已接近 topk 的 matched-cost 表现进一步推过当前 <0.5x 最优点。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"主要风险是正门限会削弱有效容量，导致性能从与 topk 持平退化回明显更差；但 r29 已证明该 family 在当前 target 的 0.44x 成本带值得做一次最小动态参数跟进，这一轮能直接回答 jumprelu 的优势是否只是偶然噪声。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD","value":"0.05"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["jumprelu 在当前 target 的 0.44x 成本带已与 topk K=192 基本持平，值得做一次单变量动态参数验证。","JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD 不改变 LUTurbo 导出形式，仍是单静态库有限加权和 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i。","本轮只提高初始门限，不改 K/EF/LR，避免把 family 价值判断和成本带变化混在一起。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD=0.05 能稳定优于 topk K=192，则下一轮继续留在 jumprelu，只改 JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH 做一次锐化/平滑对照。","如果这轮退化，则停止在 jumprelu 上继续局部微调，转向另一个未充分验证且仍处于低成本区的兼容 family。"],"reference_round":29}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0070.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Final reconstruction stays x_hat = sum_{r=1..R} beta_r(x) u_r + sum_{i in S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} alpha_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}, with t(x) = sum_{r=1..R} beta_r(x) u_r. This exports to the LUTurbo/Lottable path as a static trunk table lookup plus a single routed static expert sublibrary lookup plus a finite weighted sum, so `lowrank_expert_topk` is extended-compatible. Compatibility screen before proposing this round: `expert_topk` is directly compatible; `lowrank_expert_topk`, `lowrank_expert_residual`, and `two_stage_residual_expert` are extended-compatible; batch-coupled families such as `batch_topk` and `adaptive_budget_topk` are incompatible and must stay off the active frontier. Relative to r60, changing only `TRUNK_RANK` from 64 to 32 tests the missing mid-trunk point in the low-cost band: if the routed-only improvement from r59 to r60 was not all-or-nothing, this should recover much of r60's FVU while moving left from the current lowrank+expert anchor and potentially create a new compatible Pareto segment between `expert_topk` and `lowrank_expert_residual`.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["If `TRUNK_RANK=32` keeps most of r60 quality at materially lower total_cost, next do a matched `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual` switch from this point to measure whether residual cleanup is still worth paying for at the same trunk width.","If `TRUNK_RANK=32` falls back close to the routed-only `expert_topk` band, treat that as evidence that `lowrank_expert_topk` has a sharp trunk-width floor and shift low-cost budget back to `lowrank_expert_residual` or pure `expert_topk` rather than more MoE-capacity expansion.","If throughput or convergence looks anomalous rather than simply worse, use a follow-up midpoint such as `TRUNK_RANK=48` before drawing a structural conclusion."],"notes_to_memory":["Round 70 targets the under-mapped low-to-mid-cost region with a structural width probe, not another plain-K sweep.","`lowrank_expert_topk` now has informative anchors at `TRUNK_RANK=16` and `64` under `K=128, NUM_EXPERTS=32`; `TRUNK_RANK=32` is the clean missing midpoint for the same compatible family.","Keep incompatible batch-coupled families excluded from frontier accounting; active frontier decisions should continue to use only direct-compatible and extended-compatible families."],"reference_round":60,"self_review":"This satisfies the single-variable param-only rule and stays within an already implemented compatible family. It directly answers a higher-value structural question than another `expert_topk` K move, and it avoids spending Round 70 on further local polishing of the current `lowrank_expert_residual` mainline after r66 already showed diminishing returns from more trunk compression there.","summary":"Use Round 70 for a low-cost structural probe in `lowrank_expert_topk`: start from r60 and only reduce `TRUNK_RANK` to 32. The goal is to map whether shared low-rank trunk width can produce a new compatible Pareto point in the 0.3x-0.5x band, instead of continuing plain-selector K sweeps or more local cleanup on `lowrank_expert_residual`.","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0104.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","reference_round":103,"env_overrides":[{"key":"NUM_EXPERTS","value":"64"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 B^sh 是始终激活的静态 shared 子库，E(x) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 routed experts，所有原子都来自静态向量库，因此在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。唯一主假设：r103 已证明 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 能稳定训练并在约 total_cost=0.63x 取得 FVU=0.1188，接下来最有信息量的问题是它是否仍受 routed 总容量限制；相对 r103 仅把 `NUM_EXPERTS: 32 -> 64`，保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 的短激活路径与其余 recipe 不变，如果 shared+routed MoE-like 方向确实值得继续，则应在几乎同一成本带（fresh cost 约 selection=0.52x、deployment=0.12x、total=0.64x）进一步压低 FVU。","summary":"沿 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做第一次真实容量扩展 probe：相对 r103 只增大 `NUM_EXPERTS`，直接判断 shared+routed 结构在保持短 active path 时是否还有 sparse-capacity 收益。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r103 只改 `NUM_EXPERTS`。这不是回到旧 family 的 K 轴细扫，而是对刚验证可运行的新 MoE-like family 做最核心的结构问题测试；同时 fresh cost 已核对仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","needs_sanity":true,"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r103 已确认 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 可稳定训练，最近两轮 crash 不是该 family 前向/反向实现问题。","本轮以 r103 为 reference，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=64`，用于判断 shared+routed 结构是否仍受 routed static capacity 限制。","fresh cost 估算：`shared_routed_expert_topk K=128 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=64` 的 selection≈0.52x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.64x，仍在允许的 0.3x-0.8x 结构 anchor 带内。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=64` 明显优于 r103，则 shared+routed 路线值得继续，下一步再考虑叠加 low-rank trunk。","如果结果与 r103 接近或更差，则说明 trunk-free shared+routed 线已接近饱和，后续不应继续把预算投在这条 family 的容量扩张上。","如果本轮再次出现参数落地异常，应优先检查 round config 与 checkpoint config 中 `num_experts=64` 是否真实生效，再决定是否继续该 family。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0071_repair_1.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":69,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e(h(x))}(h(x))} α_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低维投影，e(h(x)) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{b_{e,i}} 是各 expert 的静态子库原子。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的链路仍是：共享低维投影 -> router 选单个静态 expert 子库 -> expert 内 local top-k -> 静态库有限加权和，因此 `factorized_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容。兼容性结论不变：`expert_topk` 为直接兼容，`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert` 与 `factorized_expert_topk` 为扩展兼容，`batch_topk`/`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch-coupled family 为不兼容，不能进入当前 frontier。此次 repair 不改实验设计；只修复 Round 71 的工程性阻塞，使相对 r69 仅切换 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk` 的原始实验能够真正实例化、前向和反向运行。","summary":"按 repair checklist 修复 `factorized_expert_topk` 的架构注册链与最小实现：补上 config whitelist、factory dispatch 和 concrete class，保持原始 family 与 env_overrides 不变。已用失败时相同的 `(architecture=factorized_expert_topk, K=160, EF=1)` 完成 instantiate/forward/backward smoke，原始实验现在可以继续运行。","self_review":"本次修复遵守 repair 模式要求，没有重新设计实验，也没有改 family_name 或 env_overrides。改动限制在 `sparsify/` 两个必要文件；阻塞根因是 `Unknown architecture`，因此没有扩展到 AutoResearch wiring。精确 smoke 已通过，说明当前 blocker 已从注册链问题解除；如果后续真实训练再失败，应把它视为新的实现或训练层 blocker，而不是继续当作 architecture registration 问题。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 71 repair-1 根因是 `factorized_expert_topk` 未加入 `valid_archs` 与 `_get_sae_class()`，且 concrete class 缺失。","已实现最小 `factorized_expert_topk`：共享 `factor_encoder` 做低维投影，router 在低维空间选单 expert，active expert head 做 local top-k，decoder 仍为静态原子库。","精确 sanity 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='factorized_expert_topk', k=160, expansion_factor=1)` 在 CUDA 上完成 forward/backward。","当前 fresh cost 估算为 encoder≈0.08x、deployment≈0.16x、total≈0.23x，明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束；后续应以真实训练结果而不是旧 family 先验判断该结构价值。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果真实训练正常完成且 FVU 明显优于 r69 `expert_topk`，下一轮再在同 family 内验证共享 basis 宽度是否为主控制旋钮。","如果真实训练失败但不再是 `Unknown architecture`，应按新失败模式进入下一次 repair，而不是重复注册链修复。","如果真实训练可跑但质量很弱，应把它当作结构负信号，而不是工程阻塞。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0066.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判断为扩展兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r65 仅把 TRUNK_RANK 从 32 降到 24，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`、`K=128`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EF=1` 不变时，继续压缩 encoder 与部署侧的 trunk 成本；如果 r65 的收益主要来自“三段式结构本身”而非 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 这个具体宽度，则该点应以更低 total_cost 保住大部分质量，并在 <0.5x 带形成更靠左的新 Pareto 点。","summary":"r65 已经证明把 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 trunk 从 64 压到 32 仍能保住可用质量，并把 total_cost 拉回 0.49x。Round 66 不改 family、不改 K，只继续小步压 `TRUNK_RANK`，直接回答这条三段式结构还能否在低成本带进一步左移。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r65 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。该 family 属于 LUTurbo 扩展兼容 family，不触碰不兼容方向，也不需要新增 tunable 参数接线。选择 `TRUNK_RANK=24` 而不是再次压 `K` 或切 family，是因为 r65 已经给出正信号，而最近对 `K`、`STAGE1_RATIO` 和 `two_stage_residual_expert` 的尝试都没有带来更优结构性信息；当前最清晰的问题是 r65 这条新低成本三段式前沿还能否继续左移。主要风险是 trunk 再压缩后 FVU 回退过多；但即便如此，也能较清晰地界定这条 family 在当前 target 上的最小可用 trunk 宽度。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"24"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 目前已在 `TRUNK_RANK=32, K=128, NUM_EXPERTS=32` 下拿到新的 0.49x 低成本锚点；下一步优先判断它能否继续左移，而不是再做 family 切换。","Round 66 是对 r65 的纯 encoder-cost compression probe：只降 `TRUNK_RANK`，保持其他结构预算不变。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=24` 仍保住接近 r65 的 FVU，则说明这条三段式结构在当前 target 上仍有低成本压缩空间。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `TRUNK_RANK=24` 仍接近 r65，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 或 `TRUNK_RANK=28/32`，细化三段式低成本 Pareto 段。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=24` 明显退化，则说明 r65 附近已接近这条 family 的低成本极限；后续低成本预算应回投 `lowrank_expert_topk` 或新的 MoE-like 方向。","如果结果异常，先核对 round config 与 checkpoint config 中 `trunk_rank=24` 是否真实生效，再决定是否把该轮当作结构证据。"],"reference_round":65}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0095.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":94,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"40"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。在线侧仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单个静态 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容；`expert_topk` 属于直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 属于不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：r94 已证明把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从 64 压到 48 后，`lowrank + expert` 仍能在更低 total_cost 带形成新的可行点，说明 shared trunk 仍有压缩空间。相对 r94 仅将 `TRUNK_RANK: 48 -> 40`，若当前 Pareto knee 还未到达，则 FVU 应只小幅高于 0.1151，且能把这条兼容前沿继续左移到更低成本带，从而回答 `lowrank + expert` 的最小可用 shared trunk 是否已接近 40。","summary":"r94 刚在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上补出新的更低成本前沿点，因此本轮不切 family，也不回到 routed-only active-path 或 `factorized_expert_topk` 这些已给出负信号的方向。以 r94 为 reference，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=40`，继续精化这条 `lowrank + expert` 低成本线的 shared-trunk knee，优先争取新的更靠左非支配点。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r94 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。这不是旧 family 的 K 轴细扫，而是对刚刚取得正信号的兼容结构线做最小且高信息量的延伸。选择 40 而不是更激进的 32，是因为 r70 已表明 32 明显过薄；当前更合理的问题是 knee 是否位于 40-48 区间。主要风险是 40 仍会明显劣化，导致这轮只能得出“48 已接近最小可用 trunk”的结论；但这同样有价值，因为它能收敛后续低成本预算。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r94 (`lowrank_expert_topk TRUNK_RANK=48`) 以更低成本换到 FVU=0.1151，说明这条 `lowrank + expert` 线的 shared trunk 压缩并未在 48 处失效。","r93 (`expert_topk ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`) 仍是明确负信号，因此后续低成本预算不应继续投向 routed-only multi-expert active-path 扩展。","`factorized_expert_topk` 在 r90-r92 上稳定偏弱，当前优先级继续低于 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 trunk-knee 精化。","本轮若 `TRUNK_RANK=40` 仍能保住大部分质量，则说明当前 target 上 `lowrank + expert` 的可用 trunk 宽度还可继续低于 48。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `TRUNK_RANK=40` 继续形成非支配点，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=36`，完成这条低成本 knee 的更细分辨率搜索。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=40` 明显劣于 r94，则可初步判定这条 family 的最小可用 trunk 更接近 48；下一轮应停止继续压该轴，转去做 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert` 对照。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=40` 与 r94 基本持平但成本改善有限，则说明该 family 对 trunk 宽度已进入平台区，后续应减少局部压缩预算，转向更高信息量的结构切换。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0013.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"160"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式固定为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i。`topk` 的在线侧只输出稀疏支持集 S(x) 与对应系数 α_i(x)，离线侧字典库 B={b_i} 保持静态不随样本生成，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态向量查表加权和推理链路，兼容性判定为直接兼容。本轮相对 r12 仅改 `K: 128 -> 160`，回答一个问题：在 `EF=1` 的同一 encoder 成本槽位下，把 deployment 预算从约 0.12x 再抬到约 0.15x 后，`topk` 的 Pareto 改善是否仍然存在，且训练曲线后段是否继续下行而不是开始明显饱和。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=160` 仍带来清晰改善，则说明当前 `topk, EF=1` 在 <0.5x 成本带内 deployment-side frontier 仍未走平，后续可再做一次更高 K 探针或与其他直接兼容 family 做同成本对比。","如果 `K=160` 收益已经很小或曲线明显早饱和，则说明当前主线 family 在该结构槽位上的 deployment 增益开始递减，后续应停止继续抬 K，转向其他兼容 family 或高优先级未充分验证的轻量 expert 子库 / MoE-like 方向。"],"notes_to_memory":["`topk` 为直接兼容 family；导出形式保持为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i`，满足 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态库有限加权和约束。","Round 13 继续只改 `K`，避免混入 optimizer/LR/family 变化，优先确认 deployment 成本轴在当前低成本带内的边际收益是否继续存在。","按当前 proxy 线性近似，`K=160` 的 deployment 成本约 0.15x，总成本约 0.40x（0.25x + 0.15x），仍明显低于 1.5x 硬约束，也仍处于 <0.5x 成本带。"],"reference_round":12,"self_review":"满足单轮单参数变更约束；相对 r12 只修改了 `K`。继续沿 `K` 方向而不是切 family，是因为 r11→r12 刚给出显著且可解释的 deployment-side 收益，当前最有信息量的问题仍是该收益在 0.38x 之后是否开始变平。","summary":"继续主线 `topk`。其最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i`，可直接导出为 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态字典查表加权和，因此属于直接兼容。Round 13 以 r12 为参考，只把 `K` 从 128 提到 160，在不改变 encoder 成本的前提下继续测 deployment 预算增加后的边际收益，并重点观察训练曲线是否显示开始饱和。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0097.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":95,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"112"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单个静态 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容；`expert_topk` 属于直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 属于不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：r95 (`K=128`) 与 r96 (`K=96`) 已经把当前有效主线 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 deployment-knee 两端都测出来，但中间缺少 `K=112` 这个最关键的边界点。相对 r95 仅将 `K: 128 -> 112`，在保持 `TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变时，如果当前质量退化主要发生在 `K<112` 之后，那么 `K=112` 应能明显优于 r96 的 0.1305，同时把 total_cost 从 r95 的同配方进一步左移到约 0.43x（按当前 fresh cost 粗估），从而完成 `K=96-128` 边界定位。","summary":"当前不要继续细扫 `TRUNK_RANK`，也不要回到 routed-only 或 `factorized_expert_topk` 这些已给出负信号的方向。以 r95 为 reference，只改 `K=112`，把 `lowrank_expert_topk` 当前主线 recipe 的 `K=96-128` 压缩边界补完整；这是 operator guide 明确要求优先完成的 knee 定位步骤。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r95 只改 `K`。这不是 old-family 的普通 K 轴回退，因为当前 <0.5x 有效主线已经明确是 `lowrank_expert_topk`，且 r95/r96 正好留下一个高信息量的边界缺口。主要风险是 `K=112` 结果只是落在 r95 和 r96 的平滑插值线上而不形成新的非支配点；但即便如此，也能完成当前阶段明确要求的 `K=96-128` knee 定位，避免继续在未封口的边界上盲目切 family。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r95 (`lowrank_expert_topk TRUNK_RANK=40 K=128`) 与 r96 (`K=96`) 已证明当前低成本主线的 deployment budget 不是全-or-nothing，而是存在可继续压缩的空间。","当前 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 K 轴还缺少 `K=112` 这一中间点；补齐它比立即切去 `lowrank_expert_residual` 更符合 Round 97 的 runtime priority。","`factorized_expert_topk` 与 routed-only `ACTIVE_EXPERTS>1` 方向都已给出稳定负信号，本轮继续留在当前有效主线上更合理。","按当前 fresh cost 粗估，`lowrank_expert_topk K=112 NUM_EXPERTS=32 TRUNK_RANK=40` 的 selection 基本不变，deployment 低于 `K=128`，total_cost 约 0.43x，仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=112` 形成新的非支配中间点，则 `K=96-128` 边界已基本完成，下一轮应切到 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 结构对照，而不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上细扫。","如果 `K=112` 基本贴着 r95-r96 的平滑插值且不形成新前沿，则说明当前 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 deployment-knee 已足够清楚；下一轮同样应切到 matched `lowrank_expert_residual`。","如果 `K=112` 意外明显劣化并接近 r96，则可判定当前主线对 deployment budget 比预期更敏感；下一轮应回到 `K=128` 配方，并优先测试 matched residual cleanup 是否值得其额外成本。"]}
