research/history/logs/agent_action_0047.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","reference_round":46,"env_overrides":[{"key":"STAGE1_RATIO","value":"0.125"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再路由到单个静态 expert 子库做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差做全局 sparse cleanup，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路。兼容性判定：`lowrank_expert_residual` 为扩展兼容。本轮相对 r46 仅改 `STAGE1_RATIO: 0.25 -> 0.125`，主假设是当前低成本点的主要瓶颈仍是两段 sparse 预算分配不够偏向全局 residual cleanup；把 stage1 expert 预算进一步压低到约 20/160、把更多 K 留给 stage2，全成本基本不变在约 0.49x，但有机会把 FVU 从 r46 的 0.1366 拉回到接近或优于当前 `<0.5x` anchor 0.1342。","summary":"r45 到 r46 说明在 `K=160, TRUNK_RANK=16` 的低成本点上，把 `STAGE1_RATIO` 从默认 0.5 压到 0.25 确实能回收一部分质量，问题更像是预算分配而不是结构本身立即失效。下一步最有信息量的动作是继续沿同一条低成本结构线只降 `STAGE1_RATIO` 到 0.125，测试更强的“少量 expert 局部修正 + 大量全局 residual cleanup”是否才是这个成本带的正确配方。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r46 只修改 `STAGE1_RATIO`。这轮保持 `K=160` 与 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 不变，因此 total_cost 基本不变，归因清晰；若 FVU 继续改善，就说明当前 `<0.5x` 区域的关键旋钮确实是 staged budget split。风险是把 stage1 压得过低可能削弱 expert 子库的价值；但在 r45->r46 已呈现“更低 stage1_ratio 更好”的方向性后，继续向 0.125 试探比改回 0.375 或重新扫 K 更符合当前证据。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是 trunk 静态库 + expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。","在 `K=160, TRUNK_RANK=16` 下继续调整 `STAGE1_RATIO` 不改变总 K，因此 total_cost 仍基本维持在约 0.49x。","r45 FVU≈0.1436，r46 FVU≈0.1366，说明在当前低成本点把更多预算给 stage2 residual cleanup 是有效方向，值得再向 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.125` 继续验证。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.125` 能把 FVU 压到不高于当前 `<0.5x` 最佳点 0.1342，则下一轮保持该 budget split，只改 `K=168`，测试这条结构线能否在约 0.50x 处获得更稳质量。","如果 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.125` 反而变差，则说明最优 split 可能在 0.125 和 0.25 之间；下一轮保持同 family，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.1875`。","如果继续下调 stage1_ratio 仍无法追回 r44 的质量，则应把这视为该 family 在 0.49x 带的结构极限信号，之后转回其他高优先级结构方向。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0021.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i。`factorized_topk` 只改变在线打分链路为 h(x)=ReLU(W1x), scores=W2h(x) 后做 top-k，decoder 仍是单个静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理流水线，兼容性=直接兼容。r20 已证明在极低成本 0.28x 处它能给出新的兼容 frontier 点；本轮主假设是保持低秩 scorer 宽度不变，仅增加 `K` 到 192，把节省下来的 encoder 成本转移到部署查表侧，能在仍处于低成本区的前提下显著降低 FVU，补出 0.3x 左右的新 Pareto 点。","summary":"相对 r20 的完整配置，本轮只改一个 env 参数：`K=192`。保持 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_topk`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变，专门测 cheap scorer + 更高 sparse budget 的质量斜率。预计 total_cost 约从 0.28x 提升到 0.31x（selection 仍约 0.12x，deployment 约从 0.16x 升到 0.19x）。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"这轮不是继续压 encoder 成本，而是验证 r20 的低选择成本是否真能换成更有效的部署预算。风险是 hidden_dim=256 可能已成为主要瓶颈，单纯加 K 只带来有限收益；但这是当前最干净的单变量测试，能直接回答 factorized_topk 的 Pareto 斜率是否优于 topk。若收益很弱，下一轮应停止继续堆 K，转而回到 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或切换到其他未充分验证 family。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"192"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：`factorized_topk` 为直接兼容；最终导出形式不变，仍是单静态向量库上的有限加权和。","reference_round 选 r20，因为本轮要隔离 `K` 对同一 family 的影响；只改 1 个 env 参数，满足 param_only 单变量规则。","r20 在 0.28x 已优于 topk 的最低成本点，说明 factorized scorer 至少在当前 target 的超低成本带有信号；本轮继续测其沿部署成本方向的 frontier 斜率。","成本预估：K=192, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, EF=1 时，selection 约 0.12x、deployment 约 0.19x、total 约 0.31x，仍位于当前优先补强的 <0.5x 区域。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果本轮在约 0.31x 处明显优于现有 topk 低成本点，下一轮继续以该 family 自身最好点为 reference_round，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `K` 细化局部前沿。","如果本轮收益有限，说明 hidden_dim=256 已成主瓶颈；下一轮应回到 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 调整，或转向当前 target 上尚未充分验证的其他低成本兼容 family。"],"reference_round":20}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0008.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"A softer JumpReLU gate may recover stable throughput and improve proxy FVU versus the failed sharp-gating attempt by widening the bandwidth around the current best K=128 anchor without changing architecture or optimizer.","summary":"Stay on the best known working JumpReLU K=128 configuration and run a single softer-gating proxy check by increasing gate bandwidth slightly, keeping the round focused on stability recovery and a clean read on threshold dynamics.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"quality","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This stays within crash-recovery constraints and makes only a minor parameter adjustment on the current best working family. The main risk is that bandwidth softening may be too small to move FVU materially, but it is the safest informative step after consecutive crashes and the prior perf regression.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"jumprelu"},{"key":"JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD","value":"0.15"},{"key":"JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH","value":"0.15"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 8 used crash-recovery param-only mode and stayed on the best working JumpReLU K=128 anchor.","Tested a softer JumpReLU gate by widening bandwidth from 0.1 to 0.15 while keeping the threshold at 0.15 to separate stability effects from architecture changes.","This round is intended to check whether the round-3 regression came from overly sharp gating rather than from JumpReLU itself."],"next_hypotheses":["If wider-bandwidth JumpReLU improves proxy FVU with normal throughput, continue stabilizing within JumpReLU with another small gate-shape adjustment before any K reduction.","If throughput recovers but quality is flat or worse, try a small LR adjustment on the best JumpReLU anchor rather than more aggressive threshold changes.","If this softer-gating proxy still underperforms, pause JumpReLU-local sweeps until crash recovery ends and then revisit broader architecture exploration."],"primary_variable":"other_param"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0026.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e*(x)}(x)} α_i(x) b_{e*(x),i}，其中 e*(x) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert 子库，S_{e*(x)}(x) 是该静态子库内的局部 top-k 支持集。在线导出仍是“router 选 1 个静态 expert 子库 + 在该子库内查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”，因此对 LUTurbo/Lottable 属于扩展兼容。r25 显示 `expert_topk` 从 K=64 到 K=128 有明显改善，而 selection 成本基本不变；本轮主假设是仅把 `K` 提到 192，能在 total_cost 约 0.25x 的超低成本区继续显著压低 FVU，并判断这条 MoE-like 路线是否值得保留为低成本前沿候选。","summary":"相对 r25 的完整配置，本轮只改一个 env 参数：`K=192`。保持 `ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变，专门测单 expert 局部预算继续增大后的质量斜率。预计 total_cost 约从 0.19x 升到 0.25x（selection 约 0.06x，deployment 约 0.19x）。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮仍然是对新 family 的最小单变量延伸，不重新设计结构。风险是 `expert_topk` 的瓶颈并不在局部 K，而在 router 或子库划分；如果 K=192 仍没有把 FVU 压到接近现有低成本点，就应停止继续堆 K，转向别的兼容 family 或更合理的轻量路由实现。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"192"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：`expert_topk` 结构上为扩展兼容；最终导出形式是静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和。","reference_round 选 r25，因为当前 target 上 `expert_topk K=128 EF=1` 已有可用结果；本轮只改 `K`，满足 param_only 单变量规则。","r25 在 total_cost≈0.19x 处把 FVU 从 0.3636 降到 0.3149，说明当前 prototype 至少对局部 sparse budget 有响应，值得再补一个更低成本 anchor。","按当前实现的成本估计，`expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 的 selection≈0.06x、deployment≈0.19x、total≈0.25x，仍显著低于当前已知 frontier 的最低成本点。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `expert_topk` 在 0.25x 处继续明显改善，下一轮可再沿同一家族把 `K` 推到 256，确认低成本 Pareto 斜率是否持续。","如果这轮改善有限，则判定当前 fixed-4-expert/1-active prototype 已接近结构瓶颈，后续不再仅靠增 K 打磨该 family。"],"reference_round":25}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0074.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","reference_round":73,"env_overrides":[{"key":"NUM_EXPERTS","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_e Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 e(x) 由轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“router 选单个静态子库 + 子库内 local top-k + 查表加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `expert_topk` 属于直接兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert`、`factorized_expert_topk` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能继续驱动 frontier。相对 r73 仅把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 64 提到 128，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk`、`K=160`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，继续回答当前低成本带最关键的问题：如果 r73 的改善来自 true sparse-capacity MoE-like 扩容仍未吃满，而不是偶然训练波动，那么进一步放大总静态 expert 容量、同时保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 和相同查表路径长度，应能在近同一 total_cost 下继续压低 FVU，并把这条直接兼容的 routed-only 前沿继续向下推进。","summary":"Round 74 不回到旧 family 的 K 轴，也不立刻切去别的结构；沿 r73 的正信号继续做单变量 sparse-capacity continuation。只把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 提到 128，直接判断 routed-only MoE-like 前沿的容量收益是否还在持续，而成本仍预计留在 <0.5x 的低成本带。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r73 只改 `NUM_EXPERTS`。这一步比回头细扫 `K` 更符合当前阶段的结构问题，因为 r73 已经证明在 `K=160` 固定时容量扩容是有效方向。主要风险是 `expert_topk` 在 `NUM_EXPERTS=64` 后已接近收益饱和，但这正是本轮要回答的内容；若改善停止，就可以更有把握地结束 routed-only 容量线，而不是继续模糊投入。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式保持为静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和，兼容性仍为直接兼容。","r73 已表明把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 32 提到 64 在 `K=160`、`EF=1` 下能把 FVU 从 0.1334 压到 0.1260，说明 routed-only 容量扩容在当前 target 上仍有正信号。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，`expert_topk K=160 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=128` 的成本约为 selection 0.28x、deployment 0.16x、total 0.44x，仍处于本轮要求的低成本带内，且明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=128` 继续改善，则 routed-only MoE-like 将形成一条更完整的低成本直接兼容前沿；如果不再改善，可把后续预算更明确转回带 trunk 或 residual cleanup 的结构。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=128` 在近同成本下继续明显优于 r73，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=256`，确认 routed capacity 收益何时饱和。","如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=128` 改善很弱或停止，则可较清晰判定当前 `expert_topk` 的低成本瓶颈已不主要在总子库容量，后续应把结构预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `factorized_expert_topk` 这类带 shared basis / residual cleanup 的兼容方向。","如果结果异常，先核对 `round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `num_experts=128` 已真实生效，再决定是否把该轮当作结构证据。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0017.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"384"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式固定为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i。`topk` 的在线侧只输出稀疏支持集 S(x) 与对应系数 α_i(x)，离线侧字典库 B={b_i} 保持静态且不随样本动态生成，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态向量查表加权和推理链路，兼容性判定为直接兼容。本轮相对 r16 仅改 `K: 320 -> 384`，回答一个问题：当 deployment 预算从约 0.31x 提到约 0.38x、总成本从约 0.56x 提到约 0.63x 后，`topk, EF=1` 的 deployment-side frontier 是否仍有清晰 Pareto 改善，且训练曲线后段是否继续稳定下行而不是开始明显变平。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=384` 仍有明确改善，则说明当前 `topk, EF=1` 在 0.5x 以上成本带仍未走平，后续可再做一次更高 K 探针到 `K=512`，或在相近总成本下引入其他兼容 family 做横向对比。","如果 `K=384` 收益明显减弱或曲线后段变平，则说明 deployment 增益开始递减，后续应停止继续抬 `K`，优先转向其他兼容 family 或高优先级未充分验证的轻量 expert 子库 / MoE-like 方向。"],"notes_to_memory":["`topk` 为直接兼容 family；导出形式保持为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i`，满足 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态库有限加权和约束。","Round 17 继续只改 `K`，避免引入 optimizer/LR/family 混杂；当前目标是确认 deployment 轴在 0.56x 以上总成本带内是否开始明显变平。","按当前 proxy 线性近似，`K=384` 的 deployment 成本约 0.38x，总成本约 0.63x（0.25x + 0.38x），显著低于 1.5x 硬约束。"],"reference_round":16,"self_review":"满足单轮单参数变更约束；相对 r16 只修改了 `K`。选择 `K=384` 而不是直接跳到 `K=512`，是为了继续保持 deployment 轴归因清晰，并用一个中间点确认 0.56x 以上成本带的边际收益是否已经开始明显递减。","summary":"继续主线 `topk`。其最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i`，可直接导出为 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态字典查表加权和，因此属于直接兼容。Round 17 以 r16 为参考，只把 `K` 从 320 提到 384，在不改变 encoder 成本的前提下测试更高总成本带上的 deployment 边际收益，并重点观察训练曲线是否开始明显饱和。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0007.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"A gated SAE that decouples latent support selection from reconstruction magnitude can beat the current JumpReLU anchor at K=128 by learning a separate sigmoid routing branch while staying initialization-close to plain ReLU top-k.","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["If gated shows better proxy FVU at acceptable throughput, stabilize the family by exposing and tuning gate temperature/init strength in a follow-up.","If gated quality is promising but throughput regresses, keep the family alive and do a performance-focused follow-up rather than discarding the architecture.","If gated fails to improve proxy FVU, move on to a different routing-focused family instead of more JumpReLU-local sweeps."],"notes_to_memory":["Added a new `gated` SAE family under `sparsify/` with a second encoder branch that produces sigmoid gates for support selection.","The gate branch is initialized with zero weights and a positive bias so the prototype starts close to plain ReLU top-k rather than an aggressively sparse regime.","Current execution-layer hooks do not expose gated-specific env knobs, so this first prototype relies on default `gated_temperature=1.0` and `gated_init_logit=2.0`."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"This is a clean single-family prototype and respects the proxy-first policy, but it adds a second encoder matmul so throughput may regress; that risk is acceptable for one exploratory proxy round because recent local JumpReLU tuning already failed.","summary":"Prototype a new `gated` architecture at the K=128 anchor by adding a separate sigmoid routing branch, keeping all other launch settings at baseline so the round cleanly measures whether decoupled support selection can open a better quality regime than JumpReLU.","touched_files":["/root/sparsify-ascend/sparsify/config.py","/root/sparsify-ascend/sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0080.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(r_1)}(r_1)} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 r_1 = x - Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i，B={b_i} 是静态 coarse library，C_e={c_{e,j}} 是静态 expert residual 子库，e(r_1) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“coarse 查表 + expert residual 子库查表 + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `two_stage_residual_expert` 属于扩展兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert`、`factorized_expert_topk` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。r77、r78、r79 已连续给出清晰负信号：shared-basis `factorized_expert_topk` 明显弱于 matched `expert_topk`，routed-only `expert_topk` 提高 `K` 进一步退化，而 `lowrank_expert_residual` 把 `STAGE1_RATIO` 从 0.25 提到 0.5 也变差，说明当前低到中成本带的主要问题已不太像 routed-only scorer、lookup budget 或 expert-stage 预算不足。相对 r76 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=128`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变，直接回答当前高优先级结构问题：在已经给足 sparse-capacity `NUM_EXPERTS=64` 的条件下，low-rank trunk 是否仍然是当前 target 的必要组成，还是“coarse global library + routed expert residual”这条 trunk-free staged 结构已足够形成新的低到中成本 Pareto 段。如果后者成立，这个 matched architecture probe 应在约同一成本带内接近 r76；如果仍明显落后，则可更干净地判定当前 target 上 low-rank trunk 的价值已被重新验证。","summary":"Round 80 不继续沿 `lowrank_expert_residual` 做局部旋钮细扫，也不回到已给出负信号的 routed-only 或 shared-basis 线；而是做一次高信息量 matched architecture probe。以 r76 为 reference，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 切到 `two_stage_residual_expert`，其余 `K=128, NUM_EXPERTS=64, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25, EF=1, adam, lr=8e-4` 全部保持不变，直接测试在 true sparse-capacity 条件下 trunk-free staged 结构是否值得继续。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r76 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这比继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 上扫 `TRUNK_RANK` 或回到 `expert_topk`/`factorized_expert_topk` 更符合当前阶段的结构扩展优先级，因为最近三轮已经分别对 shared-basis、routed-only lookup-budget、以及三段式 stage split 给出负信号；现在更值得回答的是 low-rank trunk 本身是否仍是必要组成。主要风险是 `two_stage_residual_expert` 在较小容量 recipe 下已有弱信号，而参考配置中的 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 对新 family 实际不生效，因此这是“训练 recipe matched、结构语义不含 trunk”的对照，而不是严格共享所有有效结构参数的配方；但这正是本轮需要的结构归因。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_stage_residual_expert"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`two_stage_residual_expert` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是静态 coarse library 加静态 expert residual 子库上的有限加权和，兼容性为扩展兼容。","本轮是对 r76 的 matched architecture probe：保持 `K=128 / NUM_EXPERTS=64 / STAGE1_RATIO=0.25 / EF=1 / adam / 8e-4` 不变，只切换到 `two_stage_residual_expert`，直接测试在 true sparse-capacity 条件下 low-rank trunk 是否仍然必要。","r77、r78、r79 已连续否定 shared-basis、routed-only lookup-budget、以及更高 expert-stage 预算这三条解释，因此当前最有信息量的问题是 trunk 本身的必要性，而不是继续打磨现有 family 的局部旋钮。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 代码路径估算，`two_stage_residual_expert K=128 NUM_EXPERTS=64 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 的总成本约在 0.64x 附近，仍处于允许保留的低到中成本解释性带内，并显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `two_stage_residual_expert` 在近同成本下接近或优于 r76，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或 `K`，判断 staged sparse 结构是否能继续向更低成本带推进。","如果它明显弱于 r76，则可较清晰判定当前 target 上 low-rank trunk 仍是必要组成；后续应把结构预算收回到 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 `TRUNK_RANK` 轴，而不是继续展开 trunk-free staged family。","如果结果异常，先核对 `round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `architecture=two_stage_residual_expert` 已真实生效，再决定是否把该轮当作结构证据。"],"reference_round":76}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0006.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"切到直接兼容 family `whitened_topk`，最终重构公式仍为 `x_hat = Σ_{i in S(x)} α_i(x) b_i`。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时，`{b_i}` 仍是单个静态向量库；在线只是在选择前增加确定性的预处理/归一化与固定低秩预条件路径，然后继续做 top-k 选择、系数计算、查表 `W b_i`、加权求和，因此仍能落到现有“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路。本轮相对 r1 仅修改 `ARCHITECTURE`，测试在仍处于 `<0.5x` 区域的更高结构槽位下，预处理是否能换来明显更低 FVU。","summary":"兼容性判断：`whitened_topk` 为直接兼容。当前 `topk / factorized_topk / jumprelu` 在 `~0.31x` 同成本槽位已给出连续负或近零增益信号，继续在该槽位做同类 probe 的信息密度开始下降。`whitened_topk@K=64,EF=1` 的本地成本估计约为 total `0.44x`（selection `0.38x` + deployment `0.06x`），仍在当前优先覆盖的 `<0.5x` 区域内，但对应了新的结构槽位，能回答“固定预处理是否值得其额外 encoder 成本”。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"whitened_topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"遵守单变量原则，基于 `reference_round=1` 仅修改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不再停留在 `0.31x` 同槽位，而是有意识地补一个新的 `<0.5x` 结构点；若 `whitened_topk` 仍无明显增益，说明当前 target 上简单单库 family 的低成本主线已接近摸清，下一步应更积极转向其他结构族或准备轻量 expert 子库方向。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"whitened_topk"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`whitened_topk` 直接兼容 LUTurbo：最终形式仍是 `Σ α_i b_i`，差异只在选择前的确定性预处理路径。","本地成本估计：`whitened_topk@K=64,EF=1` 约为 total `0.44x`，可作为 `<0.5x` 区域内新的结构槽位 probe。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `whitened_topk@64` 明显优于 `topk@64`，下一轮可在该 family 内做 `K` 邻域验证是否存在更优 Pareto 点。","如果 `whitened_topk@64` 仍无显著增益，下一轮应优先转向新的兼容结构家族或高优先级未验证方向，而不是继续在单库 top-k 变体上局部打磨。"],"reference_round":1}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0053.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":51,"family_name":"two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"prototype","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_stage_residual_expert"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(r_1)}(r_1)} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 r_1 = x - Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i，e(r_1) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。第一段在静态 coarse library B={b_i} 上做有限加权和，第二段对残差在静态 expert 子库 C_e={c_{e,j}} 上做局部 sparse 修正，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：r51 已证明 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 的真 MoE-like 子库扩容有效，而 r52 说明继续增大同 family 的 K 不能稳定改善；相对 r51 仅切到 `two_stage_residual_expert`，保留 `NUM_EXPERTS=16`，可以测试“coarse global library + routed expert residual”是否能在约 0.69x total_cost 的中低成本带显著优于纯 `expert_topk` 的 FVU=0.1273，并形成新的结构性 Pareto 段。","summary":"停止继续细扫 `expert_topk` 的 K 轴，转向当前更高信息增量的结构问题。相对 r51 只改 `ARCHITECTURE=two_stage_residual_expert`，继承 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 的真 MoE-like 容量设置，直接回答 staged residual 是否比纯 routed sublibrary 更值得在 0.5x-0.8x 带继续推进；按当前 cost proxy 估算，该点约为 encoder 0.50x、deployment 0.19x、total 0.69x，仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r51 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这不是回到 plain selector 的重复扫点，而是基于已验证的 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 设置，对高优先级未充分验证方向 `two-stage residual expert` 做更公平的新一轮结构验证。相比把同样的 true sparse-capacity expansion 加到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上，这一候选的总成本更接近当前优先的 0.3x-0.8x 带，因而信息密度更高。主要风险是两段式结构默认 `STAGE1_RATIO` 可能不理想；但在尚未拿到 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 条件下的 clean family 结果前，不应先调该预算旋钮。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`two_stage_residual_expert` 在继承 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 后，第二阶段从 legacy fixed-split expert residual 变成 true sparse-capacity routed residual，更符合当前优先验证的 MoE-like 方向。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，`two_stage_residual_expert K=192 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=16` 的成本约为 selection 0.50x、deployment 0.19x、total 0.69x，预算比率约 0.46x，处于允许保留结构性质量锚点的中成本带。","如果该点仍明显弱于 r51 `expert_topk`，则说明仅加 coarse stage 还不足以补齐当前 target 的低成本质量缺口，后续更应转向带 trunk 的 `lowrank + expert` 或 `lowrank + expert + residual`。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果该结构在约 0.69x 成本下明显优于 r51 `expert_topk`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，测试 coarse library 与 expert residual 的预算分配是否是主控制旋钮。","如果该结构改善有限，则下一轮优先切到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 true sparse-capacity 版本，回答是否必须用 trunk 才能继续压低 FVU。","如果运行结果与预估配置不符，应先核对 round config 与 checkpoint config 中 `num_experts=16` 是否被正确继承，再决定是否接受该轮结论。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0009.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"切到直接兼容 family `group_topk`，最终重构公式仍为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_group(x)} α_i(x) b_i`。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时，`{b_i}` 仍是单个静态向量库；组内竞争只改变支持集形成方式，不改变后续“选择 + 系数计算 + 查表 `W b_i` + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”的部署链路。本轮相对 r8 仅修改 `ARCHITECTURE`，在保持 `K=64, EXPANSION_FACTOR=1, OPTIMIZER=adam, LR=8e-4` 不变的同成本槽位下，测试局部分组竞争能否比 plain top-k 降低 FVU。","summary":"兼容性判断：`group_topk` 为直接兼容。当前 `<0.5x` 区域已由 `topk` 建立 `K=32/48/64` 的 cost anchor，最新最佳点是 `r8 topk@K=64,EF=1,adam`，total_cost 约 `0.31x`。本地成本估计显示 `group_topk@K=64,EF=1` 的 selection 仍约 `0.25x`、deployment 约 `0.06x`、combined 约 `0.31x`，与 r8 同槽位且尚未在当前 target 验证；因此最干净的下一问是在不改变成本带的前提下，检查分组竞争是否带来更好的低成本 Pareto 点。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"group_topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"遵守单变量原则，基于 `reference_round=8` 仅修改 `ARCHITECTURE`。我刻意不同时改 `GROUP_TOPK_SIZE`，避免把“架构切换”和“组大小调参”混在一轮里；也不选 `routed/gated`，因为它们在 `K=64,EF=1` 下 encoder 成本约翻倍到 `0.50x`，会改变当前主线的低成本槽位归因。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"group_topk"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`group_topk` 直接兼容 LUTurbo：最终形式仍是单静态向量库上的有限加权和 `Σ α_i b_i`，仅支持选择机制从全局竞争改为组内竞争。","在当前 target 上，`group_topk@K=64,EF=1` 的估计总成本与 `r8 topk@K=64,EF=1` 同为约 `0.31x`，适合做 matched architecture probe。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `group_topk@K=64,EF=1` 优于 `topk@K=64,EF=1`，下一轮再在该 family 内单独探索 `GROUP_TOPK_SIZE` 或 `K`。","如果 `group_topk` 仍无增益，则低成本单库直接兼容 family 的新增信息将趋于饱和，下一轮应优先转向新的结构槽位或高优先级未充分验证方向。"],"reference_round":8}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0084.json:7:  "expected_win": "explore_unknown",
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0061.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Local gated sweeps have restored the stable baseline but are not closing the quality gap, and the most concrete unresolved blocker is still that `residual_topk` cannot be selected by the execution layer. The least-bad informative move is a narrow code round that registers and wires `residual_topk` into `SparseCoderConfig` validation and SAE class dispatch so the intended K=128 proxy prototype can finally produce a real quality signal.","summary":"Add `residual_topk` support under `sparsify/` and rerun the same K=128 proxy prototype under the existing signum regime.","change_type":"edit_sae_code","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"residual_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This follows the operator guidance to fix architecture-specific blockers before drawing quality conclusions, and it keeps the round focused on a single variable: making the blocked family runnable. The main risk is that registration is not the only incompatibility, but even that outcome is more informative than spending another round on incremental gated tuning.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"residual_topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.01"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["The runtime policy still says quality is the primary objective, but recent gated param-only rounds are now yielding only marginal frontier movement rather than a step-change toward the aggressive FVU target.","`residual_topk` remains untested on quality because its recent failures were architecture-registration crashes in `sparsify/`, which should be treated as implementation blockers rather than evidence against the family.","This round should change only the SAE code needed to make `residual_topk` selectable and runnable by the existing launcher, keeping the prototype hyperparameters otherwise fixed."],"next_hypotheses":["If `residual_topk` runs and shows competitive proxy FVU, keep the family alive and stabilize its internal budget split next.","If `residual_topk` runs cleanly but is clearly worse than gated and not better than prior incubating families, archive it quickly and resume broader architecture exploration.","If `residual_topk` still fails after registration and dispatch are fixed, treat the remaining issue as a deeper implementation incompatibility and move to a different new family rather than continue local gated sweeps."],"primary_variable":"code_fix"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0040.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":27,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_stage_residual_expert"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(r_1)}(r_1)} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 r_1 = x - Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i。第一段在静态 coarse library B={b_i} 上做有限加权和，第二段对剩余残差用轻量 router 选择一个静态 expert 子库 C_e={c_{e,j}} 并做局部 sparse 修正，因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：相比已经很强但偏高成本的 `lowrank_expert_residual`，去掉 dense trunk，改为 `coarse sparse + expert residual` 两段式后，能在更低 total_cost 带形成新的结构性 Pareto 段，并直接回答 `two-stage residual expert` 是否值得继续。","summary":"不继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 上做第三轮局部调参，而是切到当前高优先级未充分验证方向 `two-stage residual expert`。以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，先验证“coarse sparse + expert residual”这个新结构槽位本身是否成立。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：运行配置相对 r27 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。当前已在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 上连续两轮未形成新前沿，更合理的下一步是扩大结构信息增量，而不是继续细扫其邻域。选择 `two_stage_residual_expert` 而不是再回到 plain selector，是因为它直接对应当前优先级列表中的未验证方向，同时比带 trunk 的三段式更有希望落入低到中成本带。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `two_stage_residual_expert` 首轮稳定且明显优于 `expert_topk K=192`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，验证 coarse 段与 expert residual 段的预算分配是否是主控制旋钮。","如果该 family 有信号但成本仍偏高，下一轮优先只改 `K` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO`，把它压向 0.3x-0.6x 带。","如果该原型仍不具竞争力，则说明当前 target 更可能需要 dense trunk；后续再回到 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的低成本化路线。"],"notes_to_memory":["`two_stage_residual_expert` 的导出形式是第一段静态 coarse library 加第二段单 expert 静态子库残差修正上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。","本轮优先回答新的结构问题，而不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 `TRUNK_RANK/STAGE1_RATIO` 上做局部扫点。","实现时应优先复用现有 `two_stage_residual` 与 `expert_topk` 组件，并复用已有 `STAGE1_RATIO` 语义，避免新增 tunable 名称。","若该新 family 需要后续调 `STAGE1_RATIO`，应在新增 family 时同步补齐 override registry 的允许键，避免后续 param_only 回合静默拒绝 override。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0109.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":108,"family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","expected_win":"lower_cost","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"96"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 B^sh 是始终激活的静态 shared 子库，E(x) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 routed experts，所有原子都来自静态向量库，因此在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。明确排除不兼容 family：`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled 结构不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r107 与 r108 已证明 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 在 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 下形成了真实的低成本结构段，并且 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 已把 total_cost 左移到约 0.38x；下一步最有信息量的问题不再是继续压每-expert 宽度，而是这条新结构线在更低部署查表预算下是否仍能保住明显优于旧 `<0.5x` anchor 的质量。相对 r108 仅把 `K` 从 128 降到 96，在保持 `NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320`、`EF=1` 与其余训练配方不变时，按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，总成本将约从 0.38x 降到 0.34x，仍远低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束；如果 FVU 仍显著优于当前同为低成本带的 `expert_topk K=128` 与 `lowrank_expert_topk K=96`，则 shared+routed 将把新的结构性 Pareto 段继续向更低部署预算推进。","summary":"Round 109 不回到旧主线做 K/TRUNK_RANK 邻域微调，而是沿已形成新前沿的 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做一次 deployment-cost 压缩。以 r108 为 reference，只把 `K` 从 128 降到 96，直接测试 shared+routed 线能否在约 0.34x 成本下继续保住对当前 `<0.5x` anchor 的明显质量优势。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r108 只改 `K`。这不是 old-family 的重复 K 轴打磨，而是对当前已经形成新非支配点的 shared+routed 结构线做第一次 deployment-side left-shift probe，信息密度高于继续沿 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 连续左移。选择改 `K` 而不是把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 回退到 1，是因为 r106-r108 已经表明 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 是这条线当前最强的已验证组合；本轮应优先保留这一结构收益，只压查表成本。主要风险是 `K=96` 会让 routed 子库的有效局部查表预算不足，导致 FVU 回退明显；但这同样是高价值结论，因为它会直接界定 shared+routed 在低部署预算下的可行边界。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r107 与 r108 已形成 shared+routed 的两段低成本兼容前沿：`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=384, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 在约 0.42x 下达成 val_fvu=0.1010，`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 在约 0.38x 下达成 val_fvu=0.1072。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，`shared_routed_expert_topk K=96 NUM_EXPERTS=64 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 的 selection≈0.25x、deployment≈0.09x、total≈0.34x，明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算。","当前 `<0.5x` 最有希望的新结构线已从旧 `lowrank_expert_topk` 转向 `shared_routed_expert_topk`；本轮应优先回答这条新线在更低 deploy budget 下是否仍成立。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=96` 在约 0.34x 下仍把 FVU 控制在 0.12 左右或更低，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=80` 或 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=288`，继续细化 shared+routed 的低成本前沿。","如果 `K=96` 明显退化但仍优于 `expert_topk` / `lowrank_expert_topk` 的低成本 anchor，则可回到 `K=112`，把 shared+routed 前沿在 0.34x-0.38x 带内做更细 knee 定位。","如果 `K=96` 明显劣于当前 shared+routed 点，则可初步判断这条结构线在当前 target 上更缺局部 lookup budget 而非 encoder 宽度，后续应保持 `K=128`，再评估 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=288/352` 或切到 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 对照。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0094.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":60,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"48"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。在线导出仍是 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单个静态 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容；`expert_topk` 属于直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 属于不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：r60 已证明 `TRUNK_RANK=64` 的 shared trunk 能把 `lowrank + expert` 压到当前最强的 <0.5x 低成本锚点之一，而 r70 又表明 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 已明显过薄；在 r86/r93 继续否定 multi-expert active path 后，当前更高信息量的问题不再是继续拉长 active path，而是 shared trunk 的 Pareto knee 是否位于 32 与 64 之间。相对 r60 仅将 `TRUNK_RANK: 64 -> 48`，若当前 64 维 trunk 存在冗余，则 FVU 应保持接近 r60 的 0.1123，同时把 total_cost 从约 0.48x 左移到约 0.45x（selection≈0.28x，deployment≈0.17x），从而在 0.4x-0.5x 带补出新的结构性 anchor。","summary":"r93 已把 routed-only `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 明确打成负信号，`factorized_expert_topk` 也连续多轮稳定偏弱，因此本轮不再继续 MoE active-path 扩展，也不回到旧 family 的 K 轴。以 r60 为 reference，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=48`，直接回答当前更关键的结构问题：`lowrank + expert` 这条兼容低成本主线的 shared trunk 宽度是否存在比 64 更经济、但明显优于 32 的中间 Pareto knee。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r60 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。这不是 plain selector 的重复扫点，也不是继续沿已给出负信号的 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` / `factorized_expert_topk` 方向消耗预算，而是在当前仍有真实 frontier 价值的 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上做一次高信息量结构压缩 probe。主要风险是 48 维 trunk 仍可能明显弱于 64，导致结果只重复 r70 的退化趋势；但即便如此，也能把这条 family 的 trunk-width knee 明确收敛到更窄区间，避免后续继续在无效 active-path 轴上试错。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r93 (`expert_topk ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`) 从 r74 的 0.1243 退化到 0.2040，说明当前 target 上 routed-only multi-expert active path 不是值得继续主推的低成本方向。","`factorized_expert_topk` 在 r90-r92 上稳定停在约 0.2158，shared-basis expert routing 这条实现线当前优先级应继续下调。","`lowrank_expert_topk` 仍是当前最有希望补 <0.5x 前沿的扩展兼容 family 之一：r60 (`TRUNK_RANK=64`) 给出 0.1123，而 r70 (`TRUNK_RANK=32`) 退化到 0.1340；`TRUNK_RANK=48` 是尚未验证的中间膝点。","按当前 fresh cost 估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=128 NUM_EXPERTS=32 TRUNK_RANK=48 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 的 total_cost 约 0.45x，仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算，也处于本轮最需要补强的低到中成本带。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `TRUNK_RANK=48` 基本保住 r60 的 FVU，同时把成本左移到约 0.45x，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=40`，继续精化这条 shared-trunk Pareto knee。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=48` 明显劣于 r60 且接近 r70，则可初步判定这条 `lowrank + expert` 低成本线的最小可用 trunk 更接近 64；后续不再细扫该轴，而转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert`。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=48` 结果介于 r60 与 r70 之间但未形成非支配点，则说明当前 family 对 trunk width 的收益已较饱和，后续应减少对 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的局部压缩预算。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0019.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_topk"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i。`factorized_topk` 只把在线选择链路改成 h(x)=ReLU(W1x), scores=W2h(x) 后再做 top-k，decoder 仍是单个静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性=直接兼容。主假设：在当前 target 上，低秩 factorized scorer 可能在 K=160、EF=1 的 <0.5x 成本带内，比同成本附近的 topk 给出更低 FVU，从而补出新的低开销 Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `factorized_topk` 在 K=160 上拿到正信号，再以该 family 自己的 reference_round 单独调 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，确认低秩 scorer 的最佳成本槽位。","如果该 probe 明显不如 topk，则回到更干净的 matched-cost 对照（如 K=128 的 arch-only probe），或把下一轮预算转向真正轻量的 MoE-like 新 family 实现。"],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：`factorized_topk` 为直接兼容；最终导出形式不变，仍是单库稀疏加权和。","reference_round 选 r13，因为它是当前 target 上有效的 `topk K=160 EF=1` 低成本锚点；本轮只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，满足单变量规则。","按当前实现的 auto `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，K=160/EF=1 时 hidden_dim=640，预估 selection≈0.31x、deployment≈0.16x、total≈0.47x，仍位于本轮优先探索的 <0.5x 区域。","这轮先做 arch-only probe，不同时引入 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，避免把 family 切换与结构宽度耦合。"],"reference_round":13,"self_review":"这不是更低成本点，而是一个低开销新 family 探针；auto hidden=640 让 encoder 成本高于同 K topk，所以只有当 FVU 改善足够明显时才可能进入 frontier。单变量约束下先做 architecture probe 是更可归因的顺序。","summary":"相对 r13 的完整配置（`topk`, `K=160`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`, `OPTIMIZER=adam`, `LR=8e-4`），本轮只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 改为 `factorized_topk`。其最终重构仍为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i`，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路。目标是在估计 total_cost≈0.47x 的低开销区，验证 factorized scorer 是否能把 FVU 压到优于当前 topk 低成本前沿。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0054.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":53,"family_name":"two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"prototype","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"STAGE1_RATIO","value":"0.25"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(r_1)}(r_1)} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 r_1 = x - Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i，e(r_1) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。第一段仍是在静态 coarse library B={b_i} 上做有限加权和，第二段仍是在静态 expert 子库 C_e={c_{e,j}} 上做局部 sparse residual 修正，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：r53 已证明 `two_stage_residual_expert + NUM_EXPERTS=16` 比纯 `expert_topk` 更有前景，接下来真正需要回答的是两段预算分配是否是主控制旋钮；相对 r53 仅设置 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`，把更多 K 留给 expert residual 段，应能在总成本基本不变的情况下把 FVU 从 0.1134 继续压低。","summary":"当前不再继续扫 `expert_topk` 的 K，也不急着切去另一条 family。相对 r53 只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`，是对 `two_stage_residual_expert` 最关键结构旋钮的首次干净验证：保持 `K=192`、`NUM_EXPERTS=16` 和总成本近似不变，只测试“少量 coarse + 更强 expert residual”是否能把这条新前沿继续向下推进。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r53 只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`。这不是 old-family 的重复局部打磨，而是对一个刚形成新 Pareto 段的结构做首个高信息量归因实验。选择 `0.25` 而不是继续调 K，是因为当前成本代理下 `STAGE1_RATIO` 基本不改变 selection/deployment 总量，却能直接回答 staged residual 的有效容量应更多放在 coarse 还是 expert residual。主要风险是 coarse 段若压得过低，可能导致第一阶段欠拟合并拖累整体重构；但这正是本轮要验证的结构问题。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`two_stage_residual_expert` 在 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 下已给出 0.50x / FVU 0.1134 的新结构性前沿点，说明 staged residual 比纯 `expert_topk` 更值得继续。","在当前实现里，`STAGE1_RATIO` 主要改变 K 在 coarse 段与 expert residual 段之间的分配，而不显著改变总 selection/deployment 成本，因此适合作为同成本归因实验。","若 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 明显优于默认分配，则可初步判断当前 target 更需要把有限激活预算投向 routed expert residual，而不是更大的 coarse global pass。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 在约 0.50x 成本下继续明显降低 FVU，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.125` 或 `0.33`，进一步定位最佳 coarse/residual 分工区间。","如果 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 退化明显，则下一轮优先尝试 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.75`，验证该 family 是否其实更依赖强 coarse stage 而非更强 expert residual。","如果该 family 在 `STAGE1_RATIO` 调整后仍只能小幅优于 `expert_topk`，则后续应把预算转向带 trunk 的 `lowrank + expert` 或 `lowrank + expert + residual`，回答是否必须引入低秩主干才能继续显著下压 FVU。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0023.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 prototype 先固定 |E(x)|=1：router 先从若干静态 expert 子库中选 1 个子库，再只在该子库内做局部 top-k。在线导出时，LUTurbo/Lottable 只需执行“轻量 router 选 expert 子库 + 在该静态子库内查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”，仍然是一个或多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此兼容性判断为扩展兼容。主假设：相比继续在已验证 family 上局部打磨，一个固定 4-expert、单激活路径的 `expert_topk` 原型有机会把全字典选择改成局部子库选择，在 K=64 的低成本区显著压低 selection cost，并为 <0.28x 区域提供新的有效信号。","summary":"新增一个轻量 MoE-like family `expert_topk`，不引入新 tunable 参数，先用固定原型：4 个静态 expert 子库、每个 token 仅激活 1 个 expert、在被选 expert 内执行 top-k。相对 r10 的 K=64/EF=1/adam 配方，只通过 `ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk` 启动该新 family，并在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` 中完成最小实现与成本估计接入。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这是一次有意偏向高优先级未充分验证方向的结构探索，而不是继续挤压 factorized_topk 的局部参数。主要风险有两个：一是 prototype 若训练时用全 expert 计算、部署时只按单激活路径计成本，必须显式覆盖 `selection_cost_estimate`，否则预算判断会失真；二是固定 4 expert/1 active 可能过于僵硬，但先用无新参数原型能把接线与归因范围控制在 `sparsify/` 内。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"expert_topk"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：新 family `expert_topk` 为扩展兼容；最终形式是若干静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和，不依赖样本级动态生成字典。","本轮优先响应高优先级未充分验证方向：轻量 expert 子库 / MoE-like 路由；已实现 family 目前在 <0.5x 区域仍未给出满意 FVU。","为遵守最小修改范围，本轮不新增 tunable 参数，prototype 先固定 `NUM_EXPERTS=4`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，仅修改 `sparsify/`。","必须在实现中单独处理部署成本估计，确保 `selection_cost_estimate` 反映 router + 单 expert 局部 scorer 的激活路径，而不是训练期可能使用的全 expert 计算图。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `expert_topk` prototype 能稳定训练且在超低成本区给出有效信号，下一轮再决定是否把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 或 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 作为新 tunable 参数正式接线。","如果 sanity 或首轮训练暴露实现/成本估计问题，下一轮优先修复该 family 本身，不要立即回退到共享 trainer 路径或重新转向旧 family 微调。"],"reference_round":10}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0078.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_e Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 e(x) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“router 选单个静态子库 + 子库内 local top-k + 查表加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `expert_topk` 属于直接兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`factorized_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。r77 已经给出清晰负信号：`factorized_expert_topk` 在与 r74 近同成本的 matched probe 下 FVU=0.2482，说明当前 `expert-internal low-rank / shared-basis` 原型不值得继续作为低成本主线。相对 r74 仅把 `K` 从 160 提到 192，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk`、`NUM_EXPERTS=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，直接回答 routed-only MoE-like 低成本前沿的下一关键问题：如果 r73→r74 的连续改善说明当前低成本带的主瓶颈仍有一部分来自每 token 的局部 lookup budget 不足，而不只是总容量，那么在保持同一容量与短 active path 的前提下，适度增加 `K` 应能在仍低于 0.5x total_cost 的范围内继续压低 FVU，并判断 routed-only 低成本线此刻更缺容量还是更缺 lookup budget。","summary":"Round 78 不继续追 r77 已明显失效的 `factorized_expert_topk`，也不回到旧 family 的局部微调；而是在当前最干净、已验证有效的直接兼容 MoE-like 线上做一次高信息量 matched probe。以 r74 为 reference，只把 `K` 从 160 提到 192，直接区分当前 routed-only `expert_topk` 低成本前沿的主要瓶颈究竟还是总容量，还是已经转到单 token 的 lookup budget。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r74 只改 `K`。这不是 plain selector 的旧式 K 轴细扫，因为参考点本身是高优先级 MoE-like sparse-capacity recipe `NUM_EXPERTS=128`，而本轮是在 r77 已明确否定 shared-basis 原型后，对 routed-only 前沿做的瓶颈分解 probe。主要风险是改善可能很小；但即便如此也有高信息量，因为若 `K=192` 在该 recipe 下仍无明显收益，就可更清晰判定当前 `expert_topk` 的低成本瓶颈已不主要在 lookup budget，后续应把结构预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 trunk/stage 轴或其他兼容 family。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"192"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式保持为静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和，兼容性仍为直接兼容。","r77 的 matched `factorized_expert_topk` 探针在近同成本下明显弱于 r74，说明当前 `expert-internal low-rank / shared-basis` 原型不值得继续主线推进。","本轮相对 r74 只改 `K=192`，是在 `NUM_EXPERTS=128` sparse-capacity recipe 上做 lookup-budget probe，而不是重复旧的 plain-selector K 轴。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 代码路径估算，`expert_topk K=192 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=128` 的成本约为 selection 0.28x、deployment 0.19x、total 0.47x，仍处于当前重点补点的 <0.5x 低成本带内，并显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=192` 在仍约 0.47x 成本下明显优于 r74，则下一轮可保持 `expert_topk` 不变，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS` 或继续小幅改 `K`，寻找 routed-only 前沿的最佳低成本拐点。","如果 `K=192` 改善很弱，则可较清晰判定当前 `expert_topk` 的低成本瓶颈已不主要在 lookup budget，后续应把结构预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 `TRUNK_RANK` / `STAGE1_RATIO` 轴，或重开其他兼容 family。","如果结果异常，先核对 `round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `k=192` 已真实生效，再决定是否把该轮当作结构证据。"],"reference_round":74}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0058.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`residual_topk` did not fail on quality or runtime grounds; it failed because the execution layer still does not recognize the architecture name. The smallest informative next move is a narrow code-fix round that registers and wires `residual_topk` into the existing config/class dispatch and forward path so the prototype can finally receive one real K=128 proxy measurement under the current strongest regime.","summary":"Register and implement the `residual_topk` architecture in `sparsify/`, then rerun the same K=128 proxy prototype under the current best signum settings.","change_type":"edit_sae_code","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"residual_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This is the minimal blocker-removal step after a concrete architecture-registration crash, and it keeps the round focused on making the intended new family runnable rather than changing the experimental target. The main risk is that a second incompatibility appears after registration, but that is still better handled as a code-fix path than by abandoning the family without a valid signal.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"residual_topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.01"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 57 produced a concrete execution-layer blocker for `residual_topk`: the architecture name is still missing from `SparseCoderConfig` validation and/or SAE class dispatch, so the family has no usable quality signal yet.","This is stronger evidence of incomplete code integration than of a bad architecture, so `residual_topk` should not be judged on quality yet.","The next round keeps the original `residual_topk` K=128 proxy target fixed and changes only the code needed to make the family selectable and runnable by the existing launcher."],"next_hypotheses":["If `residual_topk` runs and shows promising proxy FVU, keep the family alive and stabilize its internal K split next.","If it runs cleanly but is clearly worse than gated and not better than factorized-topk, archive it quickly and move to another architecture family.","If `residual_topk` still fails after registration is fixed, treat the remaining issue as a deeper implementation incompatibility and shift effort elsewhere."],"primary_variable":"code_fix"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0041.json:6:  "expected_win": "explore_unknown",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0052.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":51,"family_name":"expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"224"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 e(x) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，B_e={b_{e,i}} 是静态 expert 子库。在线导出仍是“router 选静态子库 + 子库内查表 + 有限加权和”的 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判定为直接兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：r51 已证明 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 的真 MoE-like 扩容有效后，当前误差瓶颈更可能来自单 expert 内的激活预算不足而不是总容量不足；相对 r51 仅把 `K: 192 -> 224`，应能在保持短 active path 与低总成本的同时进一步降低 FVU，并把这条 routed-expert 前沿推进到约 0.47x total_cost。","summary":"继续追 MoE-like 这条已出现明确信号的新结构线，而不是回到 plain selector 邻域。相对 r51 只改 `K=224`，是在已验证 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 生效的前提下，测试 routed sublibrary 的低成本 Pareto 能否继续向下推进；按当前 cost proxy 估算，encoder 仍约 0.25x，deployment 约 0.22x，total 约 0.47x，仍留在当前重点关注的 <0.5x 带内。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r51 只改 `K`。这不是回到 old-family 的重复 K 轴扫描，而是在当前最有信息增量的新 MoE-like family 上补第二个结构性前沿点。该 family 属于直接兼容，且本轮不引入新 tunable、不需要改代码或接线。主要风险是 r51 的大幅改善已经主要来自总容量扩张，继续增大 K 可能只带来有限收益；如果这轮改善很弱，就应减少对纯 `expert_topk` 的后续 K 扫点，把预算转向 `lowrank + expert` 或 `two-stage residual expert`。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`expert_topk` 在 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 下已经从 legacy fixed-split 布局切到 true sparse-capacity mode；r51 的 FVU=0.1273 说明 MoE-like 子库扩容在当前 target 上不是伪信号。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，`expert_topk NUM_EXPERTS=16 K=224 EF=1` 的成本约为 encoder 0.25x、deployment 0.22x、total 0.47x，预算比率约 0.31x，仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","如果这轮仍显著改善，则说明当前低成本区不仅受总容量限制，也受单 expert 内激活预算限制；若改善很弱，则更可能需要引入 trunk 或 residual 结构，而不是继续单纯增大 routed expert 的 K。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=224` 在约 0.47x 成本下继续明显降低 FVU，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=256`，测试这条 MoE-like 前沿能否贴近 0.5x 左右的质量拐点。","如果 `K=224` 改善有限，则下一轮不再继续细扫 `expert_topk` 的 K 轴，而是切到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert`，回答是否需要 trunk / staged residual 才能继续下压 FVU。","如果运行结果与预估成本明显不符，应优先复核 round config 与 cost entry 是否正确继承了 `NUM_EXPERTS=16`，避免把配置漂移误判成结构结论。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0029.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式取 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i。对 `jumprelu` 而言，JumpReLU threshold 只改变支持集 S(x) 的形成方式，decoder 仍是同一个静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的查表 + 加权求和链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 r10 仅把 K 从 64 提到 192，可把该 family 放到与当前 <0.5x 主竞争带相同的约 0.44x total_cost（encoder 0.25x + deploy 0.19x）上，回答它在当前 target 上是否能比 topk K=192 的 FVU=0.1577 更好。","summary":"基于 r10 的 jumprelu 配方做一次单变量低开销 probe：只把 K 提到 192，保持 EF=1、adam、8e-4 不变，把 jumprelu 放到 0.44x 成本带，与当前最佳 <0.5x 点做正面对照。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"主要风险是 JumpReLU 在默认 threshold/bandwidth 下只会削弱有效容量，导致在相同 K 成本带落后于 plain topk；如果这轮仍明显输给 topk K=192，就应把 jumprelu 视为当前 target 上的低优先级 family，而不是继续围绕默认门限做局部微调。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"192"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["jumprelu 属于直接兼容 family，导出形式仍为单静态库有限加权和 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i。","在当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，jumprelu K=192 EF=1 的预估成本为 sel=1048576 (0.25x), deploy=786432 (0.19x), total=1835008 (0.44x)。","group_topk 已在相同 0.44x 成本带给出 0.1708 FVU 但未超过 topk K=192，本轮改测另一类支持形成机制而不是继续打磨同一家族。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 jumprelu 在 0.44x 下优于 topk K=192，则下一轮优先固定 family 不变，只改一个 JumpReLU 动态参数验证门限是否还能继续改善。","如果 jumprelu 不优于 topk K=192，则下一轮转向另一个低成本未充分验证方向，而不是继续在 support-shaping 单库 family 上做局部微调。"],"reference_round":10}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0091.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{e∈E(z(x))} Σ_{i∈S_e(z(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 z(x)=Bx 是共享低维投影，E(z) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 active experts，expert 内用小型 low-rank head A_e z 做 local scoring/top-k，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + 少量静态 expert 子库选择 + 子库内查表 + 有限加权求和”的 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `factorized_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容；`expert_topk` 属直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r86 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_topk` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，在保持 `K=128`、`NUM_EXPERTS=16`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，如果 r86 的失败主要来自 full-dim routed scorer 太重而不是 multi-expert MoE-like 本身，那么 shared-basis expert routing 应能在更低 total_cost 下显著改善 FVU，并在约 0.3x 成本带形成新的结构性 anchor。按当前成本模型粗估，selection≈0.19x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.31x，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","summary":"Round 91 继续定向补低成本前沿，但不回到旧 family 的 K 轴微调。以 r86 为 reference，只切换到 `factorized_expert_topk`，直接回答“multi-expert active path 的问题是在 MoE 结构本身，还是在 full-dim scorer 太重”这个当前最关键的低成本结构问题。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r86 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这一步比继续调 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 或 `NUM_EXPERTS` 更有信息量，因为它保留同一 multi-expert MoE-like 语义，只替换 scorer 结构，从而更干净地区分瓶颈来源。主要风险是该 family 在当前 target 上可能仍有训练稳定性问题；若结果异常，应先归因为实现或优化稳定性，而不是直接否定 shared-basis expert routing。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["这轮是对 r86 负结果的结构归因实验：保持 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 与 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 不变，只把 routed scorer 换成 shared-basis low-rank head。","`factorized_expert_topk` 的最终形式仍是静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和；共享投影只改变在线选择链路，不引入动态字典，因此兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 粗估，`factorized_expert_topk K=128 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=16 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 的 total_cost 约 0.31x，明显低于 r86 所在成本带，也落在当前最需要补强的低成本区间。","如果该 family 在近 0.31x 成本下仍明显不优于当前 low-cost anchors，则 shared-basis expert routing 这条线在当前 target 上应降低优先级。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 在约 0.31x total_cost 下显著优于 r86 并接近当前 <0.5x 前沿，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=32`，验证 shared-basis MoE-like 的容量扩张是否继续成立。","如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 有正信号但仍弱于预期，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，区分瓶颈是在 shared basis 宽度还是在 routed capacity。","如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 仍然表现很差，则说明当前 target 上 multi-expert routed-only 路线整体不值得继续，后续应把低成本结构预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert`。"],"reference_round":86}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0063.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Crash recovery mode requires returning to the strongest working gated path and making only a minor parameter adjustment. The least-risk informative move is to keep the K=128 gated signum anchor fixed and restore a small auxiliary loss with `AUXK_ALPHA=0.01` to check whether the canonical regularized regime improves training stability or quality without reopening architecture risk.","summary":"Run a gated proxy recovery pass at `K=128` with the current best signum setup and `AUXK_ALPHA=0.01` to recheck stability on the strongest working family.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This follows crash recovery constraints by avoiding code edits and staying on the best validated family with one small parameter change. The main risk is low novelty, but restoring clean signal on a stable configuration is more important than broader exploration after consecutive crashes.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.01"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Crash recovery mode overrides architecture exploration for this round and requires a param-only run on the strongest known working configuration.","The best validated anchor remains gated EF=16, K=128, signum, LR=1.6e-3; this round changes only AUXK_ALPHA to probe a conservative recovery variant.","Recent residual-topk crashes should continue to be treated as unresolved implementation-path failures rather than evidence against the stable gated baseline."],"next_hypotheses":["If the gated recovery run is healthy and competitive, resume frontier work from the stable gated family before attempting new architecture exploration again.","If `AUXK_ALPHA=0.01` regresses versus the aux-free anchor, keep `AUXK_ALPHA=0` as the main K=128 recovery baseline.","If stability is restored cleanly, the next move can revisit adjacent low-risk gated comparisons before reopening blocked architecture paths."],"primary_variable":"other_param"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0032.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i。对 `jumprelu` 而言，threshold 与 bandwidth 只改变支持集 S(x) 的形成方式，decoder 仍是同一个静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的查表 + 加权求和链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。r29-r31 已表明 `jumprelu` 在 0.44x 成本带能与当前 best <0.5x 点基本持平并略优，因此下一步最有信息量的动作不是继续改门控细节，而是在保持同 family 与同配方的前提下只增大 K 到 224，把总成本推到约 0.47x，测试它能否在仍低于 0.5x 的区域内给出更明确的 FVU 改善。","summary":"基于 r31 的 jumprelu 配方做一次低开销前沿扩展：仅把 K 从 192 提到 224，保持 ARCHITECTURE=jumprelu、EF=1、JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD=0.05、JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH=0.05、adam、8e-4 不变，验证该 family 能否在约 0.47x total_cost 下补出优于当前 <0.5x 最佳点的新 Pareto 点。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"主要风险是 K=224 只带来很小的 FVU 改善，不足以抵消部署成本上升，从而形成一个被现有 0.44x 点近似支配的弱点；但在 jumprelu 已经出现 matched-cost 正信号的前提下，这一步能直接回答该 family 是否值得占据 <0.5x 主线。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"224"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["jumprelu 当前是唯一在 0.44x 成本带对 topk K=192 给出微弱正信号的已测兼容 family。","在当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，jumprelu K=224 EF=1 的预估成本约为 encoder 0.25x + deploy 0.22x = total 0.47x，仍处于本阶段重点的 <0.5x 区域。","本轮改 K 而不改门控参数，用于判断 jumprelu 的收益是否能沿低成本 Pareto 前沿继续放大。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 jumprelu K=224 明显优于当前 best <0.5x 点，则下一轮优先在该 family 内继续做少量 K 邻域刻画，确认低成本前沿形状。","如果 K=224 仍只给出边际改善或无改善，则停止继续打磨 jumprelu，转向新的兼容 family 或新的结构槽位。"],"reference_round":31}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0076.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","reference_round":65,"env_overrides":[{"key":"NUM_EXPERTS","value":"64"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“trunk 查表 + 单 expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 属于扩展兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert`、`factorized_expert_topk` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。相对 r65 仅把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 32 提到 64，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`、`K=128`、`TRUNK_RANK=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，直接回答当前低成本三段式结构的核心未决问题：如果 r65 在约 0.49x 带的瓶颈仍有一部分来自 routed expert 子库总容量不足，而不只是 trunk 宽度或 residual cleanup 配比，那么扩大总静态 expert 容量、同时保持 active path 不变，应能在近同一 total_cost 下继续压低 FVU，并把 `lowrank + expert + residual` 这条兼容结构前沿进一步向下推进。","summary":"Round 76 不回到旧 family 的 K 轴，而是把低成本三段式主线做一次真正的 sparse-capacity probe。以 r65 为参考只把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 提到 64，直接判断当前 <0.5x 附近最有希望的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 低成本点，瓶颈究竟在 routed capacity 还是已经转到 trunk / residual 侧。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r65 只改 `NUM_EXPERTS`。这比继续沿 `expert_topk` 做第三次纯容量外推更有信息量，因为 `lowrank_expert_residual` 已是当前最强的兼容三段式 family，且 r64 已说明 trunk-free staged 结构明显偏弱；当前更值得回答的是，在保留 trunk 和 residual cleanup 的前提下，额外 routed capacity 是否还能在低成本带换到更低 FVU。主要风险是收益很小，但这同样是高价值结论，因为它会把后续低成本预算更明确地收敛到 `TRUNK_RANK` / `STAGE1_RATIO` 或其他结构方向。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 的 LUTurbo 形式保持为静态 trunk 库 + 静态 expert 子库 + 静态 residual 补偿库上的有限加权和，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","r65 已在 `K=128, TRUNK_RANK=32, NUM_EXPERTS=32, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 下给出约 0.49x 的低成本锚点；本轮只扩 routed capacity，不改 trunk、K 或 budget split。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 的代码路径估算，`lowrank_expert_residual K=128 TRUNK_RANK=32 NUM_EXPERTS=64 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 的总成本只会相对 r65 小幅上升，仍处于低到中成本带内，远低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","如果这一步继续改善，则说明三段式 family 在低成本带仍未吃满 expert capacity；如果不改善，则可更清晰地把后续重点转向 trunk 宽度、stage split 或新的 expert-internal low-rank 方向。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=64` 在近同成本下显著优于 r65，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=128`，确认三段式结构中的 routed capacity 收益何时饱和。","如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=64` 改善很弱，则可较清晰判定当前 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的低成本瓶颈已不主要在 expert 容量，后续应改做 `TRUNK_RANK`、`STAGE1_RATIO`，或回到 `factorized_expert_topk` 这类 shared-basis 方向。","如果结果异常，先核对 `round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `num_experts=64` 已真实生效，再决定是否把该轮当作结构证据。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0067.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。在线侧仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”流水线，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判断为扩展兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r60 仅把 NUM_EXPERTS 从 32 提到 64，在保持 ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk、K=128、TRUNK_RANK=64、EF=1、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1 不变时，如果当前 0.48x 左右低成本段的瓶颈仍有一部分来自 routed static capacity 不足，而不只是 shared trunk 太薄，那么更大的总 expert 子库容量应在几乎同一 total_cost 下继续压低 FVU，并回答 true sparse-capacity MoE-like 扩容在当前 target 上是否还能形成新的低成本 Pareto 段。","summary":"选择 lowrank_expert_topk 的 NUM_EXPERTS 单变量 probe，而不是继续扫 K 或回到 plain selector。原因是 r60 已证明 shared trunk 变宽有效，现在最有信息量的问题是：在保持 active path 很短且 total_cost 仍约 0.48x 的前提下，继续放大 routed capacity 是否还能带来可观收益。按当前成本估算，NUM_EXPERTS=64 约为 encoder 0.30x、deployment 0.19x、total 0.48x，仍处于本轮要求的低成本带。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r60 只改 NUM_EXPERTS。该 family 属于 LUTurbo 扩展兼容 family，且 NUM_EXPERTS 已在 sparsify/、override_registry、config_resolution、runner 与 scripts/autoresearch_test.sh 中接通，无需新增代码。选择这一步而不是继续压 TRUNK_RANK/K，是因为当前阶段更需要回答 true MoE-like sparse-capacity 扩容是否仍有增益；主要风险是 r57→r59 已显示纯容量扩张收益偏弱，因此本轮也可能证明该 family 的主要瓶颈已从容量转向 trunk/router 质量。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"NUM_EXPERTS","value":"64"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式保持为静态 trunk 库加单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=128 TRUNK_RANK=64 NUM_EXPERTS=64` 的成本约为 selection 0.30x、deployment 0.19x、total 0.48x。","本轮是对 r60 的 true sparse-capacity continuation：只增大总 expert 容量，不增加 active experts，也不改 K/TRUNK_RANK。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 NUM_EXPERTS=64 在近同成本下显著优于 r60，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 NUM_EXPERTS=128，确认低成本段的容量收益是否继续成立。","如果 NUM_EXPERTS=64 改善很弱，则可较清晰判定当前 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的低成本瓶颈已不主要在 routed capacity，后续应把预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或其他带 residual cleanup 的结构。","如果结果异常，先核对 round*.config.json 与 checkpoint config.json 中 `num_experts=64` 已真实生效，再决定是否把该轮当作结构证据。"],"reference_round":60}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0058.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":56,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"STAGE1_RATIO","value":"0.5"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库，e(x) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。在线侧仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判定为扩展兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：r57 说明 `lowrank + expert` 本体已经有明显价值，而 r56 说明在 `K=128` 下三段式结构仍优于去掉 residual 的 matched 对照；因此当前 0.46x 点的主要未决问题不再是“要不要 residual”，而是 expert 段与 residual 段的预算分配是否偏向 residual 过多。相对 r56 仅将 `STAGE1_RATIO: 0.25 -> 0.5`，在总成本基本不变的前提下给 routed expert 更多激活预算，若当前 target 更需要局部 expert 结构而非更重的全局 cleanup，则 FVU 应能从 0.1113 进一步下压。","summary":"当前不继续压 K，也不回到 plain selector。相对 r56 只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.5`，是在已验证有效的 `lowrank_expert_residual K=128 NUM_EXPERTS=16 TRUNK_RANK=16` 配方上做一次同成本高信息量归因实验：保持总成本近似不变，只测试 expert 段与 residual 段的预算重分配能否把这条 <0.5x 前沿继续往下推。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r56 只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`。这不是旧 family 的局部 K 轴打磨，而是围绕当前最强低成本结构点做一次明确的结构归因。选择 `0.5` 而不是更极端的 `0.125/0.75`，是因为 r57 已证明纯 `lowrank + expert` 虽弱于三段式，但并不无效；因此先把预算拉回更均衡的分配，更有机会在不牺牲 residual 修正的前提下提升质量。主要风险是 residual cleanup 其实正是当前 0.46x 点的核心收益来源，提升 stage1 配额可能导致 FVU 回升；但这正是本轮要回答的关键问题。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk K=128` 的 FVU=0.1430 说明 `lowrank + expert` 本体已有清晰价值，但 `lowrank_expert_residual K=128 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 进一步降到 0.1113，说明 residual cleanup 仍然重要。","当前 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可能把 `K=128` 中过多预算放给了全局 residual cleanup，而对 routed expert 段偏保守；`0.5` 是一次同成本下更均衡的验证。","`STAGE1_RATIO` 主要重分配 expert 与 residual 两段的 K 预算，不显著改变总 selection/deployment 成本，因此适合作为低成本前沿的纯结构归因实验。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.5` 在约 0.46x 成本下明显优于 r56，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=160` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.375`，继续细化这条三段式前沿的最优分工。","如果 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.5` 明显劣于 r56，则可初步判断当前低成本区更依赖强 residual cleanup；下一轮应回到 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 线路，并优先测试 `K=144` 或 `TRUNK_RANK`。","如果 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.5` 与 r56 接近但不更优，则说明该 family 在 `K=128` 附近对预算分配不太敏感，后续应把注意力转回更能改变 total_cost 的 `K` 或切到 `two_stage_residual_expert` 做对照。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0001.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"选择直接兼容 family `topk`，其最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i in S(x)} α_i(x) b_i`。导出到 LUTurbo 时，`{b_i}` 是静态向量库，在线仅做 top-64 选择、系数计算、查表 `W b_i`、加权求和，并保留现有选择性补偿接口。相对 cold-start baseline 仅把 `K` 从 128 降到 64，可把 combined total_cost 从约 `0.38x` 降到约 `0.31x`，先在 `<0.5x` 区域建立可解释 cost anchor。","summary":"兼容性判断：`topk` 为直接兼容。选择 `K=64` 是单变量、低接线风险、最贴合当前 round 1 成本探索目标的动作；在 `d_in=1024, n=4096, EF=1` 下，encoder ratio 约 `0.25x`，deployment ratio 约 `0.06x`，combined ratio 约 `0.31x`，明显低于 `1.5x` 硬预算，也比 baseline `K=128` 的约 `0.38x` 更接近低成本前沿。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"遵守冷启动单变量原则：`reference_round=null`，仅修改一个 env 参数 `K`。该提案不依赖新增 tunable 参数，也不引入不兼容 family。主要风险是 FVU 可能因 `K` 减半而上升，但这正是当前 target 需要先测清的低成本锚点。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"64"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`topk` 直接兼容 LUTurbo：`x_hat = Σ α_i b_i`，可直接导出为静态向量库查表加权和。","cold-start 首轮优先建立 `<0.5x` 低成本 anchor；`K=64, EF=1` 的 topk combined cost 约 `0.31x`。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=64` 的 FVU 仍可接受，下一轮继续向 `K=32` 压缩以补足更低成本区。","如果 `K=64` 的 FVU 退化过大，再回到同量级成本附近测试 `factorized_topk` 或恢复更高 `K`。"],"reference_round":null}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0039.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":37,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"lower_total_cost","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差做 sparse cleanup，因此仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。r37 已在 K=192、EF=1 下得到强质量锚点 FVU≈0.0424；本轮相对 r37 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK: 384 -> 128`，主假设是当前 trunk 明显过重，降低 trunk rank 后仍能保留大部分重构质量，同时把 total_cost 从约 1.06x 压到约 0.69x，从而把这条新结构性前沿往低到中成本带延伸。","summary":"以 r37 的强质量结果为参考，只下调 `TRUNK_RANK` 到 128，测试 `lowrank_expert_residual` 能否在明显更低 total_cost 下保持接近 r37 的低 FVU。这比继续在高成本点附近微调更符合当前低开销探索目标。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束；相对 r37 只修改 `TRUNK_RANK`。该改动同时降低 encoder 与 deployment 成本，归因清晰，且直接回答当前最关键的问题：这条新 family 是否能形成一段向低中成本延展的 Pareto 段。相比继续调 `STAGE1_RATIO`，`TRUNK_RANK` 更契合 Round 39 的低成本优先策略。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 仍保持明显优于现有 <0.8x 区域 anchor 的 FVU，则下一轮继续保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=192` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO`，细化这条新 Pareto 段的形状。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的 FVU 退化过大，则说明该 family 的质量对 trunk 依赖较强；下一轮优先回到同 family，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=192` 寻找折中点。","如果该 family 在降成本后仍具竞争力，则 `two-stage residual expert` 的优先级可以暂时后移，因为当前 family 已经回答了三段式结构值得继续。"],"notes_to_memory":["r37 `lowrank_expert_residual K=192 EF=1` 已产生强质量锚点，val_fvu≈0.042385。","`lowrank_expert_residual` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是 trunk 静态库 + expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。","按当前实现的成本估算，`TRUNK_RANK=128` 时 combined_ratio≈0.69x，显著低于 r37 的≈1.06x，且仍在硬约束内。","Round 39 应优先回答这条新 family 是否能向低中成本带延展，而不是回到 plain selector 家族继续扫 K。"],"touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0028.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式取 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i。对 `group_topk` 而言，组内竞争只改变 support 形成方式，不改变 decoder 形式；导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是单个静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 r27 只把 ARCHITECTURE 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `group_topk`，可把总成本维持在约 0.44x（encoder 0.25x + deploy 0.19x），同时测试“组内竞争带来的更分散支持集”是否能在当前低成本区把 FVU 压到优于现有 topk K=192 的 0.1577。","summary":"停止继续打磨已显著落后前沿的 expert_topk，改用 r27 作为单变量锚点，仅切到直接兼容的 group_topk，在 K=192、EF=1、adam、8e-4 下做一次 matched 低开销 probe，验证组竞争是否能在 0.44x 成本带补出新的 <0.5x Pareto 点。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"group_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"主要风险是 group_topk_size=4 的默认分组可能对当前 hookpoint 不合适，导致组约束只带来容量损失而没有支持质量增益；如果这轮在 0.44x 附近仍明显落后 topk K=192，就应尽快结束这一 family 的优先级，而不是继续做 recipe 微调。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"group_topk"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["group_topk 的 LUTurbo 导出形式与 topk 相同：x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i b_i，组内竞争只发生在在线选择链路。","在当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，group_topk K=192 EF=1 的预估成本为 sel=1048576 (0.25x), deploy=786432 (0.19x), total=1835008 (0.44x)。","expert_topk 已在更低成本区给出三个可行但明显偏弱的点，本轮应把预算转向其他兼容 family，而不是继续局部打磨它。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 group_topk 在 0.44x 下优于 topk K=192，则下一轮优先沿同 family 调 K=160 或 256，确认该 family 的低成本 Pareto 形状。","如果 group_topk 不优于 topk K=192，则下一轮转向另一个未充分验证但仍处于低成本带的直接兼容 family，如 jumprelu。"],"reference_round":27}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0063.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判断为扩展兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r61 仅把 K 从 128 降到 96，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`、`TRUNK_RANK=64`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EF=1` 不变时，优先压缩部署查表成本，把这条已被验证有效的三段式结构拉回 <0.5x 带；如果 r61 的质量优势主要来自结构本身而不只是更高 K，那么该点应在明显更低 total_cost 下仍维持接近或优于当前 <0.5x 最佳点的 FVU，并形成新的结构性 Pareto 段。","summary":"r62 已给出清晰负信号：继续把固定 K 预算从 expert 段挪给 residual 段不会改善。Round 63 不再细扫 ratio，而是从 r61 的有效三段式锚点直接压 `K`，测试 `lowrank_expert_residual` 能否回到 <0.5x 低成本带并保住质量。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r61 只改 `K`。该 family 属于 LUTurbo 扩展兼容 family，不触碰不兼容方向，也不需要新增 tunable 参数接线。选择 `K=96` 而不是继续调 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或 `TRUNK_RANK`，是因为 r62 已经说明段间预算再分配不是主要旋钮，而当前低开销探索模式最缺的是把这条已验证有效的三段式结构压回 <0.5x 区域。主要风险是 K 压缩过度导致 FVU 回退到接近 `lowrank_expert_topk`；但无论结果正负，都能直接回答这条 family 在低成本带是否成立。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"96"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 在 `TRUNK_RANK=64, NUM_EXPERTS=32, K=128` 下已证明结构有效；下一步重点应是把它压回低成本带，而不是继续做段间配比微调。","Round 63 是对 r61 的 deploy-cost compression probe：只降 `K`，直接测试三段式结构能否在 <0.5x 区域保住大部分质量。","按当前 frontier 口径，`K` 是把 r61 从约 0.53x 拉回低成本带的最直接单变量杠杆。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=96` 仍显著优于当前 <0.5x 最佳点，则下一轮继续保持 family 不变，只改 `K=80` 或 `K=112`，细化这条新三段式 Pareto 段的位置。","如果 `K=96` 明显退化到接近 `lowrank_expert_topk`，则说明当前三段式结构的收益高度依赖较高 deploy budget；后续应把低成本预算重新投回 `lowrank_expert_topk` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert`。","如果结果异常，先核对 round config 与 checkpoint config 中 `k=96` 是否真实生效，再决定是否把该轮当作结构证据。"],"reference_round":61}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0041.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_perf_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"group_topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.01"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"group_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"The recent `first_step_timeout` crashes are not specific to `group_topk`: the gated AUXK=0 recovery run also advanced through the first few microbatches and then stalled at the first optimizer step. That points to a shared training-path bottleneck rather than an architecture verdict. Replacing CUDA's per-step fired-latent `cat`+advanced-index update with an incremental boolean fired mask in `sparsify/trainer.py` should remove that first-step spike and let the unresolved `group_topk` K=128 proxy run complete under the current strongest regime.","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["If the patched `group_topk` run completes and is competitive with gated at K=128, keep the family alive and start stabilizing its grouped-selection design inside `sparsify/`.","If the run completes normally but `group_topk` is still clearly worse on FVU, retire hard grouped competition and move to a more expressive new family rather than more selector variants.","If `group_topk` still hits a first-step timeout after this shared trainer fix, stop spending rounds on it and treat the remaining issue as a deeper execution-path incompatibility."],"notes_to_memory":["Rounds 38 and 40 both progressed through several microbatches before timing out, so the failure signature is now shared across `group_topk` and gated rather than isolated to one family.","The stall aligns with the first optimizer step, which makes shared post-accumulation bookkeeping a stronger suspect than encoder forward quality.","This round patches `sparsify/trainer.py` so CUDA tracks fired latents with an incremental per-step boolean mask instead of building a large concatenated index tensor at step end, while preserving the deferred NPU path."],"primary_variable":"code_fix","self_review":"This is the narrowest defensible follow-up because the unresolved issue is now a shared runtime bottleneck, and another parameter-only probe would risk repeating the same crash without adding architectural evidence. The main risk is that the timeout may come from optimizer or logging overhead instead, but the logs make the fired-latent bookkeeping on the first optimizer step the best current target.","summary":"Patch the shared trainer dead-feature bookkeeping to reduce first-optimizer-step overhead on CUDA, then retry the blocked `group_topk` K=128 proxy comparison under the gated anchor settings.","touched_files":["sparsify/trainer.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0075.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","reference_round":74,"env_overrides":[{"key":"NUM_EXPERTS","value":"256"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_e Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 e(x) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“router 选单个静态子库 + 子库内 local top-k + 查表加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `expert_topk` 属于直接兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert`、`factorized_expert_topk` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。相对 r74 仅把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 128 提到 256，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk`、`K=160`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，继续回答 routed-only MoE-like 前沿的核心问题：如果 r73→r74 的连续改善说明当前低成本带的主要瓶颈仍有一部分来自总静态子库容量不足，而不是 router 质量或 K 预算已经饱和，那么进一步扩大总容量、同时保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 的短激活路径，应能在仍处于 <0.5x 的近同一 total_cost 下继续压低 FVU，并更清楚地界定这条直接兼容前沿的容量收益何时开始饱和。","summary":"Round 75 继续沿 r73、r74 的正信号做单变量 sparse-capacity continuation，不回到旧 family 的 K 轴微调。只把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 提到 256，直接判断 routed-only `expert_topk` 的容量收益是否还能继续换到更低 FVU，同时仍留在低成本带。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r74 只改 `NUM_EXPERTS`。这一步不是旧 family 的局部扫点，而是当前高优先级 MoE-like 方向的继续验证；r73 和 r74 已经给出同方向正信号，现在最有信息量的问题就是容量收益是否已接近饱和。主要风险是边际收益继续变小，但这同样是有价值的结构结论，因为它会明确告诉我们 routed-only 低成本线是否该收口并把预算转回带 trunk 或 residual cleanup 的兼容 family。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式保持为静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和，兼容性仍为直接兼容。","r73 (`NUM_EXPERTS=64`) 与 r74 (`NUM_EXPERTS=128`) 在相同 `K=160, EF=1` 下连续改善，说明 routed-only sparse-capacity 扩容在当前 target 上尚未被证伪。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，`expert_topk K=160 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=256` 的成本约为 selection 0.31x、deployment 0.16x、total 0.47x，仍在 Round 75 要重点补点的 <0.5x 低成本带内，并明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","如果这一步仍改善，则直接兼容 routed-only 前沿将得到更完整的容量曲线；如果改善停止，可更有把握地把后续结构预算转向 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `factorized_expert_topk` 等方向。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=256` 在近同成本下继续明显优于 r74，则下一轮可保持 family 不变，只改 `K=192` 或继续上探更大容量，判断 routed-only 前沿更该向上要质量还是继续向右做容量。","如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=256` 改善极小或停止，则可较清晰判定当前 `expert_topk` 的低成本瓶颈已不主要在总子库容量，后续应把结构预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual`、`lowrank_expert_topk` 或 `factorized_expert_topk` 这类带 shared basis / trunk / residual cleanup 的兼容结构。","如果结果异常，先核对 `round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `num_experts=256` 已真实生效，再决定是否把该轮当作结构证据。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0010.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"切到直接兼容 family `jumprelu`，最终重构公式仍为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S(x)} α_i(x) b_i`。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时，`{b_i}` 仍是单个静态向量库；在线链路仍是先形成支持集、再计算系数、查表 `W b_i`、加权求和，并可接入现有选择性补偿接口，JumpReLU 只改变支持形成方式而不改变最终静态库有限加权和的部署形式。本轮相对 r8 仅修改 `ARCHITECTURE`，在保持 `K=64, EXPANSION_FACTOR=1, OPTIMIZER=adam, LR=8e-4` 不变的同成本槽位下，验证阈值化支持选择在当前最佳 recipe 下是否能给出更好的训练曲线形状与更低 FVU。","summary":"兼容性判断：`jumprelu` 为直接兼容。当前 `<0.5x` 区域已经有 `topk` 的 `K=32/48/64` anchors，`r9 group_topk` 在 matched low-cost 槽位下也未优于 `r8 topk`；继续只在 `topk` 内局部微调的信息增量有限。相比之下，`jumprelu` 在旧的 signum recipe 下与 `topk` 基本打平，但尚未在当前最佳 `adam` recipe 上做过 matched probe，而其总成本仍约 `0.31x`（selection `0.25x` + deployment `0.06x`）。因此这轮最干净的问题是：在不改变 total_cost 的前提下，阈值化支持形成能否在当前 hookpoint 上优于 plain top-k。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"遵守单变量原则，基于 `reference_round=8` 仅修改 `ARCHITECTURE`。我没有转去 `gated/routed/bucketed_topk`，因为它们会把总成本抬到约 `0.56x`，会同时切换结构槽位与成本带；也没有继续停留在 `group_topk` 或 `topk` 微调，因为当前最需要的是确认同成本低开销带里是否还有未充分验证的直接兼容 family 能在 `adam` recipe 下给出新增信息。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"jumprelu"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`jumprelu` 直接兼容 LUTurbo：最终形式仍是单静态向量库上的有限加权和 `Σ α_i b_i`，阈值门控只影响支持形成。","`jumprelu@K=64,EF=1` 在当前 target 上的估计总成本仍约 `0.31x`，与 `r8 topk@K=64,EF=1` 同槽位；此前仅在 signum recipe 下测试过，当前 `adam` 最佳 recipe 仍属未验证。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `jumprelu@adam` 优于 `topk@adam`，下一轮再在 `jumprelu` 内单独探索 `K` 或带宽相关参数。","如果 `jumprelu@adam` 仍无增益，则说明当前 low-cost 直接兼容单库 family 的新增信息接近饱和，下一轮应优先转向新的结构槽位或更高优先级未充分验证方向。"],"reference_round":8}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0051.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 e(x) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，B_e={b_{e,i}} 是静态 expert 子库。在线侧仍可导出为“router 选静态子库 + 子库内查表 + 有限加权和”的 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判定为直接兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：相对 r26 仅设置 NUM_EXPERTS=16，把 expert_topk 从 legacy fixed-split 布局切到真正的 MoE-like sparse-capacity expansion，在保持 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1、K=192、EF=1 不变的前提下显著扩大总静态容量；如果当前 <0.5x 区域的主要瓶颈是容量不足而非路由机制本身，那么该点应在约 0.44x total_cost 下明显优于 r26 的 FVU=0.29111021757125854。","summary":"下一轮不再回到 plain selector 邻域，也不继续在 lowrank_expert_residual 上做局部压缩；先回答高优先级的真 MoE-like 问题。相对 r26 只改 NUM_EXPERTS=16，是对 expert_topk 做最干净的单变量稀疏扩容验证：active path 仍短，cost proxy 预计 selection≈0.25x、deployment≈0.19x、total≈0.44x，正好落在当前最需要补强的低成本带。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r26 只改 NUM_EXPERTS。该 family 属于直接兼容，不触碰不兼容 family，也不需要新增架构或新参数接线。当前代码里 NUM_EXPERTS 已经接入 `sparsify/`、override registry、config resolution、runner 和脚本透传，因此本轮应直接用真实训练回答“纯 routed sublibrary 扩容是否成立”。主要风险是当前 total_cost proxy 只统计 active path，未显式惩罚更大的静态库存储；因此即便结果为正，后续也仍要再判断它对 LUTurbo 真实系统成本是否同样成立。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"NUM_EXPERTS","value":"16"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`expert_topk` 在显式设置 NUM_EXPERTS 时会从 legacy fixed-split 布局切到 true sparse-capacity mode：每个 active expert 保持 base width，而总静态 expert 容量随 NUM_EXPERTS 扩张。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 实测估算，`expert_topk K=192 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=16` 的 total_cost 约为 0.44x，仍低于当前 <0.5x 前沿上界与 1.5x 硬预算。","这是 NUM_EXPERTS 的正式验证轮；训练后必须检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 中出现 `num_experts=16`，并检查 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `sae.num_experts=16`，若任一缺失则本轮结果无效。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 NUM_EXPERTS=16 生效且 FVU 明显优于 r26，并接近当前 <0.5x anchors，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 K，测试真 MoE-like 前沿能否继续向左或向下延伸。","如果 NUM_EXPERTS=16 生效但改善很弱，则可以较清晰地判定纯 routed sublibrary 扩容不足以解决当前 target，应把预算转向带 trunk 的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert`。","如果配置持久化里没有出现 `num_experts=16`，则下一轮继续只做参数生效确认，不把这轮训练结果当成结构证据。"],"reference_round":26}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0002.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"The new JumpReLU family deserves its first proxy measurement at the K=128 quality anchor; learnable thresholds with smooth gating may suppress weak activations and beat plain TopK FVU before any cost-oriented moves.","summary":"Run the first proxy comparison for the `jumprelu` family at K=128 using the prototype already added under `sparsify/`. Keep the round focused on establishing whether this family can materially improve the anchor-quality regime before any smaller-K or throughput tradeoffs.","change_type":"parameter_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This is the narrowest coherent follow-up because there is still no empirical signal for the new family. Risk remains runtime overhead from the dense encode path, but that should be interpreted as implementation cost unless quality is also clearly unpromising.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"jumprelu"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD","value":"0.15"},{"key":"JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH","value":"0.10"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 2 uses the existing JumpReLU prototype for its first proxy measurement at the K=128 quality anchor.","No additional code changes were needed; this round is intended to establish initial quality and runtime signal for the new family."],"next_hypotheses":["If JumpReLU beats the TopK K=128 anchor on proxy, tune threshold initialization and bandwidth as the family-specific stabilization pass.","If JumpReLU quality is competitive but runtime is poor, follow with a code-fix round to optimize the encode path rather than discarding the family.","If JumpReLU clearly misses the quality target, explore a different architecture family with stronger routing structure instead of continuing weak local tuning."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0002.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"选择直接兼容 family `topk`，最终重构公式仍为 `x_hat = Σ_{i in S(x)} α_i(x) b_i`。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时，`{b_i}` 仍是单个静态向量库，在线链路不变：先做 top-k 选择与系数计算，再查表 `W b_i` 并加权求和，可继续接入选择性补偿。相对 r1 仅将 `K` 从 64 降到 32，测试更低部署查表开销下是否还能维持可接受 FVU，从而补足 `<0.5x` 区域的更低成本锚点。","summary":"兼容性判断：`topk` 为直接兼容。Round 2 的首要任务是补全 `<0.5x` total_cost` 区域；在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=topk, EF=1` 不变时，把 `K=64` 降到 `K=32` 可将 deployment 从约 `0.06x` 进一步降到约 `0.03x`，combined total_cost 从约 `0.31x` 压到约 `0.28x`，是当前最干净、最可归因的低开销扩展点。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"遵守单变量原则，基于 `reference_round=1` 仅修改 `K`。这轮不会回答跨 family 架构优劣，但能直接补齐更低成本区的 Pareto 形状；主要风险是 `K` 继续减半后 FVU 明显变差，不过这正是当前阶段需要测清的低成本边界。高优先级未验证的 MoE-like 方向仍值得后续抽轮次实现，但在当前低成本区域仅有 1 个点时，先做这个低风险 cost anchor 更稳妥。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"32"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`topk` 在当前 target 上继续保持直接兼容：`x_hat = Σ α_i b_i`，在线导出链路无需变化。","r2 优先补 `<0.5x` 更低成本锚点；`topk, EF=1, K=32` 的预估 total_cost 约 `0.28x`，低于 r1 的 `0.31x`。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=32` 的 FVU 仍可接受，可把它作为低成本端 anchor，再转向 architecture-only 的 `factorized_topk` 或 `routed` 做同区间对照。","如果 `K=32` 的 FVU 退化过大，则回到 `K=64` 附近保持成本不变，优先测试新的兼容 family 以寻找更优同成本点。"],"reference_round":1}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0060.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert；在线导出仍是 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判断为扩展兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r59 只把 TRUNK_RANK 从 16 提到 64，在保持 `NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`K=128`、`EF=1`、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1 不变时，如果当前 `lowrank + expert` 的主要瓶颈已经从 routed capacity 转移到 shared smooth trunk 太薄，那么更宽的 low-rank 主干应在仍处于低成本带的前提下显著压低 FVU，并回答这条 shared+expert 结构是否值得继续扩展。","summary":"不回到 plain selector，也不继续做 K/LR 邻域微调；沿着 r59 的 true sparse-capacity `lowrank_expert_topk` 主线，只改 `TRUNK_RANK`，直接判断当前低成本区的瓶颈更像是 trunk 宽度不足还是 routed expert 容量不足。按当前代码成本估算，`TRUNK_RANK=64` 约为 encoder 0.29x、deployment 0.19x、total 0.48x，仍在本轮优先关注的 <0.5x 带边缘内。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r59 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。该 family 属于 LUTurbo 扩展兼容 family，不触碰不兼容方向，也不需要新增 tunable 参数接线。选择 `TRUNK_RANK` 而不是继续加 `NUM_EXPERTS`，是因为 r57→r59 在 routed capacity 扩张下只有小幅改善；当前更高信息量的问题是 shared trunk 是否已成为主要瓶颈。主要风险是 cost 仍会从约 0.41x 升到约 0.48x，若 FVU 改善很弱，则说明这条 `lowrank + expert` 结构在当前 target 上可能已接近饱和。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"64"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式保持不变：静态 trunk 库加单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","r59 已把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 提到 32 并取得小幅改善；Round 60 用 `TRUNK_RANK` 单变量 probe 来区分瓶颈是在 shared trunk 还是在 routed capacity。","按当前代码成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=128 NUM_EXPERTS=32 TRUNK_RANK=64` 的 total_cost 约 0.48x，仍远低于 1.5x 硬预算。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `TRUNK_RANK=64` 明显改善 FVU，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只回退到更经济的 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 做 matched 检查，确认更优 Pareto 落点是否已经在 0.43x 附近。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=64` 改善仍很弱，则可较清晰判定 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的短板不只是 trunk 宽度，后续应把预算转向 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert`，而不是继续在这条 family 上加容量。","如果本轮结果异常，先核对 round config 与 checkpoint config 中 `trunk_rank=64` 是否真实生效，再决定是否把结果当作结构证据。"],"reference_round":59}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0035.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择一个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，并只在该子库内做 local top-k 得到 α_{e,i}(x)。因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设：在 EF=1、K=128 的低开销带，lowrank trunk 先吸收平滑主干、expert local top-k 再处理残差，能比 plain expert_topk 与同带宽 plain selector 提供更好的 FVU/total_cost 权衡，并形成新的 Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果 r12->lowrank_expert_topk(K=128) 给出有效信号且 FVU 明显优于当前 0.38x-0.56x 邻域锚点，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 K 到 160，验证该 family 在 0.69x total_cost 处是否继续沿 Pareto 前进。","如果该原型训练不稳或收益不足，则优先继续实现 `lowrank + expert + residual`，而不是回到 plain topk/jumprelu 的局部扫点。"],"notes_to_memory":["已按 sae-architecture-integration checklist 完成新 family 接线：`lowrank_expert_topk` 已加入 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist，并加入 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch。","新增原型 family 的导出形式为 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，满足 LUTurbo 静态库约束，兼容性应视为扩展兼容。","已完成 instantiate/forward/backward smoke：`lowrank_expert_topk`, K=128, EF=1 通过。","当前原型采用固定 4 experts、active_experts=1、无新增 tunable 参数，因此本轮只需改 `ARCHITECTURE`，不需要修改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。","在 target proxy(1024x4096) 上，`lowrank_expert_topk` 的估算成本为：K=128 -> total 0.56x；K=160 -> total 0.69x；K=192 -> total 0.81x。低开销起点应优先从 K=128 开始。"],"reference_round":12,"self_review":"这轮只改了一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE`，相对 r12 保持 K=128、EF=1、LR=8e-4、optimizer=adam 不变，归因清晰。代码侧只做最小 family 原型接线，没有引入新 tunable，因此不存在 override/runner 静默回退风险。风险是当前 prototype 的 expert 数和 active_experts 仍是固定值，若首轮效果一般，不能立刻下结论否定 `lowrank + expert` 方向本身。","summary":"已实现并 smoke 通过新的 `lowrank_expert_topk` family，用最小 lowrank+expert 原型覆盖当前高优先级未验证结构槽位。建议下一轮以 r12(topk K=128 EF=1) 为参考，只切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，先在约 0.56x total_cost 的低开销带验证该 family 是否能形成新的 Pareto 段。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0096.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":95,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"96"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单个静态 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容；`expert_topk` 属于直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 属于不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：r94 与 r95 已经把 `lowrank + expert` 的 shared-trunk knee 压到 `TRUNK_RANK=40-48` 区间，并连续形成新的更靠左低成本点，因此当前最有信息量的问题不再是继续细扫 trunk，而是这条更强 recipe 是否已经足够支撑更低部署查表预算。相对 r95 仅将 `K: 128 -> 96`，在保持 `TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变时，如果当前瓶颈更多在 deployment lookup 而不是 trunk 宽度，那么 FVU 应只温和回升，并把这条兼容前沿继续左移到更低 total_cost 带。","summary":"不回到 plain selector 的旧 K 轴，也不立刻切去别的 family。以 r95 为 reference，只改 `K=96`，对刚刚被 r94/r95 强化的 `lowrank_expert_topk` 做第一次 deploy-cost compression probe，直接回答这条 `lowrank + expert` 结构在更低在线查表预算下是否仍能维持新的低成本 Pareto 段。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r95 只改 `K`。这不是 old-family 的重复邻域扫描，而是在当前已有连续正信号的新结构线上，第一次测试 deployment 侧是否还能继续压缩。主要风险是 `K=96` 会让局部 expert residual 容量明显不足，FVU 回升到接近或劣于 `expert_topk K=160` 的 0.1243；但这同样是高价值结论，因为它能清楚界定当前这条低成本线的最小可用 lookup budget。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r94 (`TRUNK_RANK=48`) 与 r95 (`TRUNK_RANK=40`) 已连续把 `lowrank_expert_topk` 前沿左移，说明当前 target 上 `lowrank + expert` 的 shared trunk 确实可压缩。","r93 (`expert_topk ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`) 仍是 routed-only multi-expert active path 的明确负信号，因此本轮继续留在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 主线比回到 MoE active-path 扩展更合逻辑。","当前还没有 `lowrank_expert_topk NUM_EXPERTS=32 TRUNK_RANK=40 K=96` 的真实训练结果；这是该强化 recipe 上的首个低部署预算 probe。","按当前 fresh cost 估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=96 NUM_EXPERTS=32 TRUNK_RANK=40` 的 selection 基本不变，deployment 会比 r95 进一步下降，total_cost 继续左移且仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=96` 仍形成非支配点，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=80` 或 `K=112`，继续细化这条低成本 Pareto 段的 deployment knee。","如果 `K=96` 明显退化到接近或劣于 `expert_topk K=160`，则说明当前 `lowrank + expert` 线的收益仍依赖 `K=128` 级别的 lookup budget；下一轮应停止继续压 K，转去做 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 结构对照。","如果 `K=96` 与 r95 非常接近但成本改善有限，则说明这条 family 的主要瓶颈已从 deployment 转回 encoder 侧；后续应优先比较 residual cleanup，而不是继续做更激进的 K 压缩。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0037_repair_1.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":27,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个 expert 子库 e(x) 并在其内做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差再做一次小预算 sparse 补偿。因此它仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。本次 repair 不改变实验设计，只修复 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的注册链与最小可运行实现，使原始 Round 37 实验能够按原设定重新运行。","summary":"已修复 Round 37 的工程性阻塞：补上 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 config whitelist、factory dispatch、concrete class，并完成同一目标 `(ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual, K=192, EF=1)` 的 instantiate/forward/backward smoke。保持原 family 与 env_overrides 不变，重新运行原始实验。","self_review":"这次 repair 没有改 family_name，也没有改 env_overrides；仍然是相对 r27 只切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`。阻塞根因是 `Unknown architecture`，已按架构集成 checklist 修复：whitelist、dispatch、class、exact-string smoke 都已完成。额外把该 family 接到了 `TRUNK_RANK/STAGE1_RATIO` override registry，避免后续调参时静默失效。exact smoke 在 `lowrank_expert_residual, K=192, EF=1` 上通过，估算总成本约 1.06x 原始 matmul、预算比率 0.71x，仍在硬约束内。","next_hypotheses":["如果 rerun 能稳定完成，则再根据真实 FVU 判断 `lowrank + expert + residual` 是否值得继续；当前 repair 轮不对结构优劣做新结论。","如果 rerun 仍失败，下一次 repair 应直接针对新的失败模式处理，而不是再次回到注册链。"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 37 的首个 blocker 是注册链缺失，不是训练语义问题。","`lowrank_expert_residual` 已加入 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist，并加入 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch。","已实现最小可运行 `LowRankExpertResidualSparseCoder`：low-rank trunk + expert-local first pass + global residual cleanup second pass。","已补 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py` 中 `lowrank_expert_residual -> {TRUNK_RANK, STAGE1_RATIO}`，避免后续 structural override 被拒绝。","exact smoke 结果：`integration_smoke: OK lowrank_expert_residual 192 1 cuda`；成本估算 combined_ratio≈1.06x，combined_budget_ratio≈0.71x，可行。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0038.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":37,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"lower_total_cost","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差做 sparse cleanup，因此仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。r37 已经证明该 family 在 K=192、EF=1 下可给出很强质量信号；本轮相对 r37 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK: 384 -> 128`，主假设是当前 trunk 明显过重，降低 trunk rank 后仍能保留大部分重构质量，同时把 total_cost 从约 1.06x 压到约 0.69x，直接补当前更需要的低到中成本 Pareto 段。","summary":"沿着已验证有效的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 主线做单变量降成本回退，而不是切回旧 family。以 r37 为参考只降 `TRUNK_RANK` 到 128，测试该三段式结构能否以明显更低 total_cost 保持接近 r37 的低 FVU。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束；相对 r37 只修改 `TRUNK_RANK`。这是当前信息增量最高的动作，因为 r37 已给出强质量锚点，下一步最应该回答的是这条新 Pareto 段能否往低成本方向延伸，而不是继续在同一高成本点附近微调 `STAGE1_RATIO`。`TRUNK_RANK=128` 还能同时降低 encoder 与 deployment 成本，归因清晰。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 仍维持明显优于现有 <0.8x 区域 anchor 的 FVU，则下一轮继续保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=192` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO`，细化这条新 Pareto 段的形状。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的 FVU 退化过大，则说明该 family 质量主要依赖较重 trunk；下一轮优先回到 `TRUNK_RANK=192` 做中间点，而不是继续压得更低。","如果该 family 在降成本后仍然保持竞争力，则 `two-stage residual expert` 的优先级可以暂时后移，因为当前 family 已经回答了三段式结构值得继续。"],"notes_to_memory":["r37 `lowrank_expert_residual K=192 EF=1` 已给出强质量锚点，memory 中记录的 FVU 约为 0.0424。","`lowrank_expert_residual` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是 trunk 静态库 + expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。","按当前实现的成本估算，`TRUNK_RANK=128` 时 combined_ratio 约 0.69x，显著低于 r37 的约 1.06x，同时仍在硬约束内。","Round 38 应优先回答这条新 family 是否能向低中成本带延展，而不是回到 plain selector 家族继续扫 K。"],"touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0025.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e*(x)}(x)} α_i(x) b_{e*(x),i}，其中 e*(x) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert 子库，S_{e*(x)}(x) 是该静态子库内�), with stronger evidence if it stays near the smooth trend between the current `K=7` (`0.12780356407165527`) and `K=4` anchor.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"smaller_k","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This is the cleanest next step: one hypothesis, one variable, no execution-layer changes, and it directly tests whether the family’s useful regime extends below K=7. I am not proposing a rerun because the K=7 result is comfortably non-dominated versus the K=4 anchor, so frontier expansion is a stronger use of the next round.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"6"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 82 should be a controlled parameter-only probe at K=6 for `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` after confirmed non-dominated points at K=7 and above under the fixed EF=12/signum/LR=3.2e-3/AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 recipe.","The success criterion is frontier expansion rather than a same-K comparison: if K=6 stays below the current K=4 anchor FVU (0.14181029796600342), it is a valid new Pareto tradeoff."],"next_hypotheses":["If `K=6` yields another strong non-dominated point, test `K=5` under the same fixed recipe.","If `K=6` is only marginally below the `K=4` anchor, do one confirmatory rerun at `K=6` before pushing lower.","If `K=6` misses the `K=4` anchor clearly, conclude this family's frontier likely ends at `K=7` and shift exploration to a new family or mechanism."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0009.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Keeping `lowrank_two_stage_residual` fixed at `K=16` and reducing only `EXPANSION_FACTOR` from 12 to 8 will test whether this family can add a lower-cost non-dominated point without giving up too much FVU.","summary":"Use a parameter-only probe on the existing `lowrank_two_stage_residual` family at `K=16`, changing only `EXPANSION_FACTOR` to `8` while pinning `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, and `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0`. The low-K tail has already been mapped from `K=32` down to `K=1`, so the next clean frontier question is whether the same family can trade some reconstruction quality for a meaningfully smaller model at a proven useful K.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"smaller_ef","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This avoids the prior policy-rejected code-plus-architecture move, preserves strict variable isolation with `primary_variable=expansion_factor`, and probes the remaining frontier dimension on a stable family.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"16"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"8"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 9 shifts from the completed K sweep to an EF sweep on the same family, using `K=16` as the anchor and changing only `EXPANSION_FACTOR`.","The previous routed-family proposal was policy-rejected because it coupled code editing with an architecture change, so the next step should stay parameter-only and isolate a single frontier dimension."],"next_hypotheses":["If `K=16, EF=8` stays competitive, continue to `K=24, EF=8` or `K=8, EF=8` to map the lower-EF lane.","If `EF=8` degrades too much at `K=16`, keep `EF=12` for this family and revisit architecture changes only after a clean code-only integration plan.","If `EF=8` is borderline but promising, test `EF=10` at the same `K=16` to refine the cost-quality knee."],"primary_variable":"expansion_factor"}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0019.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"A router-driven variant of `lowrank_two_stage_residual` should improve the smaller-K frontier at `K=16, EF=12` by using explicit support-selection perturbations in each residual stage, potentially beating the current `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K=16 point (`FVU=0.10792168974876404`) without changing optimizer or width.","summary":"Added and registered `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual` under `sparsify/`, with independent routers for stage-1 and stage-2 support selection. Exact-architecture instantiate/forward/backward smoke test passed for `ARCHITECTURE=routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual, K=16, EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` on CUDA, so the next round should be a clean architecture-only experiment at that point.","change_type":"edit_sae_code","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This is a disciplined architecture-only move after many rounds of local tuning on `lowrank_two_stage_residual`. The registration chain is complete and the exact launch string smoke-tested. Main risk: the router score coefficient (`0.1 * tanh(...)`) is heuristic, so the family may need one follow-up calibration round if it is competitive but noisy.","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"16"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["Integrated new architecture family `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual` into `sparsify/config.py` and `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`.","Implemented router-perturbed support selection in both residual stages while keeping the low-rank trunk and two-stage residual decode structure unchanged.","Exact smoke test passed: `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual`, `K=16`, `EF=12`, forward+backward on CUDA."],"next_hypotheses":["If `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual` wins at `K=16`, rerun the same family at `K=24, EF=12` to test whether routing also improves the adjacent mid-K frontier point.","If it is close but worse than baseline, keep the family and test a smaller router perturbation strength rather than abandoning routing immediately.","If it clearly underperforms at `K=16`, revert focus to the mainline `lowrank_two_stage_residual` family and resume smaller-K exploitation there."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0096.json:22:    "expected_win": "confirm_baseline",
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0040.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Five rounds of stagnation mean scalar tweaks are exhausted, so the next move should be a fundamentally different architecture under a controlled recipe rather than more LR or aux changes. `lowrank_grouped_residual` is a materially different low-EF family that enforces group-local competition, and testing it at the frontier-relevant `K=16, EF=12` slot can reveal whether structured support selection improves the mid-K tradeoff over `lowrank_two_stage_residual`.","summary":"Run a pure architecture comparison at `K=16, EF=12` by switching from `lowrank_two_stage_residual` to `lowrank_grouped_residual` while keeping optimizer, learning rate, expansion factor, and aux fixed to the settled mid-K recipe. This satisfies severe-stagnation guidance by opening a genuinely different architecture branch instead of continuing minor scalar sweeps.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"lowrank_grouped_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This follows the severe-stagnation policy directly: stop minor tweaks and try a fundamentally different architecture. `K=16` is the cleanest target because it is frontier-relevant, uses the strongest settled `EF=12` recipe, and gives a controlled readout on whether grouped competition helps in the transition band.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_grouped_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"16"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 40 exits the failed scalar-exploitation loop under severe stagnation and opens a materially different architecture branch instead of continuing LR or aux sweeps.","The new test is `lowrank_grouped_residual` at `K=16, EF=12` under the settled `signum`, `LR=3.2e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` recipe to evaluate whether group-local sparse competition improves the mid-K frontier band."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_grouped_residual` wins at `K=16`, continue the same architecture-only comparison at `K=24` before changing any scalar hyperparameters.","If it is close but slightly worse at `K=16`, keep the family active and test one adjacent K to see whether the benefit is band-specific.","If it clearly loses at `K=16`, reject this branch and move to another substantially different built-in architecture rather than returning to minor sweeps."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0192.json:22:    "expected_win": "lower_cost",
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0149.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Eight non-improving rounds indicate the recent grouped, residual-VQ, and JumpReLU branches are not opening a new frontier, so the next step should remain a genuinely different existing architecture at the key `K=32, EF=16` slot. `lowrank_gated_residual` is the strongest remaining fundamentally different candidate because it uses learned gating without soft-codebook composition, and earlier results suggest it can be competitive in adjacent K regimes even though it has not yet been tested at this exact low-K EF=16 slot under the current pinned recipe.","summary":"Run an architecture-only comparison at `K=32, EF=16` by switching to `lowrank_gated_residual` while keeping optimizer, LR, aux loss, and preprocessing fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"lowrank_gated_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This follows the severe-stagnation directive to stop minor tweaks and keep trying fundamentally different existing architectures. I kept `K=32` because it remains the most valuable exposed EF=16 frontier slot for a clean architecture comparison, and I pinned the rest of the recipe so the result isolates whether plain learned gating beats the exhausted soft-codebook-style families.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_gated_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"32"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 149 continues severe-stagnation recovery by testing `lowrank_gated_residual` at `K=32, EF=16` after grouped soft-codebook, residual-VQ, and JumpReLU comparisons all failed to threaten the current bucketed frontier point.","Rationale: plain lowrank gating is structurally different from the recently exhausted soft-codebook and quantized families, and it has shown credible performance in other K regimes, making it a sensible remaining architecture probe at the most valuable exposed slot."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_gated_residual` is competitive at `K=32`, follow with `K=24` to map whether gating creates a better small-K tradeoff curve than the bucketed backbone.","If it is close but still worse than bucketed, shift the next round to a non-architecture axis such as preprocessing or optimizer on the strongest current bucketed anchor.","If it clearly loses at `K=32`, treat plain lowrank gating as noncompetitive in the current EF=16 regime and move to the next underexplored axis rather than more architecture churn."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0124.json:22:    "expected_win": "information_gain",
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0094.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"The routed soft-codebook two-stage family has now improved the frontier at `K=8`, `K=16`, and `K=24`, so the next direct test is whether the same architecture can also take over the `K=32` anchor under the unchanged EF=12 recipe.","summary":"Run one parameter-only follow-up at `K=32` with `routed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`, keeping `EF=12`, `signum`, `LR=3.2e-3`, and `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` fixed. This cleanly measures whether routing is now the dominant structural improvement across the full currently explored low/mid-K band.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"frontier_improve","family_name":"routed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"active","self_review":"This is the cleanest exploitation step: only `K` changes, and the family has already produced repeated frontier gains at adjacent anchors. The main risk is diminishing returns at higher K, where the non-routed baseline may already have enough budget that explicit routing adds complexity without benefit. Still, this is exactly the uncertainty that the next run should resolve.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"routed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"32"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r94 should extend the routed soft-codebook family sweep to `K=32` after frontier wins at `K=8`, `K=16`, and `K=24`.","Keep all recipe fields fixed and change only `K`; this isolates whether the routed advantage survives at the top end of the currently active EF=12 band.","A `K=32` win would strongly indicate that `routed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` should replace the plain two-stage soft-codebook backbone across the explored EF=12 frontier."],"next_hypotheses":["If `routed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` wins at `K=32`, consider testing the same family at `K=64` to probe whether the advantage persists beyond the current low-K coverage.","If it is close but slightly behind at `K=32`, try one targeted routing-temperature adjustment before abandoning the family at higher K.","If it clearly loses at `K=32`, treat the routed advantage as strongest in the `K=8` to `K=24` regime and refocus search on a different family for higher-K anchors."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0107.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"After eight non-improving rounds and two failed soft-codebook branch follow-ups at K=24, the next informative move is a fundamentally different architecture: a discrete low-rank-plus-VQ residual model may trade a small amount of reconstruction flexibility for a better mid-K Pareto point and more deployment-aligned structure.","summary":"Severe stagnation is active, so this round should stop iterating within the current soft-codebook family. Hold the successful mid-K recipe fixed and run one clean architecture comparison at the valuable smaller-K anchor `K=24` with `lowrank_residual_vq`, which is qualitatively different from the plain, grouped, gated, and routed soft-codebook variants tried recently. This keeps the experiment attributable to architecture alone while testing whether a discrete residual mechanism can reopen the K=24 frontier lane.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"small_k_frontier","family_name":"lowrank_residual_vq","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This follows the severe-stagnation policy: it changes architecture rather than making another scalar tweak, keeps K in the allowed set, and targets a valuable smaller-K frontier slot. The risk is that prior older-budget evidence for `lowrank_residual_vq` was weak, but that is still preferable to continuing minor soft-codebook variations after repeated non-improvements.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual_vq"},{"key":"K","value":"24"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Severe stagnation remained active after `lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual` cleanly ran but lost at `K=24`, so the search should move away from additional soft-codebook family tweaks.","Round 107 should test `lowrank_residual_vq` at `K=24` as a fundamentally different architecture under the fixed EF=12/signum/LR=3.2e-3 recipe to probe whether a discrete residual mechanism can recover the mid-K lane.","Keep the override set minimal and exact so the result isolates architecture rather than another recipe drift."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_residual_vq` is competitive at `K=24`, follow with the same fixed recipe at `K=32` to map whether the discrete residual lane scales across mid-K.","If it clearly loses at `K=24`, continue severe-stagnation search with another fundamentally different mechanism such as a non-codebook sparse selector family rather than returning to soft-codebook tweaks.","If it is noisy but close, run one confirmatory repeat at the same `K=24` anchor before promoting or discarding the family."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0134.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Adam may be failing specifically in the brittle low-K bucketed regime rather than across the whole `bucketed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` family. Testing the same EF=16 recipe at `K=64` isolates optimizer sensitivity on a stronger mid-K frontier point and could improve FVU without sacrificing a non-dominated tradeoff.","summary":"Run a parameter-only optimizer probe on `bucketed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` at `K=64, EF=16`, switching from `signum` to `adam` while keeping the rest of the recipe fixed. This checks whether the recent Adam failure was K32-specific and gives a cleaner read on whether Adam is worth keeping alive on the current leading family.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"bucketed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This stays within the operator-requested runtime axes and avoids unsupported loss-function plumbing through the fixed launcher. It is not the highest-value smaller-K target, but after Adam and Hadamard both failed at K32, a K64 control is the cleanest way to determine whether Adam is broadly bad under EF=16 or only bad in the tightest bucketed regime.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"bucketed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 134 should use `bucketed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` at `K=64` as the optimizer control after Adam failed badly at K32 under the same EF=16 family.","Keep the override set minimal and explicit so attribution stays on optimizer rather than architecture, EF, or aux drift.","If Adam is still poor at K64, treat `adam` as broadly unpromising for the current EF=16 bucketed backbone and stop spending rounds on it without a stronger reason."],"next_hypotheses":["If Adam improves the K64 bucketed point, propagate Adam to K96 or K128 to see whether the gain is a general mid/high-K effect before revisiting K32 with a retuned LR.","If Adam is neutral or worse at K64, deprioritize optimizer swaps on the bucketed family and return to supported preprocessing probes on a different existing backbone.","If Adam is close but noisy at K64, run one confirmatory repeat on the same target rather than branching to another architecture."],"primary_variable":"optimizer"}
